{"_id":"AwaSwcf1rfnJT3QY","name":"James the Swordsman","type":"hunter","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/avatars/pregens/core-book-james-the-swordsman.png","items":[{"_id":"oBnRzBLlOBjOWFzk","name":"Descriptor 1","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"I have been a lot of things in my life: ship captain, duellist of great renown, and lover of the most beautiful noblewomen. After years of successes and victories, a mysterious child defeated me with deception. This despicable boy led me into the lair of a dangerous beast and, after imprisoning me, left me to be eaten by the monster. I survived, though I lost a hand... I know for certain he who I seek is no human, and I joined the Order to hunt down the child I hate above all else, and thus have my revenge.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 4.","positive":"I have been a lot of things in my life: ship captain, duellist of great renown, and lover of the most beautiful noblewomen. After years of successes and victories, a mysterious child defeated me with deception. This despicable boy led me into the lair of a dangerous beast and, after imprisoning me, left me to be eaten by the monster. I survived, though I lost a hand... I know for certain he who I seek is no human, and I joined the Order to hunt down the child I hate above all else, and thus have my revenge.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241636,"modifiedTime":1783973241636,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"FbRoxNfHphsyNXQd","name":"Descriptor 2","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"I am a skilled swordsman and possess fine manners, which is why the Order considers me an excellent candidate to move among High Society. I love indulging in good food and dissolute company.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 4.","positive":"I am a skilled swordsman and possess fine manners, which is why the Order considers me an excellent candidate to move among High Society. I love indulging in good food and dissolute company.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241636,"modifiedTime":1783973241636,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"voh4Dv5hlkyFqea1","name":"Descriptor 3","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"I have learned to face monsters and aberrations without being intimidated. The Beast is on my trail because, having tasted my flesh, it can no longer do without it…","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 4.","positive":"I have learned to face monsters and aberrations without being intimidated. The Beast is on my trail because, having tasted my flesh, it can no longer do without it…","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241636,"modifiedTime":1783973241636,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"w3wtU6GHaC3Am1te","name":"Dark Ego Descriptor","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"I am a man of the world and nothing can really surprise me anymore. I never question myself. After all, I’m the best at what I do.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 4.","positive":"I am a man of the world and nothing can really surprise me anymore. I never question myself. After all, I’m the best at what I do.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241636,"modifiedTime":1783973241636,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"MYixdaMasYytbl8M","name":"With a Sword or a Smile","type":"gift","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/icon-gift.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"Once per Scene you may perform a gesture of extreme precision with your weapon, such as slipping an object off someone or writing something on a surface. The person observing your skill will either be impressed or intimidated, depending on the Storyteller’s decision. You receive 1 Additional Success when you use the emotion you have aroused to your advantage.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 4.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241636,"modifiedTime":1783973241636,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"n3OPAa2woT0r4kmA","name":"Tick-Tock, Here Comes The Beast","type":"gift","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/icon-gift.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"While outdoors, you may ask the Storyteller for the Beast to come in search of your flesh. The Beast is a monstrous NPC with the following characteristics: OL Hard 7 – (4 Wounds).\n\nDescriptor (the Beast): I am a great and mighty beast. I overwhelm everything I come across on my way to snatch my prey.\n\nGift – Ravenous Madness: The Beast has an insane craving for your flesh, and will unleash its rage on anyone standing in its way. With its titanic strength, it can tear down trees and walls, and hurl a man away with a single swipe of its huge paws. The Beast is also quite stupid and will leave the Scene as soon as you are out of sight. You receive 2 Additional Successes to any Defense Check against it. If the Beast suffers the fourth Wound, it will dissolve. However, it will regenerate and can be used in the next Scene.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 4.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241636,"modifiedTime":1783973241636,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"jQ8Bs3Pn0a1yJY64","name":"Dark Ego - I Will Have My Satisfaction","type":"darkEgo","img":"icons/svg/terror.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"When you choose an opponent, there is no escape for them. Once per Scene, you can take an additional action against the target of your challenge (even if you had already acted during this Exchange) to anticipate their move and stop their action with yours. If an opponent inflicts a Wound on you, you savor the taste of the challenge and receive 1 Additional Success at each Check against them for the rest of the Scenario.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 4.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0,"trigger":"You challenge an enemy or otherwise make clear who and how skilled you are."},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241636,"modifiedTime":1783973241636,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"7b5zj6diCyIqRCxz","name":"A fine dueling blade","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"A fine dueling blade","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 4.","quantity":1},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241636,"modifiedTime":1783973241636,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"jRoEKUjsTbXHVqDe","name":"a black powder gun","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"a black powder gun","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 4.","quantity":1},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241636,"modifiedTime":1783973241636,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"9btiuzzEaOQFQfRC","name":"a finely crafted hook","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"a finely crafted hook","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 4.","quantity":1},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241637,"modifiedTime":1783973241637,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"uOg5YKmgcQ2H5pA7","name":"a purple-red cloak","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"a purple-red cloak","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 4.","quantity":1},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241637,"modifiedTime":1783973241637,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"zTLzCH8dRlSjfAdg","name":"traveling boots","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"traveling boots","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 4.","quantity":1},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241637,"modifiedTime":1783973241637,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"7qVpBt9511Yf2kTr","name":"a precious pair of binoculars","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"a precious pair of binoculars","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 4.","quantity":1},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241637,"modifiedTime":1783973241637,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"rsnVlbomcSuf5IEn","name":"several valuable rings","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"several valuable rings","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 4.","quantity":1},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241637,"modifiedTime":1783973241637,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"1iA7CrDYeOQBfIUT","name":"Source Sheet","type":"storyElement","img":"icons/svg/scroll.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"<p><strong>Core Book</strong></p><p>bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 4.</p>","notes":"bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 4"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241637,"modifiedTime":1783973241637,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}],"effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"pregenSlug":"core-book-james-the-swordsman","pregenCollection":"Core Book","source":"bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf","pages":"4"}},"system":{"details":{"concept":"Core Book","origin":"James the Swordsman","role":"Hunter of the Order","notes":"I have been a lot of things in my life: ship captain, duellist of great renown, and lover of the most beautiful noblewomen. After years of successes and victories, a mysterious child defeated me with deception. This despicable boy led me into the lair of a dangerous beast and, after imprisoning me, left me to be eaten by the monster. I survived, though I lost a hand... I know for certain he who I seek is no human, and I joined the Order to hunt down the child I hate above all else, and thus have my revenge."},"resources":{"soma":{"value":7,"max":7},"xp":0,"wounds":{"value":0,"max":3},"darkness":{"value":0,"max":6}},"opposition":{"defaultLevel":5,"modifier":0},"bookmark":{"wound1":"","wound2":"","wound3":"","extraWound":""}},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241637,"modifiedTime":1783973241637,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"PbUHEd7k5B71k7TB","name":"Garou the Old Wolf","type":"hunter","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/avatars/pregens/core-book-garou-the-old-wolf.png","items":[{"_id":"swezn8BMBBnIZThV","name":"Descriptor 1","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"I am a mountain wolf and far more cunning than the stupid villagers who tremble at the mere sight of me. I have lived proudly at the head of my pack, leading a thousand raids and eating succulent, tender morsels of human flesh. But I am not so old I cannot face those who hate me the most, though I may be hunted and reviled. Now that I’m part of the Order, I use my strength to defend the weak hunters who are my companions, knowing that with a single bite I could end their insignificant lives.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 6.","positive":"I am a mountain wolf and far more cunning than the stupid villagers who tremble at the mere sight of me. I have lived proudly at the head of my pack, leading a thousand raids and eating succulent, tender morsels of human flesh. But I am not so old I cannot face those who hate me the most, though I may be hunted and reviled. Now that I’m part of the Order, I use my strength to defend the weak hunters who are my companions, knowing that with a single bite I could end their insignificant lives.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241637,"modifiedTime":1783973241637,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"pfHYMfOaq00NjZ8J","name":"Descriptor 2","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"My senses are unfailing. Nothing can escape my sense of smell and that is why the Order uses me as a guardian. I hate strong smells and loud noises because they feel like burning irons to acute senses.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 6.","positive":"My senses are unfailing. Nothing can escape my sense of smell and that is why the Order uses me as a guardian. I hate strong smells and loud noises because they feel like burning irons to acute senses.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241637,"modifiedTime":1783973241637,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"UtFN1p2V3bBjvLMe","name":"Descriptor 3","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"A true predator knows how to appear as the most helpless of lambs. I know how to disguise myself. My confidence is boundless and I often tend to underestimate danger, ready to risk anything for a tasty bite.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 6.","positive":"A true predator knows how to appear as the most helpless of lambs. I know how to disguise myself. My confidence is boundless and I often tend to underestimate danger, ready to risk anything for a tasty bite.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241637,"modifiedTime":1783973241637,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"khTJtje3L5vNVALW","name":"Dark Ego Descriptor","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"I am fiercer and more powerful than any human and my fangs can pierce even metal. My proud wolf spirit is everything to me.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 6.","positive":"I am fiercer and more powerful than any human and my fangs can pierce even metal. My proud wolf spirit is everything to me.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241637,"modifiedTime":1783973241637,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"JB6guX7xUoG9SIQT","name":"Find Them Forever After","type":"gift","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/icon-gift.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"Once you catch someone’s scent, you never forget it. During a Scene, you can spend 1 Soma to memorize the scent of a person you are interacting with. You will always recognize it and it will be easy for you to follow its traces even after some time. If you concentrate, you can hear a noise even at great distances. When someone approaches you, the Storyteller will warn you long before anyone else in the Scene would notice.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 6.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241637,"modifiedTime":1783973241637,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"HG71as6x89jNnY8v","name":"Wolf Among the Lambs","type":"gift","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/icon-gift.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"You may spend 1 Soma to assume the shape of a common human. Create a Descriptor that represents you and includes at least one of these words: Old, Helpless, Weak. In your human form you can speak and act without problems, but, as soon as you use your Dark Ego, you will immediately lose the effect of Wolf Among the Lambs. You receive 1 Additional Success when you use the Descriptor you created to deceive someone and catch them off guard.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 6.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241637,"modifiedTime":1783973241637,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"yzG7ReEiGvukOZac","name":"Dark Ego - The Big Bad Wolf","type":"darkEgo","img":"icons/svg/terror.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"You are hardened by a lifetime in the great mountains and your skill is matched only by your courage. When you unleash your rage, create a Descriptor for it that includes at least one of these words: Strong, Fierce, Unstoppable. You can employ the strength of three men, gnaw through stone as easily as flesh, or break down any barrier. When you act using this special Descriptor for Position Checks, you get 1 Additional Success. Once per Scene, you can unleash your rage and receive 3 Additional Successes instead of 1.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 6.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0,"trigger":"You assume the form of a Wolf or reveal yourself for what you really are, scaring off weak humans."},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241637,"modifiedTime":1783973241637,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"S7QdHzjDvLSdrUxK","name":"Fangs and claws (natural weapons)","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"Fangs and claws (natural weapons)","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 6.","quantity":1},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241637,"modifiedTime":1783973241637,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"OZ2YJLQLRIGHMzUZ","name":"a necklace of stones and wood that I carry in a paw—token of the only human I do not consider food","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"a necklace of stones and wood that I carry in a paw—token of the only human I do not consider food","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 6.","quantity":1},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241637,"modifiedTime":1783973241637,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"NoQ4edZFAfc3MrkF","name":"knick-knacks, keys, and other junk that I sometimes vomit up from my large stomach","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"knick-knacks, keys, and other junk that I sometimes vomit up from my large stomach","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 6.","quantity":1},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241637,"modifiedTime":1783973241637,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"Oji0UJEJxlSLwzIt","name":"Source Sheet","type":"storyElement","img":"icons/svg/scroll.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"<p><strong>Core Book</strong></p><p>bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 6.</p>","notes":"bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 6"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241637,"modifiedTime":1783973241637,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}],"effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"pregenSlug":"core-book-garou-the-old-wolf","pregenCollection":"Core Book","source":"bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf","pages":"6"}},"system":{"details":{"concept":"Core Book","origin":"Garou the Old Wolf","role":"Hunter of the Order","notes":"I am a mountain wolf and far more cunning than the stupid villagers who tremble at the mere sight of me. I have lived proudly at the head of my pack, leading a thousand raids and eating succulent, tender morsels of human flesh. But I am not so old I cannot face those who hate me the most, though I may be hunted and reviled. Now that I’m part of the Order, I use my strength to defend the weak hunters who are my companions, knowing that with a single bite I could end their insignificant lives."},"resources":{"soma":{"value":6,"max":6},"xp":0,"wounds":{"value":0,"max":3},"darkness":{"value":0,"max":6}},"opposition":{"defaultLevel":5,"modifier":0},"bookmark":{"wound1":"","wound2":"","wound3":"","extraWound":""}},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241637,"modifiedTime":1783973241637,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"81ZD8w9cdOxjx8yE","name":"The Astonishing Pied Piper Without a Name","type":"hunter","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/avatars/pregens/core-book-the-astonishing-pied-piper-without-a-name.png","items":[{"_id":"YOrMShr5kOrjAmNq","name":"Descriptor 1","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"I have always made my art my reason for living. I can play so skillfully that it might as well be magic. I have learned to use the power of music to reach into the souls of both humans and animals. Unfortunately, I have lost count of the number of times I have performed dishonorable acts while pursuing the perfect melody. Having been guilty of various crimes and having taken revenge on those who mocked my sincere love for music, I serenely waited for my execution. The Order freed me in exchange for a promise to serve them and put my skills to work in the fight against Darkness. It was in the darkest moments that I glimpsed the perfect melody, so perhaps as a Hunter, I can find it and make it my own.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 8.","positive":"I have always made my art my reason for living. I can play so skillfully that it might as well be magic. I have learned to use the power of music to reach into the souls of both humans and animals. Unfortunately, I have lost count of the number of times I have performed dishonorable acts while pursuing the perfect melody. Having been guilty of various crimes and having taken revenge on those who mocked my sincere love for music, I serenely waited for my execution. The Order freed me in exchange for a promise to serve them and put my skills to work in the fight against Darkness. It was in the darkest moments that I glimpsed the perfect melody, so perhaps as a Hunter, I can find it and make it my own.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241637,"modifiedTime":1783973241637,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"CD4xvppWZDR7UOmP","name":"Descriptor 2","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"With my pipe I can play any melody and touch the hearts of living beings. Art needs time to express itself.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 8.","positive":"With my pipe I can play any melody and touch the hearts of living beings. Art needs time to express itself.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241637,"modifiedTime":1783973241637,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"vNRlSVZvG5vwJ74V","name":"Descriptor 3","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"I am a skilled acrobat and musician. My talent is unrivaled and the Order has chosen me for my ability to capture people’s attention and stimulate their emotions. When I am in the grip of artistic inspiration, I am totally divorced from reality.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 8.","positive":"I am a skilled acrobat and musician. My talent is unrivaled and the Order has chosen me for my ability to capture people’s attention and stimulate their emotions. When I am in the grip of artistic inspiration, I am totally divorced from reality.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241637,"modifiedTime":1783973241637,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"xfJfFQfgk4rqz3Nn","name":"Dark Ego Descriptor","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"As an artist I have traveled to many places and I know many myths and legends. I’m hungry for knowledge and I’m fascinated by everything I don’t know.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 8.","positive":"As an artist I have traveled to many places and I know many myths and legends. I’m hungry for knowledge and I’m fascinated by everything I don’t know.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241637,"modifiedTime":1783973241637,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"XOlzRBIW7s5J7296","name":"Soul Music","type":"gift","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/icon-gift.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"When you play your pipes you can spend 1 Soma to sing a special melody. Choose from:\n1. Imparting an emotion: Create a Descriptor that represents the emotional state you wish to convey. Everybody present will receive that Descriptor for the current Scene. You may have to make a Position Check to affect opponents.\n2. Bewitching animals: You may give simple commands to animals that hear your melody. If they show an aggressive attitude, you have to make a successful Position Check for your melody to take effect. As long as you are playing, you may ask the animals to do simple actions such as moving or following a simple command.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 8.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241637,"modifiedTime":1783973241637,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"dVrNSOWqzTn3oRT8","name":"Skilled Acrobat","type":"gift","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/icon-gift.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"When you sing, dance, or move with grace, you always put on a great show. As an additional action, you can spend 1 Soma and decide on one of the following effects:\n1. You can make an incredible leap, many feet high, without anyone being able to stop you.\n2. You may take an object, even if it is worn by an enemy.\n3. You can perform a minor action with a stunt, such as opening a door or flipping a switch, and then return exactly to where you started.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 8.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241637,"modifiedTime":1783973241637,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"KRxcTnlxBVDV6D3f","name":"Dark Ego - The Power of Music","type":"darkEgo","img":"icons/svg/terror.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"Once per Scene, you can make a sound that can be heard by whomever you wish, even from a great distance. Everyone who hears it suffers 1 Wound, fragile objects break, and frightened animals flee. Alternatively, you can play a gentle melody and the wind itself will obey you, carrying your message to whomever you wish, wherever they are. When using The Power of Music, you can also activate a Soul Music effect on one or more targets of your choice.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 8.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0,"trigger":"Demonstrate your art to its fullest extent, with a show that cannot be ignored."},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241637,"modifiedTime":1783973241637,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"Irhx6r5cbTOakDwx","name":"A precious pipe of the finest workmanship","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"A precious pipe of the finest workmanship","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 8.","quantity":1},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241638,"modifiedTime":1783973241638,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"HM6wxp4dNq9cBVvC","name":"a theater mask","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"a theater mask","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 8.","quantity":1},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241638,"modifiedTime":1783973241638,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"gAlfINBNTIWK7HUb","name":"a cloak of many colors","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"a cloak of many colors","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 8.","quantity":1},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241638,"modifiedTime":1783973241638,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"dmhV0hInzrQMRt47","name":"multicolored chalks and powders","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"multicolored chalks and powders","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 8.","quantity":1},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241638,"modifiedTime":1783973241638,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"ctc9uoGaCdXqHyxD","name":"an old ocarina (the first instrument I ever played), and Hamelin","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"an old ocarina (the first instrument I ever played), and Hamelin","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 8.","quantity":1},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241638,"modifiedTime":1783973241638,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"RzBFK54xqCloBKIn","name":"my faithful trained mouse","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"my faithful trained mouse","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 8.","quantity":1},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241638,"modifiedTime":1783973241638,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"CvaK8tuXmB3On7Xo","name":"Source Sheet","type":"storyElement","img":"icons/svg/scroll.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"<p><strong>Core Book</strong></p><p>bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 8.</p>","notes":"bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 8"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241638,"modifiedTime":1783973241638,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}],"effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"pregenSlug":"core-book-the-astonishing-pied-piper-without-a-name","pregenCollection":"Core Book","source":"bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf","pages":"8"}},"system":{"details":{"concept":"Core Book","origin":"The Astonishing Pied Piper Without a Name","role":"Hunter of the Order","notes":"I have always made my art my reason for living. I can play so skillfully that it might as well be magic. I have learned to use the power of music to reach into the souls of both humans and animals. Unfortunately, I have lost count of the number of times I have performed dishonorable acts while pursuing the perfect melody. Having been guilty of various crimes and having taken revenge on those who mocked my sincere love for music, I serenely waited for my execution. The Order freed me in exchange for a promise to serve them and put my skills to work in the fight against Darkness. It was in the darkest moments that I glimpsed the perfect melody, so perhaps as a Hunter, I can find it and make it my own."},"resources":{"soma":{"value":5,"max":5},"xp":0,"wounds":{"value":0,"max":3},"darkness":{"value":0,"max":6}},"opposition":{"defaultLevel":5,"modifier":0},"bookmark":{"wound1":"","wound2":"","wound3":"","extraWound":""}},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241638,"modifiedTime":1783973241638,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"GvHlehXezileafN9","name":"Baba yaga The Child Witch","type":"hunter","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/avatars/pregens/core-book-baba-yaga-the-child-witch.png","items":[{"_id":"QpTgAgFaNGEu82d0","name":"Descriptor 1","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"I am a child witch, and my power is equal only to my ambition. I did not have a childhood, for I was born already aware of my abilities. To most, I seem cynical and cruel. That is because they do not understand that they are pawns, insignificant pieces in the bloody games that witches and warlocks play. The Order does not look down on my age, which is why it has given me the leadership I deserve.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 10.","positive":"I am a child witch, and my power is equal only to my ambition. I did not have a childhood, for I was born already aware of my abilities. To most, I seem cynical and cruel. That is because they do not understand that they are pawns, insignificant pieces in the bloody games that witches and warlocks play. The Order does not look down on my age, which is why it has given me the leadership I deserve.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241638,"modifiedTime":1783973241638,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"jO3YDCjtoFzjk3Y0","name":"Descriptor 2","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"I am a sorceress and my magical powers allow me to do whatever I want. I need the right amount of time to cast my spells.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 10.","positive":"I am a sorceress and my magical powers allow me to do whatever I want. I need the right amount of time to cast my spells.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241638,"modifiedTime":1783973241638,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"9mSUrCOOFkerpgAQ","name":"Descriptor 3","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"I am very skilled at reading people, that is why the Order has chosen me as leader of the Hunters. I love manipulating people and I often do it merely to amuse myself.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 10.","positive":"I am very skilled at reading people, that is why the Order has chosen me as leader of the Hunters. I love manipulating people and I often do it merely to amuse myself.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241638,"modifiedTime":1783973241638,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"4gjBRl2T22GV3iMC","name":"Dark Ego Descriptor","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"Like any respectable sorceress, I carry my trusty bag full of herbs, poisons, and all kinds of magic tools. My childlike appearance is often useful, but sometimes it leads others to underestimate me. I hate that.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 10.","positive":"Like any respectable sorceress, I carry my trusty bag full of herbs, poisons, and all kinds of magic tools. My childlike appearance is often useful, but sometimes it leads others to underestimate me. I hate that.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241638,"modifiedTime":1783973241638,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"59GJpsdUTP17NYKJ","name":"Magic","type":"gift","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/icon-gift.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"When you want to achieve something, you may use witchcraft. Choose what you want with a sentence like: I want to fly on that old broom, or I want to look like a demon in the eyes of those fools. Your spell must be focused on an object in your possession, such as a broom to fly or a mask you can wear to look like a demon. Pay a cost from 0 to 2 Soma, decided by the Storyteller, to activate your spell for the duration of a Scene. Remember that you can’t ask for someone’s sudden death, but you can inflict Wounds with your actions through magic.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 10.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241638,"modifiedTime":1783973241638,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"27yYZcpuEIgUvZiZ","name":"Listen to my Words","type":"gift","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/icon-gift.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"Once per Scene, when you talk to someone, you can ask the Storyteller a question about them. The question must be regarding their behaviour, such as any vices or their desires they might have. You gain 1 Additional Success in any action where you exploit what you’ve discovered.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 10.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241638,"modifiedTime":1783973241638,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"sOM18jLiBg4qlrD5","name":"Dark Ego - The Evil Witch","type":"darkEgo","img":"icons/svg/terror.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"Receive 1 Additional Success on any Check when you use one of your spells, either through the Magic Gift or by inserting it into your narrative through the Descriptors. Moreover, you can unleash your evil aura to gain one or more of the following effects:\n1. Animals and ordinary people are tormented by your presence and will flee in terror.\n2. You gain 1 Additional Success if you use your magic to punish someone for breaking a promise or agreement you made earlier.\n3. In the area around you, you can summon daylight or darkness.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 10.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0,"trigger":"Scare ordinary people or dispense punishment through your magic."},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241638,"modifiedTime":1783973241638,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"NjAGtq8vlONgvPHA","name":"An old and worn-out black cloak","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"An old and worn-out black cloak","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 10.","quantity":1},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241638,"modifiedTime":1783973241638,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"YwZrsYB67QscAl3u","name":"a bag of magical ingredients","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"a bag of magical ingredients","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 10.","quantity":1},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241638,"modifiedTime":1783973241638,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"OVEvcHvIngQVeSAj","name":"a small curved dagger","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"a small curved dagger","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 10.","quantity":1},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241638,"modifiedTime":1783973241638,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"hoYEyIrpu2kEbpt9","name":"a rag doll","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"a rag doll","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 10.","quantity":1},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241638,"modifiedTime":1783973241638,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"O40QDjrmaPL4j2B2","name":"the Ring of the Order","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"the Ring of the Order","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 10.","quantity":1},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241638,"modifiedTime":1783973241638,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"R7Bnu9rWcJCZZfRJ","name":"a lucky elderberry branch","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"a lucky elderberry branch","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 10.","quantity":1},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241638,"modifiedTime":1783973241638,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"QnYK8fSToDMGjWvc","name":"the keys of a strange hut in a tree which is always in my vicinity","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"the keys of a strange hut in a tree which is always in my vicinity","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 10.","quantity":1},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241638,"modifiedTime":1783973241638,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"Qt7vYBSEbQf8Aso5","name":"Source Sheet","type":"storyElement","img":"icons/svg/scroll.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"<p><strong>Core Book</strong></p><p>bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 10.</p>","notes":"bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 10"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241638,"modifiedTime":1783973241638,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}],"effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"pregenSlug":"core-book-baba-yaga-the-child-witch","pregenCollection":"Core Book","source":"bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf","pages":"10"}},"system":{"details":{"concept":"Core Book","origin":"Baba yaga The Child Witch","role":"Hunter of the Order","notes":"I am a child witch, and my power is equal only to my ambition. I did not have a childhood, for I was born already aware of my abilities. To most, I seem cynical and cruel. That is because they do not understand that they are pawns, insignificant pieces in the bloody games that witches and warlocks play. The Order does not look down on my age, which is why it has given me the leadership I deserve."},"resources":{"soma":{"value":5,"max":5},"xp":0,"wounds":{"value":0,"max":3},"darkness":{"value":0,"max":6}},"opposition":{"defaultLevel":5,"modifier":0},"bookmark":{"wound1":"","wound2":"","wound3":"","extraWound":""}},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241638,"modifiedTime":1783973241638,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"3k5iyzmyl7bCNYjJ","name":"Regina The Thief Of Hearts","type":"hunter","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/avatars/pregens/core-book-regina-the-thief-of-hearts.png","items":[{"_id":"Q7ODOGHT5IRSzWeQ","name":"Descriptor 1","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"I was born to be a leader and I have always surrounded myself with faithful followers ready to satisfy my every whim. Lacking the benefit of noble birth, the power I held was pried from the hands of those less deserving to wield it, no matter the cost. I ruled armies of thugs, and broke the hearts of both men and women. After each conquest, I set out in search of a bigger challenge. Because there is still so much out there that should be rightfully mine, I always want more. The Order has given me a new purpose, a new perspective, and new creatures to enslave.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 12.","positive":"I was born to be a leader and I have always surrounded myself with faithful followers ready to satisfy my every whim. Lacking the benefit of noble birth, the power I held was pried from the hands of those less deserving to wield it, no matter the cost. I ruled armies of thugs, and broke the hearts of both men and women. After each conquest, I set out in search of a bigger challenge. Because there is still so much out there that should be rightfully mine, I always want more. The Order has given me a new purpose, a new perspective, and new creatures to enslave.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241638,"modifiedTime":1783973241638,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"7T6bK3BsEyh5DGbT","name":"Descriptor 2","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"I am determined to get what I want, and nothing will get in my way. I will kill, humiliate, or conquer anything that stands between me and my objective. As you can imagine, I sincerely hate being told no!","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 12.","positive":"I am determined to get what I want, and nothing will get in my way. I will kill, humiliate, or conquer anything that stands between me and my objective. As you can imagine, I sincerely hate being told no!","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241639,"modifiedTime":1783973241639,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"MHmRt7uCCq7HGsC8","name":"Descriptor 3","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"Thanks to my contacts and charisma, I always have an ace up my sleeve: followers ready to help me and allies who owe me favors. Maintaining an empire of beneficial connections requires commitment and resources.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 12.","positive":"Thanks to my contacts and charisma, I always have an ace up my sleeve: followers ready to help me and allies who owe me favors. Maintaining an empire of beneficial connections requires commitment and resources.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241639,"modifiedTime":1783973241639,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"4Sl56nxGWNNjFFAP","name":"Dark Ego Descriptor","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"I have an enviable charm and love to dress up to fit the role I have chosen. Even when I try to restrain myself, I never go unnoticed.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 12.","positive":"I have an enviable charm and love to dress up to fit the role I have chosen. Even when I try to restrain myself, I never go unnoticed.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241639,"modifiedTime":1783973241639,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"KddcDJJ0yAaururL","name":"I Want It!","type":"gift","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/icon-gift.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"When you act with clear and direct intention to achieve an objective, you get 1 Additional Success on each Position Check. Once per Session, you can turn a Failure into an Outcome with Increment. Describe how you grit your teeth and fight to get what you want.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 12.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241639,"modifiedTime":1783973241639,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"MHJv5ETZx5P4d9h3","name":"The Queen","type":"gift","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/icon-gift.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"During a Scene you always have a couple of trusted servants with you, ready to execute your every order. Create a Descriptor for each, which represents the skill for which you hold them in your service. Your servants will do their best to satisfy your every wish. Decide how you pay them. The Storyteller, when and if they deem it necessary, will ask you to honor their services so as not to lose the use of this Gift for the rest of the Scene. You can check this Descriptor multiple times to get XP.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 12.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241639,"modifiedTime":1783973241639,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"Yj3qklCqD7TTrdF2","name":"Dark Ego - As I Want!","type":"darkEgo","img":"icons/svg/terror.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"You know that your way is the only right way to do things. During the Scene, as an additional action, you can choose another character who will be issued a command. In the case of an ally, if they do exactly what you tell them, they will receive 1 Additional Success to their action or increase their Opposition Level by 1. If you give a peremptory order to ensnare an enemy, they will lower their Opposition Level by 1 or, if you’ve already seen it in action, you can prevent them from using one of their Gifts. Once per Scene, you can shout, drawing everyone’s attention to you. For a few moments, they will pause to listen to what you have to say.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 12.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0,"trigger":"Take control of a situation and impose your decisions by dramatically drawing attention to yourself."},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241639,"modifiedTime":1783973241639,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"PZ7ttUGkz4mugl9l","name":"A long leather whip with metal studs and spikes","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"A long leather whip with metal studs and spikes","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 12.","quantity":1},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241639,"modifiedTime":1783973241639,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"sqvhbPswI7EO2FGs","name":"a beautiful fan to hide my face, dresses for every occasion","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"a beautiful fan to hide my face, dresses for every occasion","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 12.","quantity":1},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241639,"modifiedTime":1783973241639,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"SSAfiLsWRWW8agap","name":"a long burgundy cape, gold and jewels gifted by countless suitors","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"a long burgundy cape, gold and jewels gifted by countless suitors","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 12.","quantity":1},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241639,"modifiedTime":1783973241639,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"OKYlFOmABR7C0JQ3","name":"a sharp stiletto I wear as a hairpin","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"a sharp stiletto I wear as a hairpin","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 12.","quantity":1},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241639,"modifiedTime":1783973241639,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"BNohnnLAsZdW76dA","name":"Source Sheet","type":"storyElement","img":"icons/svg/scroll.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"<p><strong>Core Book</strong></p><p>bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 12.</p>","notes":"bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 12"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241639,"modifiedTime":1783973241639,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}],"effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"pregenSlug":"core-book-regina-the-thief-of-hearts","pregenCollection":"Core Book","source":"bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf","pages":"12"}},"system":{"details":{"concept":"Core Book","origin":"Regina The Thief Of Hearts","role":"Hunter of the Order","notes":"I was born to be a leader and I have always surrounded myself with faithful followers ready to satisfy my every whim. Lacking the benefit of noble birth, the power I held was pried from the hands of those less deserving to wield it, no matter the cost. I ruled armies of thugs, and broke the hearts of both men and women. After each conquest, I set out in search of a bigger challenge. Because there is still so much out there that should be rightfully mine, I always want more. The Order has given me a new purpose, a new perspective, and new creatures to enslave."},"resources":{"soma":{"value":6,"max":6},"xp":0,"wounds":{"value":0,"max":3},"darkness":{"value":0,"max":6}},"opposition":{"defaultLevel":5,"modifier":0},"bookmark":{"wound1":"","wound2":"","wound3":"","extraWound":""}},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241639,"modifiedTime":1783973241639,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"3XHmTgOnu0l2B2DI","name":"Babai the Judge","type":"hunter","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/avatars/pregens/core-book-babai-the-judge.png","items":[{"_id":"SoKNyzb5zMqYFiuA","name":"Descriptor 1","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"After years of honorable service as State Inquisitor of the Republic of Venice, my body and spirit have undergone a rare mutation and fear is now unknown to me. People have always called me Bogeyman, fearing the justice that I represented. Perhaps my own absence of fear made me even more terrifying in the eyes of mortals. The Order has given me a new assignment because even in the fight against darkness, someone needs to be ready to judge what is right and what is wrong.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 14.","positive":"After years of honorable service as State Inquisitor of the Republic of Venice, my body and spirit have undergone a rare mutation and fear is now unknown to me. People have always called me Bogeyman, fearing the justice that I represented. Perhaps my own absence of fear made me even more terrifying in the eyes of mortals. The Order has given me a new assignment because even in the fight against darkness, someone needs to be ready to judge what is right and what is wrong.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241639,"modifiedTime":1783973241639,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"FIuZgXjddFAhDEk4","name":"Descriptor 2","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"I am good at understanding, evaluating, and grasping every hidden detail, which is why the Order wanted me as a judge. I am cold, methodical, and cannot stand when plans change abruptly.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 14.","positive":"I am good at understanding, evaluating, and grasping every hidden detail, which is why the Order wanted me as a judge. I am cold, methodical, and cannot stand when plans change abruptly.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241639,"modifiedTime":1783973241639,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"9RlXXxhn8ePao4aj","name":"Descriptor 3","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"My body is made of pure shadow and I can become intangible for brief moments. I hate sunlight and cannot properly focus when not surrounded by a comforting shadow.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 14.","positive":"My body is made of pure shadow and I can become intangible for brief moments. I hate sunlight and cannot properly focus when not surrounded by a comforting shadow.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241639,"modifiedTime":1783973241639,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"L7O1ezrIll3E195s","name":"Dark Ego Descriptor","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"My presence intimidates people, touching the fear that dwells deep in their hearts. The presence of children and their innocent way of looking at the world makes me uneasy.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 14.","positive":"My presence intimidates people, touching the fear that dwells deep in their hearts. The presence of children and their innocent way of looking at the world makes me uneasy.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241639,"modifiedTime":1783973241639,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"QBOzxGhLPTdMOX5u","name":"Eye of the Judge","type":"gift","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/icon-gift.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"Once per Scene, when you meet a group of NPCs you will immediately understand who is the most and the least capable of them. Moreover, the Storyteller will also reveal to you if there are relationships such as love, hate, or fidelity between two NPCs of your choice. Receive 1 Additional Success when you use the information you have discovered to intimidate or question someone.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 14.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241639,"modifiedTime":1783973241639,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"bAWGlf21l1YlRfsv","name":"Like a Shadow","type":"gift","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/icon-gift.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"You can spend 1 Soma to manipulate the shadows to your advantage, choose from:\n1. Acquire a small object, even if it is held by someone, as long as you can see it.\n2. Make an object in your immediate vicinity topple down.\n3. Stretch a shadow and manipulate its shape to make it look different.\nAdditionally, you always receive 1 Additional Success on any Defense Check you make while in a shaded area. If you get a successful Outcome, as an additional effect you can move from one shadow to another and no one can prevent it.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 14.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241639,"modifiedTime":1783973241639,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"aXMTnmPBva3b1m6F","name":"Dark Ego - If you don’t Stop, I’ll Call the Bogeyman!","type":"darkEgo","img":"icons/svg/terror.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"You are like a sinuous shadow that can reach anywhere. During a Scene, you can arrive at a location by covering any distance and overcoming any obstacle if one of your allies or an NPC calls your name. When you manifest your true nature, everyone who witnesses it will be frightened and will not act against you unless you threaten them first. The Storyteller may ask you for a Position Check to frighten particularly powerful characters. Receive 1 Additional Success on all Defense Checks you make against the actions of someone who is now fearful.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 14.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0,"trigger":"Enter or leave a shadow by manifesting your true nature and scaring someone."},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241639,"modifiedTime":1783973241639,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"36eWJOLz7xnyRQPM","name":"A precious elegant black dress","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"A precious elegant black dress","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 14.","quantity":1},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241639,"modifiedTime":1783973241639,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"1jKEbrATyLP0be1T","name":"a cape and a top hat","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"a cape and a top hat","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 14.","quantity":1},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241639,"modifiedTime":1783973241639,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"L21r0ykRu84rR2M7","name":"a sturdy cane with a hidden blade","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"a sturdy cane with a hidden blade","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 14.","quantity":1},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241639,"modifiedTime":1783973241639,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"IivoGD4kJL2vbplO","name":"a monocle lens","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"a monocle lens","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 14.","quantity":1},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241639,"modifiedTime":1783973241639,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"TlmRQ9tB7bW2fqPN","name":"an exquisitely crafted Larva (typical mask of the Venice Carnival)","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"an exquisitely crafted Larva (typical mask of the Venice Carnival)","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 14.","quantity":1},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241639,"modifiedTime":1783973241639,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"qNoW43jF9s5uTG3R","name":"an accurate pocket watch","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"an accurate pocket watch","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 14.","quantity":1},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241639,"modifiedTime":1783973241639,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"30q5lxFqmDtJP5hy","name":"Source Sheet","type":"storyElement","img":"icons/svg/scroll.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"<p><strong>Core Book</strong></p><p>bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 14.</p>","notes":"bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 14"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241639,"modifiedTime":1783973241639,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}],"effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"pregenSlug":"core-book-babai-the-judge","pregenCollection":"Core Book","source":"bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf","pages":"14"}},"system":{"details":{"concept":"Core Book","origin":"Babai the Judge","role":"Hunter of the Order","notes":"After years of honorable service as State Inquisitor of the Republic of Venice, my body and spirit have undergone a rare mutation and fear is now unknown to me. People have always called me Bogeyman, fearing the justice that I represented. Perhaps my own absence of fear made me even more terrifying in the eyes of mortals. The Order has given me a new assignment because even in the fight against darkness, someone needs to be ready to judge what is right and what is wrong."},"resources":{"soma":{"value":6,"max":6},"xp":0,"wounds":{"value":0,"max":3},"darkness":{"value":0,"max":6}},"opposition":{"defaultLevel":5,"modifier":0},"bookmark":{"wound1":"","wound2":"","wound3":"","extraWound":""}},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241639,"modifiedTime":1783973241639,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"q60PkmUrmX07umsK","name":"The Woman from the Woods","type":"hunter","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/avatars/pregens/core-book-the-woman-from-the-woods.png","items":[{"_id":"shuvUSV86jddAi4P","name":"Descriptor 1","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"My memory is gone. The first thing I remember is the Order finding me, wandering in the woods naked and covered in blood. I possess extraordinary strength and a feral instinct, such that any civilized society ought to chain me like a monster. I know that in my past is a sin so great, my memory could not bear the weight of it. But, I want to remember and perhaps by serving the Order I will be able to do so. I have a natural soft spot for children, and I can’t stand to see them get hurt. The Order uses me as a weapon in the most serious matters when it is necessary to act decisively and demonstrate that a Hunter is a force to be reckoned with.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 16.","positive":"My memory is gone. The first thing I remember is the Order finding me, wandering in the woods naked and covered in blood. I possess extraordinary strength and a feral instinct, such that any civilized society ought to chain me like a monster. I know that in my past is a sin so great, my memory could not bear the weight of it. But, I want to remember and perhaps by serving the Order I will be able to do so. I have a natural soft spot for children, and I can’t stand to see them get hurt. The Order uses me as a weapon in the most serious matters when it is necessary to act decisively and demonstrate that a Hunter is a force to be reckoned with.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241640,"modifiedTime":1783973241640,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"MLzMtN038mhIemBa","name":"Descriptor 2","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"I am incredibly strong. Despite my petite looks, I am tougher than the sturdiest of men. I struggle to control my strength and often end up damaging things unintentionally.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 16.","positive":"I am incredibly strong. Despite my petite looks, I am tougher than the sturdiest of men. I struggle to control my strength and often end up damaging things unintentionally.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241640,"modifiedTime":1783973241640,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"sZjlIKBPJPoWB4ir","name":"Descriptor 3","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"Sometimes I manifest strange abilities, the legacy of a past that I no longer remember. But, when I need it, the world around me shapes itself to protect and shelter me. I hate being out in the open and being the center of attention.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 16.","positive":"Sometimes I manifest strange abilities, the legacy of a past that I no longer remember. But, when I need it, the world around me shapes itself to protect and shelter me. I hate being out in the open and being the center of attention.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241640,"modifiedTime":1783973241640,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"plMcB5kxDsa4ji8c","name":"Dark Ego Descriptor","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"I love human flesh and can gain insight about people just looking at them. I am helplessly attracted to those who have a particular physical trait that stimulates my appetite, such as a good smell or velvety skin.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 16.","positive":"I love human flesh and can gain insight about people just looking at them. I am helplessly attracted to those who have a particular physical trait that stimulates my appetite, such as a good smell or velvety skin.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241640,"modifiedTime":1783973241640,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"BFu0Abboh5sASuQx","name":"The Woman from the Wood","type":"gift","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/icon-gift.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"You receive 1 Additional Success to any Position Check that requires you to resort to your strength. If you eliminate a living being by causing a Wound, you can do it in an extremely disturbing way. Anyone who witnesses it, at the discretion of the Storyteller, will lower their Opposition Level by 1 for the next action.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 16.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241640,"modifiedTime":1783973241640,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"BUr2574x41pMu0si","name":"Home Sweet Home","type":"gift","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/icon-gift.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"You can spend 1 Soma to draw on the strange powers of the witch you once were. When you do so, choose one of the following effects:\n1. Create a shelter for one person, perfectly camouflaged within the environment.\n2. Reshape a plant to create ladders, shields, or other simple structures.\n3. Make something disgusting/rotten edible and sweet, restoring 1 Wound to whoever eats it (except yourself).","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 16.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241640,"modifiedTime":1783973241640,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"TkRTHCVmZOal1SMf","name":"Dark Ego - Soft and Succulent Flesh","type":"darkEgo","img":"icons/svg/terror.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"The truth is that you crave human flesh, especially when raw and taken from evil people. When you inflict a Wound through violent action on someone you deem evil, and if you reach an Outcome with an Increment, you may inflict 1 additional Wound. Once per Scene when you consume human flesh, you recover 1 Wound and the Storyteller will reveal some memories of the victim, giving you contextualized information about what you are looking for.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 16.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0,"trigger":"Blatantly manifest your desire to devour human flesh, regardless of the consequences."},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241640,"modifiedTime":1783973241640,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"1vtgedVHLkC96L69","name":"A doll and a little wooden soldier — the only items I had with me when I was found. A worn-out gray travel dress stained with blood. A sharp butcher’s knife. A hair ribbon, gift from a Hunter of the Order. A cookbook filled with recipes for cakes and sweets","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"A doll and a little wooden soldier — the only items I had with me when I was found. A worn-out gray travel dress stained with blood. A sharp butcher’s knife. A hair ribbon, gift from a Hunter of the Order. A cookbook filled with recipes for cakes and sweets","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 16.","quantity":1},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241640,"modifiedTime":1783973241640,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"Ulmg1cSQyP9UOtuK","name":"Source Sheet","type":"storyElement","img":"icons/svg/scroll.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"<p><strong>Core Book</strong></p><p>bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 16.</p>","notes":"bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 16"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241640,"modifiedTime":1783973241640,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}],"effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"pregenSlug":"core-book-the-woman-from-the-woods","pregenCollection":"Core Book","source":"bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf","pages":"16"}},"system":{"details":{"concept":"Core Book","origin":"The Woman from the Woods","role":"Hunter of the Order","notes":"My memory is gone. The first thing I remember is the Order finding me, wandering in the woods naked and covered in blood. I possess extraordinary strength and a feral instinct, such that any civilized society ought to chain me like a monster. I know that in my past is a sin so great, my memory could not bear the weight of it. But, I want to remember and perhaps by serving the Order I will be able to do so. I have a natural soft spot for children, and I can’t stand to see them get hurt. The Order uses me as a weapon in the most serious matters when it is necessary to act decisively and demonstrate that a Hunter is a force to be reckoned with."},"resources":{"soma":{"value":6,"max":6},"xp":0,"wounds":{"value":0,"max":3},"darkness":{"value":0,"max":6}},"opposition":{"defaultLevel":5,"modifier":0},"bookmark":{"wound1":"","wound2":"","wound3":"","extraWound":""}},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241640,"modifiedTime":1783973241640,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"za41IlvlHuITYDR1","name":"TheImmortal","type":"hunter","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/avatars/pregens/core-book-theimmortal.png","items":[{"_id":"jISMZdV1lVDclFIY","name":"Descriptor 1","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"I am a sorcerer who has found the key to immortality. Long life has only whetted my appetite for power and in its pursuit, I have been stained by every sin. The secret behind my unending existence is that I have hidden my soul, removing it from my body. Unfortunately, the Order found its hiding place and now it is held beyond my reach in a fortified church, leaving me no choice but to submit to their commands. Guilty of one thousand and one crimes, the Order demands I balance each with one thousand and one acts of virtue. According to those foolish preachers, they are leading me down the path of redemption. In truth, the Order treats me as a servant, giving to me only the most thankless tasks, knowing that I can not be subdued by death. I remain humble and silent, waiting for the day when I will discover where they have hidden my soul. Then I will unleash my revenge and annihilate the entire Papacy...","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 18.","positive":"I am a sorcerer who has found the key to immortality. Long life has only whetted my appetite for power and in its pursuit, I have been stained by every sin. The secret behind my unending existence is that I have hidden my soul, removing it from my body. Unfortunately, the Order found its hiding place and now it is held beyond my reach in a fortified church, leaving me no choice but to submit to their commands. Guilty of one thousand and one crimes, the Order demands I balance each with one thousand and one acts of virtue. According to those foolish preachers, they are leading me down the path of redemption. In truth, the Order treats me as a servant, giving to me only the most thankless tasks, knowing that I can not be subdued by death. I remain humble and silent, waiting for the day when I will discover where they have hidden my soul. Then I will unleash my revenge and annihilate the entire Papacy...","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241640,"modifiedTime":1783973241640,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"NNbXx6HnyuKUUBnj","name":"Descriptor 2","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"I have knowledge and wisdom drawn from centuries of existence, which I can conjure to mind when needed. I often get lost in the memories of my past glories, forgetting about the world around me.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 18.","positive":"I have knowledge and wisdom drawn from centuries of existence, which I can conjure to mind when needed. I often get lost in the memories of my past glories, forgetting about the world around me.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241640,"modifiedTime":1783973241640,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"oIFu1Kyh9ZZtEqpn","name":"Descriptor 3","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"The Order uses my powers for their own purposes and I have had to become skilled at understanding and supporting the needs of my allies as a result. Although I hate to admit it, over time I have begun to take some pleasure in doing good deeds.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 18.","positive":"The Order uses my powers for their own purposes and I have had to become skilled at understanding and supporting the needs of my allies as a result. Although I hate to admit it, over time I have begun to take some pleasure in doing good deeds.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241640,"modifiedTime":1783973241640,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"ygOXscNR8AF8jgbt","name":"Dark Ego Descriptor","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"My body is but a tool which I can manipulate at will, far beyond common human limits. In spite of my old and emaciated appearance, I feel neither fatigue nor pain. With matters of the flesh no longer of concern, I value beautiful things and works of art above anything else.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 18.","positive":"My body is but a tool which I can manipulate at will, far beyond common human limits. In spite of my old and emaciated appearance, I feel neither fatigue nor pain. With matters of the flesh no longer of concern, I value beautiful things and works of art above anything else.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241640,"modifiedTime":1783973241640,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"t6uNsH4GstK3psDb","name":"Memories of an Infinite Life","type":"gift","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/icon-gift.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"You have been alive for an indefinite time and know almost everything. Once per Scene, you may ask for information about the past or a specific subject or place, which is only available to you due to your long history. The Storyteller will provide relevant and useful details. Once per Scene, you may also change the above Descriptor associated with this Gift to one that represents a skill you have conjured to your immortal mind. This new Descriptor is yours until the end of the Scene, and you receive 1 Additional Success the first time you use it for a Check.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 18.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241640,"modifiedTime":1783973241640,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"Xs9kKLGeRYIgV1z6","name":"The Servant","type":"gift","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/icon-gift.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"Once per Scene, as an additional action, you can grant 1 Additional Success to an ally’s action if you can narratively support them. You can also always spend your Soma to pay the activation cost of your allies’ Gifts.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 18.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241640,"modifiedTime":1783973241640,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"GKhCJlMmyOAwFbem","name":"Dark Ego - The Immortal","type":"darkEgo","img":"icons/svg/terror.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"When you suffer 1 Wound, you can immediately spend 1 Soma to remain conscious, allowing you to suffer many Wounds without dying. You are in full control of your body, even parts that have been cut off. You can see through a torn eye or continue to use your severed hand. At the end of the Scene in which you activated your Dark Ego, you recover all Wounds suffered except the first one. Your body regenerates and severed parts reattach in a horrific spectacle.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 18.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0,"trigger":"Use your indifference to pain or death to your advantage, revealing your true nature for anyone to see."},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241640,"modifiedTime":1783973241640,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"zWTNeERIGRtzpnwK","name":"Poor clothes","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"Poor clothes","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 18.","quantity":1},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241640,"modifiedTime":1783973241640,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"WhySEJnnDD0UlG1L","name":"a worn out sickle (reminder of times past)","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"a worn out sickle (reminder of times past)","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 18.","quantity":1},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241640,"modifiedTime":1783973241640,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"qnPcACLkwGsZ1yD9","name":"a small bag with precious items collected during adventures","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"a small bag with precious items collected during adventures","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 18.","quantity":1},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241640,"modifiedTime":1783973241640,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"y5674t6cMw1HPEZG","name":"a key that opens one of many secret refuges","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"a key that opens one of many secret refuges","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 18.","quantity":1},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241640,"modifiedTime":1783973241640,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"Vp2zZtUn94CbnFlj","name":"a papal ring as a symbol of indenture to the Church","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"a papal ring as a symbol of indenture to the Church","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 18.","quantity":1},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241640,"modifiedTime":1783973241640,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"b2kejfRXpUdubEwb","name":"a little toy given by someone helped with the first good deed","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"a little toy given by someone helped with the first good deed","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 18.","quantity":1},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241640,"modifiedTime":1783973241640,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"4fTfPjQFfu9zpAmE","name":"Source Sheet","type":"storyElement","img":"icons/svg/scroll.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"<p><strong>Core Book</strong></p><p>bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 18.</p>","notes":"bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 18"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241640,"modifiedTime":1783973241640,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}],"effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"pregenSlug":"core-book-theimmortal","pregenCollection":"Core Book","source":"bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf","pages":"18"}},"system":{"details":{"concept":"Core Book","origin":"TheImmortal","role":"Hunter of the Order","notes":"I am a sorcerer who has found the key to immortality. Long life has only whetted my appetite for power and in its pursuit, I have been stained by every sin. The secret behind my unending existence is that I have hidden my soul, removing it from my body. Unfortunately, the Order found its hiding place and now it is held beyond my reach in a fortified church, leaving me no choice but to submit to their commands. Guilty of one thousand and one crimes, the Order demands I balance each with one thousand and one acts of virtue. According to those foolish preachers, they are leading me down the path of redemption. In truth, the Order treats me as a servant, giving to me only the most thankless tasks, knowing that I can not be subdued by death. I remain humble and silent, waiting for the day when I will discover where they have hidden my soul. Then I will unleash my revenge and annihilate the entire Papacy..."},"resources":{"soma":{"value":7,"max":7},"xp":0,"wounds":{"value":0,"max":3},"darkness":{"value":0,"max":6}},"opposition":{"defaultLevel":5,"modifier":0},"bookmark":{"wound1":"","wound2":"","wound3":"","extraWound":""}},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241640,"modifiedTime":1783973241640,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"kyL3B6saQzGIVmt4","name":"Marina the Sea Explorer","type":"hunter","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/avatars/pregens/core-book-marina-the-sea-explorer.png","items":[{"_id":"ZVRIUMALsQ5LZksI","name":"Descriptor 1","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"I am a traveler, and, over the years, I have visited every location known to man. Being a traveling merchant has allowed me to easily hide my talents as a witch from prying eyes. Year after year, I have accumulated all kinds of magical and mundane wealth. But the Order found me and forced me to sign the most one-sided contract of my entire career as a trader. Now I must put my skills and my charisma at the service of the Order, trying to earn as much as possible to redeem the enormous debt that they have made me incur through deceit.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 20.","positive":"I am a traveler, and, over the years, I have visited every location known to man. Being a traveling merchant has allowed me to easily hide my talents as a witch from prying eyes. Year after year, I have accumulated all kinds of magical and mundane wealth. But the Order found me and forced me to sign the most one-sided contract of my entire career as a trader. Now I must put my skills and my charisma at the service of the Order, trying to earn as much as possible to redeem the enormous debt that they have made me incur through deceit.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241641,"modifiedTime":1783973241641,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"u6wEMSSvu2Dswkjb","name":"Descriptor 2","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"I am a sea witch, and as such, I have the power to shape water and move it at will. I hate enclosed places, cut off from the presence of my beloved sea.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 20.","positive":"I am a sea witch, and as such, I have the power to shape water and move it at will. I hate enclosed places, cut off from the presence of my beloved sea.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241641,"modifiedTime":1783973241641,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"sR0shGRyDLFeDv61","name":"Descriptor 3","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"Nobody knows my true form, which I hide under an appearance of eternal youth. I can change shape to some extent, while still remaining in human form. I am hopelessly attracted to all forms of beauty and I often get lost in contemplating it.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 20.","positive":"Nobody knows my true form, which I hide under an appearance of eternal youth. I can change shape to some extent, while still remaining in human form. I am hopelessly attracted to all forms of beauty and I often get lost in contemplating it.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241641,"modifiedTime":1783973241641,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"2hZ4nkOQm1FMczAH","name":"Dark Ego Descriptor","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"I have a massive collection of magical relics and treasures. I am very stingy with my collection and constantly seeking to add to my wealth so I can redeem my freedom.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 20.","positive":"I have a massive collection of magical relics and treasures. I am very stingy with my collection and constantly seeking to add to my wealth so I can redeem my freedom.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241641,"modifiedTime":1783973241641,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"GupGFKV1FnbEWxe9","name":"Sea Magic","type":"gift","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/icon-gift.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"You can unleash your witch powers and control seawater, manipulating it as if it were solid. You can use it as a weapon or as an object to support your actions, giving it the consistency of a whip that can reach up to thirty feet. When you act, you can take a second supporting action, such as picking up something, moving someone you want to defend, or hindering an enemy’s movement thanks to the water you manipulate. You can also use this Gift with fresh water, but you will need to spend 1 Soma to do so.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 20.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241641,"modifiedTime":1783973241641,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"3XBPXukzSpq7ztTN","name":"Mutable Appearance","type":"gift","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/icon-gift.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"Once per Scene you can change your appearance. Create a Descriptor that represents your new appearance. Nobody can pierce your deception, except through magical means or Gifts that allow one to discover the truth. In addition, you may spend 1 Soma to take the specific appearance of a person you have already met, mimicking their voice and manners as well. You can keep your new appearance until the Scene is over.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 20.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241641,"modifiedTime":1783973241641,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"QeEN1jC9jmbiDIWF","name":"Dark Ego - Treasures of the Sea","type":"darkEgo","img":"icons/svg/terror.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"At the beginning of the Scenario, you receive 2 Treasure Tokens. When you show off your Treasures, spend 1 Treasure Token and 1 Soma, and create a Descriptor that represents it such as Wolf-Slaying Dagger or Lens of Truth. Receive 1 Additional Success for any Check in which your Treasure may be helpful. Alternatively, spend 1 Token to draw a Potion from your pouch to give to someone. Create a Descriptor to represent its magical effect such as Seeing in the dark or Extraordinary strength. Whoever drinks it will be granted the Descriptor you created for 1 Scene, plus 1 Additional Success on the first action in which they use the advantage given by the potion. When you obtain a new treasure or close a favorable deal, you receive 1 Treasure Token.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 20.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0,"trigger":"Turn a request for help or a conversation into a negotiation, making it clear how amazing your treasures are."},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241641,"modifiedTime":1783973241641,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"qApqG6IWXBrTdqw6","name":"Exotic and colorful dresses","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"Exotic and colorful dresses","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 20.","quantity":1},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241641,"modifiedTime":1783973241641,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"CP6qvHLrZsQJkiPz","name":"a large bag full of treasures","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"a large bag full of treasures","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 20.","quantity":1},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241641,"modifiedTime":1783973241641,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"Emjm9UAFYAHqzL6O","name":"a travel bag","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"a travel bag","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 20.","quantity":1},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241641,"modifiedTime":1783973241641,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"W1mP65fQXaYQan5V","name":"rings and fine jewelry made out of seashells","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"rings and fine jewelry made out of seashells","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 20.","quantity":1},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241641,"modifiedTime":1783973241641,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"7pjPiemNDABvGPvA","name":"a vial of sea water","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"a vial of sea water","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 20.","quantity":1},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241641,"modifiedTime":1783973241641,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"2a7b7h7Qx0WCdynr","name":"cosmetics and perfumes","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"cosmetics and perfumes","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 20.","quantity":1},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241641,"modifiedTime":1783973241641,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"o1iukLILymozhmC3","name":"Source Sheet","type":"storyElement","img":"icons/svg/scroll.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"<p><strong>Core Book</strong></p><p>bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 20.</p>","notes":"bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 20"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241641,"modifiedTime":1783973241641,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}],"effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"pregenSlug":"core-book-marina-the-sea-explorer","pregenCollection":"Core Book","source":"bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf","pages":"20"}},"system":{"details":{"concept":"Core Book","origin":"Marina the Sea Explorer","role":"Hunter of the Order","notes":"I am a traveler, and, over the years, I have visited every location known to man. Being a traveling merchant has allowed me to easily hide my talents as a witch from prying eyes. Year after year, I have accumulated all kinds of magical and mundane wealth. But the Order found me and forced me to sign the most one-sided contract of my entire career as a trader. Now I must put my skills and my charisma at the service of the Order, trying to earn as much as possible to redeem the enormous debt that they have made me incur through deceit."},"resources":{"soma":{"value":6,"max":6},"xp":0,"wounds":{"value":0,"max":3},"darkness":{"value":0,"max":6}},"opposition":{"defaultLevel":5,"modifier":0},"bookmark":{"wound1":"","wound2":"","wound3":"","extraWound":""}},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241641,"modifiedTime":1783973241641,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"whJgabNRDwMRmcLY","name":"Niklaus von Krampus","type":"hunter","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/avatars/pregens/core-book-niklaus-von-krampus.png","items":[{"_id":"04xhCrcrobixW4N6","name":"Descriptor 1","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"I am a devoted clergyman who has always dedicated his life to helping others. Over the years I have become a talented exorcist and this vocation of mine led me to the remote village of Borgo Maleanime. There, I fought a particularly insidious demon, who concealed itself among the ranks of a gang of young thugs who merely pretended to be demons to scare people. It was a tough fight, but I finally got the better of the fiend. Or so I thought. Something in the exorcism did not go as expected and now the demon dwells inside me, sowing fear and pain whenever it re-emerges. The Order welcomed me into its ranks as an exorcist and I gladly accepted this role, with the hope that the missions entrusted to me would allow me to find a way to rid myself, once and for all, of that which hides within me.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 22.","positive":"I am a devoted clergyman who has always dedicated his life to helping others. Over the years I have become a talented exorcist and this vocation of mine led me to the remote village of Borgo Maleanime. There, I fought a particularly insidious demon, who concealed itself among the ranks of a gang of young thugs who merely pretended to be demons to scare people. It was a tough fight, but I finally got the better of the fiend. Or so I thought. Something in the exorcism did not go as expected and now the demon dwells inside me, sowing fear and pain whenever it re-emerges. The Order welcomed me into its ranks as an exorcist and I gladly accepted this role, with the hope that the missions entrusted to me would allow me to find a way to rid myself, once and for all, of that which hides within me.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241641,"modifiedTime":1783973241641,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"l68E99pdP9DGenIw","name":"Descriptor 2","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"I am a skilled exorcist. I know how to identify and fight evil through prayer and the sacred arts. Despite what I am, I hate holy places and manifestations of faith and religion, as they cause the demon inside me to stir.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 22.","positive":"I am a skilled exorcist. I know how to identify and fight evil through prayer and the sacred arts. Despite what I am, I hate holy places and manifestations of faith and religion, as they cause the demon inside me to stir.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241641,"modifiedTime":1783973241641,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"ci9rCgfmvvzwAd8f","name":"Descriptor 3","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"I am good at understanding people and helping them. Now, thanks to the demon that dwells in me, I can even perceive the dark side of people. Every so often, however, the demon takes over, making me behave strangely in front of ordinary people.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 22.","positive":"I am good at understanding people and helping them. Now, thanks to the demon that dwells in me, I can even perceive the dark side of people. Every so often, however, the demon takes over, making me behave strangely in front of ordinary people.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241641,"modifiedTime":1783973241641,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"Ivh0kypSdWvqLsHX","name":"Dark Ego Descriptor","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"The demon in me grants me its power, allowing me to act with savage strength and speed. It is not easy to contain this ferocity and, often, I end up hurting or destroying things I did not wish to.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 22.","positive":"The demon in me grants me its power, allowing me to act with savage strength and speed. It is not easy to contain this ferocity and, often, I end up hurting or destroying things I did not wish to.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241641,"modifiedTime":1783973241641,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"JESolgVFAmNDTg27","name":"Exorcist","type":"gift","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/icon-gift.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"When you face a clearly supernatural being, you gain 1 Additional Success on all Checks. You can also invoke sacred rites and prayers to disturb the evil you face. If a subject, artifact, or supernatural manifestation uses a Gift that you know of or have already seen in action, you can spend 1 Soma to prevent its use. Each time you activate this Gift, roll 1 die. If you roll a 5 or a 6, you gain 1 Devil Token.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 22.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241641,"modifiedTime":1783973241641,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"Vsgjj5DC3hqkKe4d","name":"The Inner Demon","type":"gift","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/icon-gift.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"Once per Scene, you can release the inner demon, whether that’d be yours or someone else’s. In your case, create a Descriptor that represents an emotion that includes the word Anger, Envy, or Wickedness. You receive 2 Additional Successes the first time you use this Descriptor for a Position Check. If you unleash someone else’s inner demon, the Storyteller will create a Descriptor for them that showcases their hidden, dark side. When using this Gift on particularly powerful individuals, the Storyteller may request a Position Check from you to succeed. Each time you use this Gift, you receive 1 Devil Token.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 22.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241641,"modifiedTime":1783973241641,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"a63uL08VSdNWLXaT","name":"Dark Ego - The Demon Revealed","type":"darkEgo","img":"icons/svg/terror.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"While generally retaining control, every now and then you have to allow the demon to manifest and unleash its anger. Create a Descriptor that represents your demonic form and that includes at least one of these words: Monstrous, Fierce, Beastly. Your physical abilities go far beyond those of a mere mortal, but you will behave like a devil, enjoying the evil and fear you inspire. When you act using this special Descriptor, you gain 1 Additional Success. You can spend 1 Devil Token to inflict 1 additional Wound or to spend as Soma for a Check. Once per Scenario, the Storyteller can spend 1 Devil Token to activate this Gift against your will.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 22.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0,"trigger":"Give free rein to your demonic side or listen to the sound of bells or cowbells for at least one minute."},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241641,"modifiedTime":1783973241641,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"gRV9d3yi4TT6JP1D","name":"An old cassock worn from many travels","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"An old cassock worn from many travels","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 22.","quantity":1},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241641,"modifiedTime":1783973241641,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"u790puWrJRxlhH0h","name":"exorcism vestments and tools","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"exorcism vestments and tools","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 22.","quantity":1},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241641,"modifiedTime":1783973241641,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"YItt8eU1d5R04JjU","name":"a shepherd’s curved staff of wood and iron to beat the devil with","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"a shepherd’s curved staff of wood and iron to beat the devil with","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 22.","quantity":1},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241641,"modifiedTime":1783973241641,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"GHMwTBl5tqX8WmLd","name":"an old pouch containing mysterious items taken while the demon is in control","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"an old pouch containing mysterious items taken while the demon is in control","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 22.","quantity":1},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241641,"modifiedTime":1783973241641,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"sxypMupsoc6WoQ0t","name":"precious small relics received as offerings","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"precious small relics received as offerings","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 22.","quantity":1},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241641,"modifiedTime":1783973241641,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"oM4cu0m0JPS3K0H0","name":"an old, time-worn bible","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"an old, time-worn bible","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 22.","quantity":1},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241642,"modifiedTime":1783973241642,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"Aky98Vk4vWloSldL","name":"Source Sheet","type":"storyElement","img":"icons/svg/scroll.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"<p><strong>Core Book</strong></p><p>bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 22.</p>","notes":"bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 22"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241642,"modifiedTime":1783973241642,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}],"effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"pregenSlug":"core-book-niklaus-von-krampus","pregenCollection":"Core Book","source":"bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf","pages":"22"}},"system":{"details":{"concept":"Core Book","origin":"Niklaus von Krampus","role":"Hunter of the Order","notes":"I am a devoted clergyman who has always dedicated his life to helping others. Over the years I have become a talented exorcist and this vocation of mine led me to the remote village of Borgo Maleanime. There, I fought a particularly insidious demon, who concealed itself among the ranks of a gang of young thugs who merely pretended to be demons to scare people. It was a tough fight, but I finally got the better of the fiend. Or so I thought. Something in the exorcism did not go as expected and now the demon dwells inside me, sowing fear and pain whenever it re-emerges. The Order welcomed me into its ranks as an exorcist and I gladly accepted this role, with the hope that the missions entrusted to me would allow me to find a way to rid myself, once and for all, of that which hides within me."},"resources":{"soma":{"value":6,"max":6},"xp":0,"wounds":{"value":0,"max":3},"darkness":{"value":0,"max":6}},"opposition":{"defaultLevel":5,"modifier":0},"bookmark":{"wound1":"","wound2":"","wound3":"","extraWound":""}},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241642,"modifiedTime":1783973241642,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"xblP0GvPJ1k5RXPU","name":"George the Holy Dragon Slayer","type":"hunter","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/avatars/pregens/core-book-george-the-holy-dragon-slayer.png","items":[{"_id":"wXG4Ju1hwoYVfMK0","name":"Descriptor 1","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"I am the most skilled and trusted agent of the Papacy and as such, it is my responsibility to make sure that the fight against darkness never falters. As a child, I fell into a river and almost drowned, but was saved by a creature that I later discovered was a dragon. When I grew up, I took holy vows and joined the Church. In doing so, I discovered that what I believed to be my savior was actually a creature of darkness, ready to steal my soul. I vowed to fight the darkness, suppressing the feeling of gratitude toward the dragon that saved me, which has always plagued me. Such weakness represents a crack through which evil could slither in. No mercy for monsters, no forgiveness for those who would join and serve the forces of evil.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 24.","positive":"I am the most skilled and trusted agent of the Papacy and as such, it is my responsibility to make sure that the fight against darkness never falters. As a child, I fell into a river and almost drowned, but was saved by a creature that I later discovered was a dragon. When I grew up, I took holy vows and joined the Church. In doing so, I discovered that what I believed to be my savior was actually a creature of darkness, ready to steal my soul. I vowed to fight the darkness, suppressing the feeling of gratitude toward the dragon that saved me, which has always plagued me. Such weakness represents a crack through which evil could slither in. No mercy for monsters, no forgiveness for those who would join and serve the forces of evil.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241642,"modifiedTime":1783973241642,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"4OCrrV26B9D4ADio","name":"Descriptor 2","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"I have dedicated my life to slaying monsters and aberrations, honing my body and my skill for that purpose. My strict discipline makes me rarely inclined to forgive the mistakes of others.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 24.","positive":"I have dedicated my life to slaying monsters and aberrations, honing my body and my skill for that purpose. My strict discipline makes me rarely inclined to forgive the mistakes of others.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241642,"modifiedTime":1783973241642,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"8tq5ea631EDCulS0","name":"Descriptor 3","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"I have vowed to eradicate all evil from this world and nothing can escape my inquisitive gaze. I hate all secrets, for I know that the seed of evil may grow within anyone.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 24.","positive":"I have vowed to eradicate all evil from this world and nothing can escape my inquisitive gaze. I hate all secrets, for I know that the seed of evil may grow within anyone.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241642,"modifiedTime":1783973241642,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"iIq0cXGarCpvOfjx","name":"Dark Ego Descriptor","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"I am a saint in the eyes of ordinary people and no door remains closed for me. My word is that of the Church itself. What I say is not to be questioned.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 24.","positive":"I am a saint in the eyes of ordinary people and no door remains closed for me. My word is that of the Church itself. What I say is not to be questioned.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241642,"modifiedTime":1783973241642,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"HXE5OfVfw2uzW8Zq","name":"The Dragon Slayer","type":"gift","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/icon-gift.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"You’re skilled at slaying monsters and demonic creatures in the name of faith. You start each Scenario with 1 Fervor Token. When facing an enemy that is obviously monstrous, if you get a successful Outcome on a Position Check, you can spend 1 Fervor Token to inflict 1 additional Wound. When such an enemy attempts to overwhelm you using one of their Gifts, you can spend 1 Fervor Token to receive 2 Additional Successes to your Defense Check. When you suffer 1 Wound, you receive 1 Fervor Token.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 24.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241642,"modifiedTime":1783973241642,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"XBqPD0AKBG7e8ciT","name":"Agent of the Papacy","type":"gift","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/icon-gift.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"When you speak to a crowd you can infuse their hearts with the light of faith. Spend 1 Fervor Token and you can create a Descriptor that represents a feeling of faith, anger, and a desire for justice against evil. Alternatively, create a Descriptor that represents trust and submission in such faith. The crowd will act accordingly for the rest of the Scene, but particularly powerful NPCs may be immune to your words. Receive 1 Additional Success on any Check you make using the sentiment you inspired. When you publicly expose evil, you receive 1 Fervor Token.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 24.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241642,"modifiedTime":1783973241642,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"XepUdrzCabSwj2Q1","name":"Dark Ego - The Saint","type":"darkEgo","img":"icons/svg/terror.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"When you channel sacred divine power, everyone bows their heads. Ordinary people will show you reverence, while weaker enemy NPCs (at the Storyteller’s discretion) won’t target you unless you’re the only available option, nor will they try to get in your way. In your presence, anyone possessing powers linked to the supernatural lowers their Opposition Level by 1. Your holy aura emits an intense light that can illuminate the whole area around you at your will.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 24.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0,"trigger":"Invoke holy divine power by reproaching all sinners and providing an example of purity and righteousness."},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241642,"modifiedTime":1783973241642,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"OuoavVWxMG4CLdeh","name":"Sacred armor","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"Sacred armor","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 24.","quantity":1},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241642,"modifiedTime":1783973241642,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"doKRv9DGaEmOjdT3","name":"a sword and a spear blessed by the Pope himself","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"a sword and a spear blessed by the Pope himself","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 24.","quantity":1},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241642,"modifiedTime":1783973241642,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"JVCVcor3TbZkmSdn","name":"my proud war stallion","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"my proud war stallion","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 24.","quantity":1},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241642,"modifiedTime":1783973241642,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"g2YzM3apaDGSLWt9","name":"a cross engraved with the Keys of Saint Peter (universal symbol of power)","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"a cross engraved with the Keys of Saint Peter (universal symbol of power)","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 24.","quantity":1},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241642,"modifiedTime":1783973241642,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"OIcFCwNKdK7DBdeG","name":"Aldebrand the faithful squire","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"Aldebrand the faithful squire","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 24.","quantity":1},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241642,"modifiedTime":1783973241642,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"48shOV04o3cwCVHg","name":"papal papers and seals","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"papal papers and seals","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 24.","quantity":1},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241642,"modifiedTime":1783973241642,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"YOnIYrMdDOdv31Yd","name":"a cloak of fine workmanship","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"a cloak of fine workmanship","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 24.","quantity":1},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241642,"modifiedTime":1783973241642,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"z3fo41Qlg60ukEmi","name":"Source Sheet","type":"storyElement","img":"icons/svg/scroll.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"<p><strong>Core Book</strong></p><p>bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 24.</p>","notes":"bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 24"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241642,"modifiedTime":1783973241642,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}],"effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"pregenSlug":"core-book-george-the-holy-dragon-slayer","pregenCollection":"Core Book","source":"bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf","pages":"24"}},"system":{"details":{"concept":"Core Book","origin":"George the Holy Dragon Slayer","role":"Hunter of the Order","notes":"I am the most skilled and trusted agent of the Papacy and as such, it is my responsibility to make sure that the fight against darkness never falters. As a child, I fell into a river and almost drowned, but was saved by a creature that I later discovered was a dragon. When I grew up, I took holy vows and joined the Church. In doing so, I discovered that what I believed to be my savior was actually a creature of darkness, ready to steal my soul. I vowed to fight the darkness, suppressing the feeling of gratitude toward the dragon that saved me, which has always plagued me. Such weakness represents a crack through which evil could slither in. No mercy for monsters, no forgiveness for those who would join and serve the forces of evil."},"resources":{"soma":{"value":6,"max":6},"xp":0,"wounds":{"value":0,"max":3},"darkness":{"value":0,"max":6}},"opposition":{"defaultLevel":5,"modifier":0},"bookmark":{"wound1":"","wound2":"","wound3":"","extraWound":""}},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241642,"modifiedTime":1783973241642,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"TgakOPCFRsrxj12j","name":"Sun Wukong the Amazing Monkey","type":"hunter","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/avatars/pregens/core-book-sun-wukong-the-amazing-monkey.png","items":[{"_id":"yZXguvum1zHM800T","name":"Descriptor 1","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"I have no memory of my life before my captivity, although I often dream of the forests and snow-capped peaks of my beloved China. I grew up as a circus animal at London’s Royal Circus but, deep within I carry the conviction that I am destined for something else. I rebelled by killing all my captors, fleeing across a vast and labyrinthine city. When the Order reached me, I thought it was the end, but the Hunters took me with them as their guardian and defender. The more I live as a Hunter, the closer I draw to transcendence. Now I am aware that, someday, I will discover who I really am.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 26.","positive":"I have no memory of my life before my captivity, although I often dream of the forests and snow-capped peaks of my beloved China. I grew up as a circus animal at London’s Royal Circus but, deep within I carry the conviction that I am destined for something else. I rebelled by killing all my captors, fleeing across a vast and labyrinthine city. When the Order reached me, I thought it was the end, but the Hunters took me with them as their guardian and defender. The more I live as a Hunter, the closer I draw to transcendence. Now I am aware that, someday, I will discover who I really am.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241642,"modifiedTime":1783973241642,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"40PqdB4fqPHs3Hrb","name":"Descriptor 2","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"I am a skilled guardian. My body is strong and hardened, my senses sharp and alert. Years of captivity have made me submissive, and I struggle not to follow every order I am given.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 26.","positive":"I am a skilled guardian. My body is strong and hardened, my senses sharp and alert. Years of captivity have made me submissive, and I struggle not to follow every order I am given.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241642,"modifiedTime":1783973241642,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"G5DOeLCqb9BvDhqp","name":"Descriptor 3","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"I am stronger and faster than any human and I am a highly skilled fighter. I don’t shy away from a challenge because I always believe I can win.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 26.","positive":"I am stronger and faster than any human and I am a highly skilled fighter. I don’t shy away from a challenge because I always believe I can win.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241642,"modifiedTime":1783973241642,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"9TWPKlV3psYnuThW","name":"Dark Ego Descriptor","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"My essence is magical, and this makes me resistant to enchantments that might snare stupid humans. My spiritual presence is imposing, and I struggle to hide what I am, especially in the eyes of those accustomed to magic.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 26.","positive":"My essence is magical, and this makes me resistant to enchantments that might snare stupid humans. My spiritual presence is imposing, and I struggle to hide what I am, especially in the eyes of those accustomed to magic.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241642,"modifiedTime":1783973241642,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"KlMwH9gpLtgIB4CI","name":"Guardian Disciple","type":"gift","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/icon-gift.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"You can intercept a danger before it overwhelms your ally. You may spend 1 Soma to get between an ally and a danger by standing in their place. Receive 1 Additional Success to any Defense Check you have to perform doing so. Once per Scenario, you can ignore 1 Wound you suffer.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 26.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241642,"modifiedTime":1783973241642,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"aoeKxojpd0bau9hM","name":"Monkey King","type":"gift","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/icon-gift.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"You are able to perform athletic feats unthinkable to a mere mortal. You may spend 1 Soma and choose an effect:\n1. You can jump incredibly far, up to thirty feet. You can bring another person with you by carrying them on your shoulders. You also ignore any damage related to a fall.\n2. Use your tail to manipulate an object and perform an additional action.\n3. Ignore any physical impediments to movement by using your impressive skills.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 26.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241642,"modifiedTime":1783973241642,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"lTFcCRItqRACFeR5","name":"Dark Ego - Descendant of the Awakening of the Void and the Emptiness","type":"darkEgo","img":"icons/svg/terror.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"When you release your true power, your body emits a divine light and no one can stop you. Take 1 Wound to get 2 Additional Successes to any physical Checks you have to perform. For the rest of the Scene spells have little effect on you and you get 2 Additional Successes to any Defense Check you make to protect yourself from arcane effects. When you deal a hit to someone, you can spend 1 Soma to inflict 1 additional Wound. The effects of this Gift cease if you behave in a composed and obedient manner, as your role as guardian dictates.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 26.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0,"trigger":"Act with passion and strength, showing everyone the incredible power that lies within your body."},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241642,"modifiedTime":1783973241642,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"QNNmgIwxvfuOVyBc","name":"A circus stick with three extendable segments","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"A circus stick with three extendable segments","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 26.","quantity":1},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241642,"modifiedTime":1783973241642,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"2wPnGzfhE8TEqUJy","name":"old and worn circus clothes","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"old and worn circus clothes","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 26.","quantity":1},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241643,"modifiedTime":1783973241643,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"vznDDlwxi25Ktrzp","name":"a golden diadem so tight on my forehead that it cannot be removed","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"a golden diadem so tight on my forehead that it cannot be removed","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 26.","quantity":1},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241643,"modifiedTime":1783973241643,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"aWNyPFQVAZZ9vJ7B","name":"a sheet with the drawing of a Chinese landscape — gift from a child who once watched one of my shows","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"a sheet with the drawing of a Chinese landscape — gift from a child who once watched one of my shows","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 26.","quantity":1},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241643,"modifiedTime":1783973241643,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"EOgymLZjvOkFCbVl","name":"Source Sheet","type":"storyElement","img":"icons/svg/scroll.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"<p><strong>Core Book</strong></p><p>bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 26.</p>","notes":"bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 26"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241643,"modifiedTime":1783973241643,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}],"effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"pregenSlug":"core-book-sun-wukong-the-amazing-monkey","pregenCollection":"Core Book","source":"bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf","pages":"26"}},"system":{"details":{"concept":"Core Book","origin":"Sun Wukong the Amazing Monkey","role":"Hunter of the Order","notes":"I have no memory of my life before my captivity, although I often dream of the forests and snow-capped peaks of my beloved China. I grew up as a circus animal at London’s Royal Circus but, deep within I carry the conviction that I am destined for something else. I rebelled by killing all my captors, fleeing across a vast and labyrinthine city. When the Order reached me, I thought it was the end, but the Hunters took me with them as their guardian and defender. The more I live as a Hunter, the closer I draw to transcendence. Now I am aware that, someday, I will discover who I really am."},"resources":{"soma":{"value":6,"max":6},"xp":0,"wounds":{"value":0,"max":3},"darkness":{"value":0,"max":6}},"opposition":{"defaultLevel":5,"modifier":0},"bookmark":{"wound1":"","wound2":"","wound3":"","extraWound":""}},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241643,"modifiedTime":1783973241643,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"ZtqN5q5NZ6u5KWFJ","name":"Verdoux Bluebeard","type":"hunter","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/avatars/pregens/core-book-verdoux-bluebeard.png","items":[{"_id":"vNF86xgicyxSrM6h","name":"Descriptor 1","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"I am a French aristocrat, called upon by my sovereign to manage the most devious and disreputable matters. I have lived an unconventional life, between accomplishing impossible tasks and keeping unspeakable secrets. It has opened my eyes to the world beyond the prosaic limits to which most are accustomed. In an effort to escape my adventurous life, I have more than once tried to start a family. However, my efforts have always ended in ruin, a price I must pay for the secrets I keep. I have lost six lovers, each killed by enemies and dangers that I naively hoped I could exclude from my life. That is why I volunteered for the Order, took an oath to weed out the darkness in this world, and sought revenge for the lives that were stolen from me.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 28.","positive":"I am a French aristocrat, called upon by my sovereign to manage the most devious and disreputable matters. I have lived an unconventional life, between accomplishing impossible tasks and keeping unspeakable secrets. It has opened my eyes to the world beyond the prosaic limits to which most are accustomed. In an effort to escape my adventurous life, I have more than once tried to start a family. However, my efforts have always ended in ruin, a price I must pay for the secrets I keep. I have lost six lovers, each killed by enemies and dangers that I naively hoped I could exclude from my life. That is why I volunteered for the Order, took an oath to weed out the darkness in this world, and sought revenge for the lives that were stolen from me.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241643,"modifiedTime":1783973241643,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"tTtwxG0vulYe2t7m","name":"Descriptor 2","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"My specialty is problem solving and I have a talent for analyzing every situation, allowing me to find resources and discover clues. Managing danger requires calm and concentration, and so I hate acting precipitously.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 28.","positive":"My specialty is problem solving and I have a talent for analyzing every situation, allowing me to find resources and discover clues. Managing danger requires calm and concentration, and so I hate acting precipitously.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241643,"modifiedTime":1783973241643,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"AWGAOp4Xnj0phGin","name":"Descriptor 3","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"I am an educated man who has studied the arts and sciences. I use this knowledge to uncover truths and reveal mysteries. I hate secrets, but only when I don’t know them.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 28.","positive":"I am an educated man who has studied the arts and sciences. I use this knowledge to uncover truths and reveal mysteries. I hate secrets, but only when I don’t know them.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241643,"modifiedTime":1783973241643,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"Lf0goSLVIuWIduYw","name":"Dark Ego Descriptor","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"Under the facade of a respectable man hides a skilled, unscrupulous problem-solver. I know how to kill and how to act with decisiveness. Everyone has done something they are not proud of and I can’t stand seeing the hypocrites who pretend as if they are morally superior to others.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 28.","positive":"Under the facade of a respectable man hides a skilled, unscrupulous problem-solver. I know how to kill and how to act with decisiveness. Everyone has done something they are not proud of and I can’t stand seeing the hypocrites who pretend as if they are morally superior to others.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241643,"modifiedTime":1783973241643,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"2bGp7VfB9Fsj7koC","name":"Problem Solver","type":"gift","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/icon-gift.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"If you’ve seen it once, you can do it yourself even better. You may spend 1 Soma to replicate the effect of a Gift from a Hunter or NPC you witnessed during the Scenario. Particular Gifts may still be off limits or only yield a part of their effect at the Storyteller’s discretion. You cannot replicate more than one Gift at a time. Once per Scene, you may ask the Storyteller to reveal to you a Gift of an NPC that you had time to study.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 28.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241643,"modifiedTime":1783973241643,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"eURSbnxoP9vgXkJo","name":"The Key to Each Door","type":"gift","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/icon-gift.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"Once per Scene, you can use one of the magic keys you own. Choose an effect:\n1. Open a closed door, no matter how many locks or defenses it has.\n2. If a subject touches your key, discover the strongest feeling they are experiencing.\n3. Close and lock a door so that no conventional methods will be able to open it.\n4. If you put your key in the mouth of a dead person you will see some of their memories. The Storyteller will describe them to you, focusing on your areas of interest.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 28.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241643,"modifiedTime":1783973241643,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"ER0lrlA7KIYDMrd0","name":"Dark Ego - The Unscrupulous Assassin","type":"darkEgo","img":"icons/svg/terror.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"You may appear as a civilized gentleman, but appearances can be deceiving. When necessary, you will not hesitate to kill. If you eliminate an NPC by inflicting a final Wound, you can also immediately eliminate a second Minor NPC. When you successfully defend yourself from a violent action, you can immediately eliminate a Minor NPC in response. Either way, the target must be within range of your wrath. After inflicting 1 Wound to someone, you can move freely as an additional action, allowing you to reach your true goal without anyone preventing you from doing so.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 28.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0,"trigger":"Reveal your dark side by injuring someone or acting aggressively despite your outwardly calm and staid appearance."},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241643,"modifiedTime":1783973241643,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"zXkd6txXbeLmRvya","name":"Nobleman’s clothes","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"Nobleman’s clothes","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 28.","quantity":1},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241643,"modifiedTime":1783973241643,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"LQSa5KAdEQreVzTA","name":"a long black cape","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"a long black cape","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 28.","quantity":1},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241643,"modifiedTime":1783973241643,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"f9v80xv1PzYLM1AJ","name":"a large bunch of keys","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"a large bunch of keys","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 28.","quantity":1},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241643,"modifiedTime":1783973241643,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"nPFuylUnVoya1Gyg","name":"a fine dueling blade","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"a fine dueling blade","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 28.","quantity":1},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241643,"modifiedTime":1783973241643,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"djIibE9JfX7eRCUf","name":"snuff of excellent quality","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"snuff of excellent quality","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 28.","quantity":1},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241643,"modifiedTime":1783973241643,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"eeQiiGwFSz2J0vTh","name":"a few doses of deadly Aqua Tofana","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"a few doses of deadly Aqua Tofana","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 28.","quantity":1},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241643,"modifiedTime":1783973241643,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"lQXQCLcc1FaRRtr8","name":"a large amount of coins and precious trinkets","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"a large amount of coins and precious trinkets","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 28.","quantity":1},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241643,"modifiedTime":1783973241643,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"e8sGxI3l3VLWjQ0K","name":"a heart-shaped locket hanging from a gold chain with the names of my lost loves engraved within","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"a heart-shaped locket hanging from a gold chain with the names of my lost loves engraved within","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 28.","quantity":1},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241643,"modifiedTime":1783973241643,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"CgR6UL11zoAXqAeZ","name":"Source Sheet","type":"storyElement","img":"icons/svg/scroll.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"<p><strong>Core Book</strong></p><p>bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 28.</p>","notes":"bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 28"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241643,"modifiedTime":1783973241643,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}],"effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"pregenSlug":"core-book-verdoux-bluebeard","pregenCollection":"Core Book","source":"bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf","pages":"28"}},"system":{"details":{"concept":"Core Book","origin":"Verdoux Bluebeard","role":"Hunter of the Order","notes":"I am a French aristocrat, called upon by my sovereign to manage the most devious and disreputable matters. I have lived an unconventional life, between accomplishing impossible tasks and keeping unspeakable secrets. It has opened my eyes to the world beyond the prosaic limits to which most are accustomed. In an effort to escape my adventurous life, I have more than once tried to start a family. However, my efforts have always ended in ruin, a price I must pay for the secrets I keep. I have lost six lovers, each killed by enemies and dangers that I naively hoped I could exclude from my life. That is why I volunteered for the Order, took an oath to weed out the darkness in this world, and sought revenge for the lives that were stolen from me."},"resources":{"soma":{"value":6,"max":6},"xp":0,"wounds":{"value":0,"max":3},"darkness":{"value":0,"max":6}},"opposition":{"defaultLevel":5,"modifier":0},"bookmark":{"wound1":"","wound2":"","wound3":"","extraWound":""}},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241643,"modifiedTime":1783973241643,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"1HWBZwitBJCoqXGF","name":"Yukie Onn the Traveling Artist","type":"hunter","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/avatars/pregens/core-book-yukie-onn-the-traveling-artist.png","items":[{"_id":"BTLvdTBNqOxYt07B","name":"Descriptor 1","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"I am a traveling artist who has known fame and honor in my homeland, Japan. That prestige meant nothing, however, when I found true love with Akihiro, son of a powerful noble family. When they forbade him from seeing me, we fled together to the remote region of Ezo. Even there we were not beyond the reach of Akihiro’s family and they pursued us into the high, snow-capped mountains. We had escaped every assassin, but could not outwit the snowstorm that trapped us. I survived, but only because Akihiro sacrificed the warmth of his life to save mine. But the cold has left me changed. It has become part of me and now the only thing that can make me feel warm is the hot blood of others. After taking revenge on all those who took Akihiro from me, I fled far away, using my talent for art to gain prestige and the protection of wealthy western nobles. Now, in the service of the Order, I save others from suffering the injustice that I have experienced, by punishing selfishness and wickedness.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 30.","positive":"I am a traveling artist who has known fame and honor in my homeland, Japan. That prestige meant nothing, however, when I found true love with Akihiro, son of a powerful noble family. When they forbade him from seeing me, we fled together to the remote region of Ezo. Even there we were not beyond the reach of Akihiro’s family and they pursued us into the high, snow-capped mountains. We had escaped every assassin, but could not outwit the snowstorm that trapped us. I survived, but only because Akihiro sacrificed the warmth of his life to save mine. But the cold has left me changed. It has become part of me and now the only thing that can make me feel warm is the hot blood of others. After taking revenge on all those who took Akihiro from me, I fled far away, using my talent for art to gain prestige and the protection of wealthy western nobles. Now, in the service of the Order, I save others from suffering the injustice that I have experienced, by punishing selfishness and wickedness.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241643,"modifiedTime":1783973241643,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"1EJlFTkhcY3fTnOs","name":"Descriptor 2","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"I am a highly skilled artist. Music, dance, and painting hold no mysteries for me. My otherworldly charm captivates ordinary people, always drawing attention to me.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 30.","positive":"I am a highly skilled artist. Music, dance, and painting hold no mysteries for me. My otherworldly charm captivates ordinary people, always drawing attention to me.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241643,"modifiedTime":1783973241643,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"NKohhxMS5ipAyO2h","name":"Descriptor 3","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"I cannot feel pain and my frail appearance hides surprising physical abilities. Blood is the only thing that can warm me and its smell alone makes me shiver.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 30.","positive":"I cannot feel pain and my frail appearance hides surprising physical abilities. Blood is the only thing that can warm me and its smell alone makes me shiver.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241643,"modifiedTime":1783973241643,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"QT1PA6i9QJnFQ0C7","name":"Dark Ego Descriptor","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"My body is pure ice and, because of this, I can manipulate ice as I please. However, I hate to manifest my power because it is dangerous to those around me and, as an artist, my purpose is to make people smile.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 30.","positive":"My body is pure ice and, because of this, I can manipulate ice as I please. However, I hate to manifest my power because it is dangerous to those around me and, as an artist, my purpose is to make people smile.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241644,"modifiedTime":1783973241644,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"IY4fafMbJ2e0g50f","name":"Otherworldly Charm","type":"gift","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/icon-gift.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"When you perform or flaunt your talents, all eyes will be on you. Receive 1 Additional Success for each Position Check you make to attract attention or charm someone. If you get an Outcome with an Increment, you may declare that a subject who has seen you has fallen in love with you. The Storyteller will create a specific Agenda for them that leads them to seek your attention.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 30.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241644,"modifiedTime":1783973241644,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"bMqrs7jr59SODm4b","name":"Blood-Hot","type":"gift","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/icon-gift.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"Once per Scene, you can consume a person’s blood when inflicting 1 non-fatal Wound. You recover 1 Wound, 1 Soma and receive some information about your victim such as a memory, an emotion or their heart’s desire. When you drink blood roll a die: if you roll a 1, you lose control and you will kill your victim by draining their blood, unless someone stops you.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 30.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241644,"modifiedTime":1783973241644,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"6kZvNvxQCgZ7d4rM","name":"Dark Ego - Ice-Cold","type":"darkEgo","img":"icons/svg/terror.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"You have control over your body temperature and, consequently, you can freeze the environment or objects in your immediate vicinity. When you manipulate ice, choose an effect by creating a Descriptor that represents it such as: Frozen Door or Aura of Frost and spend 1 Soma to manifest it for the whole Scene. As an additional effect, your frost can inflict 1 Wound on those who interact with it or make what you freeze incredibly fragile or incredibly hard. Whoever exploits the effects of frost in their favor gains 1 Additional Success for their action. Your frost has no direct effect on living things.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 30.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0,"trigger":"Shed your disguise as a simple artist and reveal your true, bitterly cold form or react passionately when fear and intimidation are used for selfish reasons."},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241644,"modifiedTime":1783973241644,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"omIn7Z4TVJWEndsk","name":"A travel kimono","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"A travel kimono","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 30.","quantity":1},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241644,"modifiedTime":1783973241644,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"LBisyNxHNz1e0yf8","name":"a stage kimono and theatrical effects","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"a stage kimono and theatrical effects","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 30.","quantity":1},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241644,"modifiedTime":1783973241644,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"PmIbH6GjJwM854p9","name":"a small ice sphere that never melts","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"a small ice sphere that never melts","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 30.","quantity":1},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241644,"modifiedTime":1783973241644,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"t3vrsciy2TH198Pv","name":"a butterfly-shaped hair clip (reminder of Akihiro)","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"a butterfly-shaped hair clip (reminder of Akihiro)","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 30.","quantity":1},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241644,"modifiedTime":1783973241644,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"ABe29oNv5j1e8FJH","name":"a finely crafted shamisen","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"a finely crafted shamisen","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 30.","quantity":1},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241644,"modifiedTime":1783973241644,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"VaVbjoXMDCavwWbo","name":"a pair of fine fans","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"a pair of fine fans","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 30.","quantity":1},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241644,"modifiedTime":1783973241644,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"DozlNZJxl7TvpRPi","name":"several daggers hidden in the kimono","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"several daggers hidden in the kimono","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 30.","quantity":1},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241644,"modifiedTime":1783973241644,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"DTrSj949Xt0rGwdJ","name":"Source Sheet","type":"storyElement","img":"icons/svg/scroll.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"<p><strong>Core Book</strong></p><p>bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 30.</p>","notes":"bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 30"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241644,"modifiedTime":1783973241644,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}],"effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"pregenSlug":"core-book-yukie-onn-the-traveling-artist","pregenCollection":"Core Book","source":"bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf","pages":"30"}},"system":{"details":{"concept":"Core Book","origin":"Yukie Onn the Traveling Artist","role":"Hunter of the Order","notes":"I am a traveling artist who has known fame and honor in my homeland, Japan. That prestige meant nothing, however, when I found true love with Akihiro, son of a powerful noble family. When they forbade him from seeing me, we fled together to the remote region of Ezo. Even there we were not beyond the reach of Akihiro’s family and they pursued us into the high, snow-capped mountains. We had escaped every assassin, but could not outwit the snowstorm that trapped us. I survived, but only because Akihiro sacrificed the warmth of his life to save mine. But the cold has left me changed. It has become part of me and now the only thing that can make me feel warm is the hot blood of others. After taking revenge on all those who took Akihiro from me, I fled far away, using my talent for art to gain prestige and the protection of wealthy western nobles. Now, in the service of the Order, I save others from suffering the injustice that I have experienced, by punishing selfishness and wickedness."},"resources":{"soma":{"value":6,"max":6},"xp":0,"wounds":{"value":0,"max":3},"darkness":{"value":0,"max":6}},"opposition":{"defaultLevel":5,"modifier":0},"bookmark":{"wound1":"","wound2":"","wound3":"","extraWound":""}},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241644,"modifiedTime":1783973241644,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"qElrumnVfbpZH6oM","name":"Cunning Machiavelli the Fox and Sly Bischeri the Cat","type":"hunter","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/avatars/pregens/core-book-fox-and-cat-cunning-machiavelli-the-fox-and-sly-bischeri-the-cat.png","items":[{"_id":"aGGXgbr4r7ocXiv4","name":"Descriptor 1","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"We are two boys who survived and thrived on the street through trickery and deceit. Unfortunately, we made a terrible mistake by choosing a weird old lady as a mark. She turned out to be a goddamn witch. The witch cursed us… And from that day on, every twelve hours, one becomes a Fox and the other a Cat. Bound by this spell, we found a way to make a lot of money, deceiving stupid nobles and rich merchants. The Order has noticed us and taken us under its wing, with the promise of breaking the curse that afflicts us.","notes":"See bt-cb-foxcat-sheet-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 2.","positive":"We are two boys who survived and thrived on the street through trickery and deceit. Unfortunately, we made a terrible mistake by choosing a weird old lady as a mark. She turned out to be a goddamn witch. The witch cursed us… And from that day on, every twelve hours, one becomes a Fox and the other a Cat. Bound by this spell, we found a way to make a lot of money, deceiving stupid nobles and rich merchants. The Order has noticed us and taken us under its wing, with the promise of breaking the curse that afflicts us.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241644,"modifiedTime":1783973241644,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"pshoDoCU0hwvbUA1","name":"Descriptor 2","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"Cunning's Descriptor: I have a natural talent for telling lies, which the Order often uses to its advantage. Despite my origins, I know a great deal about many things because lying requires planning and preparation.","notes":"See bt-cb-foxcat-sheet-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 2.","positive":"Cunning's Descriptor: I have a natural talent for telling lies, which the Order often uses to its advantage. Despite my origins, I know a great deal about many things because lying requires planning and preparation.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241644,"modifiedTime":1783973241644,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"4bx1MV4D1tjUluDx","name":"Descriptor 3","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"Sly's Descriptor: A life on the road has taught me to be a skilled thief. Everyone for themselves is my motto.","notes":"See bt-cb-foxcat-sheet-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 2.","positive":"Sly's Descriptor: A life on the road has taught me to be a skilled thief. Everyone for themselves is my motto.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241644,"modifiedTime":1783973241644,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"KCK7xOo63OhzOq3Z","name":"Descriptor 4","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"Common Descriptor: I will stop at nothing to get what I want, and it only takes me a few seconds to evaluate what is happening and find the right way to take advantage of it. I hate acting alone because there's no one to take the blame.","notes":"See bt-cb-foxcat-sheet-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 2.","positive":"Common Descriptor: I will stop at nothing to get what I want, and it only takes me a few seconds to evaluate what is happening and find the right way to take advantage of it. I hate acting alone because there's no one to take the blame.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241644,"modifiedTime":1783973241644,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"3ConSe0D2DgaQAHH","name":"Dark Ego Descriptor","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"Like it or not, we are bound by magic. We can share thoughts, each see what the other sees, and thanks to this we can work together to cheat others. Whoever is in animal form hates not being able to communicate and often annoys the other out of spite.","notes":"See bt-cb-foxcat-sheet-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 2.","positive":"Like it or not, we are bound by magic. We can share thoughts, each see what the other sees, and thanks to this we can work together to cheat others. Whoever is in animal form hates not being able to communicate and often annoys the other out of spite.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241644,"modifiedTime":1783973241644,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"KADmiq2wuu9Cdr0z","name":"Believe in Miracles (Cunning)","type":"gift","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/icon-gift.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"Once per Scene, you can tell everyone something that will be accepted without question until the lie is uncovered. The deception becomes obvious at the end of the Scene or once exposed. Gain +1 Success on any Check where you exploit the lie.","notes":"See bt-cb-foxcat-sheet-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 2.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241644,"modifiedTime":1783973241644,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"pXvAH2XHNT6jsYEn","name":"Rogue (Sly)","type":"gift","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/icon-gift.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"By pretending to be weak during a Scene, NPCs will overlook you unless you acted against them. By spending 1 Soma, you can flee any Scene involving a crowd.","notes":"See bt-cb-foxcat-sheet-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 2.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241644,"modifiedTime":1783973241644,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"JTMldAqO31DdaXn7","name":"Partner in Crime (Common)","type":"gift","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/icon-gift.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"Once per Scene, when an ally acts with your support, they receive +1 Additional Success. Additionally, if an ally achieves an Outcome with an Increment, you may immediately take an extra action.","notes":"See bt-cb-foxcat-sheet-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 2.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241644,"modifiedTime":1783973241644,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"hdn18U2N1IPIptNH","name":"Dark Ego - The Fox and the Cat","type":"darkEgo","img":"icons/svg/terror.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"You and your partner share Soma and Wounds. The human form can spend 1 Soma to use the Gift of the animal form. Once per Scene, if your partner helps you, you gain +2 Additional Successes on a Position Check.","notes":"See bt-cb-foxcat-sheet-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 2.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0,"trigger":"Trick or deceive someone, taking advantage of your partner's support."},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241644,"modifiedTime":1783973241644,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"ypAzQzRrCsqHF5Io","name":"Night (Cunning): Comfortable and light clothes, hidden small knives, counterfeit cards and stamps, fake coins and jewelry","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"Night (Cunning): Comfortable and light clothes, hidden small knives, counterfeit cards and stamps, fake coins and jewelry","notes":"See bt-cb-foxcat-sheet-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 2.","quantity":1},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241644,"modifiedTime":1783973241644,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"415H5xYcYMCGJCxx","name":"a volume of the Biblioteca Universale Sacro-Profana Encyclopedia. Day (Sly): Worn-out clothes, sharp long knife","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"a volume of the Biblioteca Universale Sacro-Profana Encyclopedia. Day (Sly): Worn-out clothes, sharp long knife","notes":"See bt-cb-foxcat-sheet-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 2.","quantity":1},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241644,"modifiedTime":1783973241644,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"wTzsw35p5XOr8yam","name":"old stick to pretend to be blind, torn purse with a hole, sack full of stolen junk","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"old stick to pretend to be blind, torn purse with a hole, sack full of stolen junk","notes":"See bt-cb-foxcat-sheet-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 2.","quantity":1},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241644,"modifiedTime":1783973241644,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"JW02B5MZvlxEeiHP","name":"Source Sheet","type":"storyElement","img":"icons/svg/scroll.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"<p><strong>Core Book: Fox and Cat</strong></p><p>bt-cb-foxcat-sheet-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 2.</p><p>Use Cunning's side at night and Sly's side during the day, following the source sheet. Spanish local sheet archived at systems/broken-tales/assets/source-pdfs/machiavelli-el-zorro-astuto-y-bischeri-el-gato-malicioso.pdf.</p>","notes":"bt-cb-foxcat-sheet-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 2"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241644,"modifiedTime":1783973241644,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}],"effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"pregenSlug":"core-book-fox-and-cat-cunning-machiavelli-the-fox-and-sly-bischeri-the-cat","pregenCollection":"Core Book: Fox and Cat","source":"bt-cb-foxcat-sheet-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf","pages":"2"}},"system":{"details":{"concept":"Core Book: Fox and Cat","origin":"Cunning Machiavelli the Fox and Sly Bischeri the Cat","role":"Hunter of the Order","notes":"We are two boys who survived and thrived on the street through trickery and deceit. Unfortunately, we made a terrible mistake by choosing a weird old lady as a mark. She turned out to be a goddamn witch. The witch cursed us… And from that day on, every twelve hours, one becomes a Fox and the other a Cat. Bound by this spell, we found a way to make a lot of money, deceiving stupid nobles and rich merchants. The Order has noticed us and taken us under its wing, with the promise of breaking the curse that afflicts us."},"resources":{"soma":{"value":6,"max":6},"xp":0,"wounds":{"value":0,"max":3},"darkness":{"value":0,"max":6}},"opposition":{"defaultLevel":5,"modifier":0},"bookmark":{"wound1":"","wound2":"","wound3":"","extraWound":""}},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241644,"modifiedTime":1783973241644,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"rxP5XU141HYY9ueC","name":"Alice of Other Worlds","type":"hunter","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/avatars/pregens/the-broken-ones-alice-of-other-worlds.png","items":[{"_id":"S3XzyxCk1Dqj2uXP","name":"Descriptor 1","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"I am a young doctor who has dedicated her whole life to the treatment of mental illnesses. I understand \nthem, for I am suffering from one as well, and only those who burned themselves while playing with \nfire can understand its dangers. After a dark period during which I managed a sanatorium, the Order \nstripped me of all academic honors and degrees, reducing me to the status of a criminal. But it didn’t \ntake long for them to understand the extent of my studies and the magnitude of my abilities. After \npossessing the Pope himself, I struck a deal with the Order. They will allow me to continue my studies, \nbut I may only study the creatures they fight. And perhaps, through the distorted minds of the Broken \nTales, I can prove that the worlds I visited as a child are real and not the ramblings of a mad mind.","notes":"See bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 2.","positive":"I am a young doctor who has dedicated her whole life to the treatment of mental illnesses. I understand them, for I am suffering from one as well, and only those who burned themselves while playing with fire can understand its dangers. After a dark period during which I managed a sanatorium, the Order stripped me of all academic honors and degrees, reducing me to the status of a criminal. But it didn’t take long for them to understand the extent of my studies and the magnitude of my abilities. After possessing the Pope himself, I struck a deal with the Order. They will allow me to continue my studies, but I may only study the creatures they fight. And perhaps, through the distorted minds of the Broken Tales, I can prove that the worlds I visited as a child are real and not the ramblings of a mad mind.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241645,"modifiedTime":1783973241645,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"ZGBQmWIBTK35UsSf","name":"Descriptor 2","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"I am a skilled physician and psychiatrist, and \ndiagnosing illnesses is simple. My work has made me \nparticularly cold and detached.","notes":"See bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 2.","positive":"I am a skilled physician and psychiatrist, and diagnosing illnesses is simple. My work has made me particularly cold and detached.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241645,"modifiedTime":1783973241645,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"oB5HqqvUvbJWQLsh","name":"Descriptor 3","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"Cheshire, my faithful trained lynx, is the most \ntrustworthy of companions – a shadow keeping \nme safe from threats. Cheshire’s attachment is an \nobsession and she may even threaten those who don’t \nwant to hurt me.","notes":"See bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 2.","positive":"Cheshire, my faithful trained lynx, is the most trustworthy of companions – a shadow keeping me safe from threats. Cheshire’s attachment is an obsession and she may even threaten those who don’t want to hurt me.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241645,"modifiedTime":1783973241645,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"m3pJimakfmvWOMxb","name":"Dark Ego Descriptor","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"Alice of\nOther Worlds\nAs a child I traveled to other worlds and my mind can perceive and see \nthings beyond common perception. Memories of my childhood haunt me, \nand I often get lost in visions of the past.","notes":"See bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 2.","positive":"Alice of Other Worlds As a child I traveled to other worlds and my mind can perceive and see things beyond common perception. Memories of my childhood haunt me, and I often get lost in visions of the past.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241645,"modifiedTime":1783973241645,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"FZe4yw7cmoEqwr0U","name":"Physician","type":"gift","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/icon-gift.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"Once per Scenario, when you take the \ntime to treat an injury, you may heal 1 Wound suffered \nby one of your patients, also bringing them back from \napparent death or unconsciousness. Y ou may spend 1 \nSoma to reassure and calm someone who is frightened or \nexperiencing any negative feeling. If you do, you receive \n1 Additional Success to any Check involving interactions \nwith that patient for the remaining of the Scenario.","notes":"See bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 2.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241645,"modifiedTime":1783973241645,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"6GWPdYyWedOX1p2K","name":"Cheshire the Lynx","type":"gift","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/icon-gift.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"Cheshire is an NPC fully \nunder your control, with the following profile:\nOL Medium 5 – (2 Wounds) \nDescriptor: I am a big, short-tempered wild lynx and I only \nlive to serve Alice.\nGift - Two Souls: Y ou share your soul with Cheshire, and \nyou can see and feel through her senses. Y ou can spend \n1 Soma to make Cheshire immaterial for an action and \nallow her to cross any obstacle.","notes":"See bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 2.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241645,"modifiedTime":1783973241645,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"pbuTXswDODdOVXhx","name":"Dark Ego - Alice of Other Worlds","type":"darkEgo","img":"icons/svg/terror.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"As an action, you may spend \n1 Soma to try to possess the body of a person or animal that is looking into \nyour eyes. Particularly powerful individuals may require a Position Check for \nyou to succeed. Y ou can act through the body you possess and continue to use \nyour Gifts and Descriptors, but you receive an additional Descriptor created \nby the Storyteller and representing the abilities of the body you are possessing. \nThe possession ends at the end of the Scene, when the possessed body suffers 1 \nWound, or you decide to return to your body of your own volition. While you \ncontrol someone else’s body, your original body is inert and at the mercy of the \nworld. Y ou cannot possess Broken Tales or supernatural creatures. Y our mind is \nnot easy to control, so you gain 1 Additional Success for Defense Checks against \nany kind of mind control and magic.","notes":"See bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 2.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0,"trigger":"You notice a detail that does not match what you consider normal.\nXP\nSoma\n 5"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241645,"modifiedTime":1783973241645,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"IoAUtmr9D7VyUxPm","name":"A valuable doctor’s coat","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"A valuable doctor’s coat","notes":"See bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 2.","quantity":1},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241645,"modifiedTime":1783973241645,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"Xh3YwHaZIzarVDUl","name":"Books about the human psyche","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"Books about the human psyche","notes":"See bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 2.","quantity":1},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241645,"modifiedTime":1783973241645,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"DBJyV6EPrkIhsSYK","name":"A watch, a gift from someone I met on my travels","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"A watch, a gift from someone I met on my travels","notes":"See bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 2.","quantity":1},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241645,"modifiedTime":1783973241645,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"cJjvpMaLDVMhDjeH","name":"A lucky rabbit’s foot","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"A lucky rabbit’s foot","notes":"See bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 2.","quantity":1},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241645,"modifiedTime":1783973241645,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"PfWciYal9n5EpIRW","name":"A set of sharp scalpels","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"A set of sharp scalpels","notes":"See bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 2.","quantity":1},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241645,"modifiedTime":1783973241645,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"4wPBfwWt2uNdUYt0","name":"A doctor’s bag","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"A doctor’s bag","notes":"See bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 2.","quantity":1},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241645,"modifiedTime":1783973241645,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"v7eqX0bjZ9kvL11S","name":"A deck of cards which is missing the queen of hearts","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"A deck of cards which is missing the queen of hearts","notes":"See bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 2.","quantity":1},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241645,"modifiedTime":1783973241645,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"FnQTFkY1pRfYU6Cb","name":"Source Sheet","type":"storyElement","img":"icons/svg/scroll.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"<p><strong>The Broken Ones</strong></p><p>bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 2.</p>","notes":"bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 2"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241645,"modifiedTime":1783973241645,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}],"effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"pregenSlug":"the-broken-ones-alice-of-other-worlds","pregenCollection":"The Broken Ones","source":"bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf","pages":"2"}},"system":{"details":{"concept":"The Broken Ones","origin":"Alice of Other Worlds","role":"Hunter of the Order","notes":"I am a young doctor who has dedicated her whole life to the treatment of mental illnesses. I understand \nthem, for I am suffering from one as well, and only those who burned themselves while playing with \nfire can understand its dangers. After a dark period during which I managed a sanatorium, the Order \nstripped me of all academic honors and degrees, reducing me to the status of a criminal. But it didn’t \ntake long for them to understand the extent of my studies and the magnitude of my abilities. After \npossessing the Pope himself, I struck a deal with the Order. They will allow me to continue my studies, \nbut I may only study the creatures they fight. And perhaps, through the distorted minds of the Broken \nTales, I can prove that the worlds I visited as a child are real and not the ramblings of a mad mind."},"resources":{"soma":{"value":5,"max":5},"xp":0,"wounds":{"value":0,"max":3},"darkness":{"value":0,"max":6}},"opposition":{"defaultLevel":5,"modifier":0},"bookmark":{"wound1":"","wound2":"","wound3":"","extraWound":""}},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241645,"modifiedTime":1783973241645,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"twi7RLRgqCKhLgnZ","name":"Beauty and her Beast","type":"hunter","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/avatars/pregens/the-broken-ones-beauty-and-her-beast.png","items":[{"_id":"ggxsrqLgAKO6rjjR","name":"Descriptor 1","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"I am Bellina Cantalupo, but everyone calls me Bella. I was once a servant to the bride of the monstrous Dionysus \nGonsalva. I played my cards well, charmed the nobleman, and rose to power. Unfortunately, the Order got in the \nway and sabotaged everything I had built. As a punishment, I was magically bound to Dionysus and now our \nsouls are intertwined. I feel his pain and his beastly instincts. Dionysus perceives, in turn, my disgust for him, \nbut it doesn’t affect the mad love he feels for me. I serve the Order in the hope of gaining its grace and being \nreleased from this punishment. But, deep down in my heart, I still long for the power that I was denied being born \na peasant, but that I know I deserve.","notes":"See bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 4.","positive":"I am Bellina Cantalupo, but everyone calls me Bella. I was once a servant to the bride of the monstrous Dionysus Gonsalva. I played my cards well, charmed the nobleman, and rose to power. Unfortunately, the Order got in the way and sabotaged everything I had built. As a punishment, I was magically bound to Dionysus and now our souls are intertwined. I feel his pain and his beastly instincts. Dionysus perceives, in turn, my disgust for him, but it doesn’t affect the mad love he feels for me. I serve the Order in the hope of gaining its grace and being released from this punishment. But, deep down in my heart, I still long for the power that I was denied being born a peasant, but that I know I deserve.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241645,"modifiedTime":1783973241645,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"Ar0qp36Pd5KJgaRE","name":"Descriptor 2","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"Dionysus follows me and protects me like a faithful beast, \nand responds to all my commands. As useful as this is, I feel \ndisgusted every time he comes near me.","notes":"See bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 4.","positive":"Dionysus follows me and protects me like a faithful beast, and responds to all my commands. As useful as this is, I feel disgusted every time he comes near me.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241645,"modifiedTime":1783973241645,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"RJMoaw0GKfkexbZT","name":"Descriptor 3","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"I am charismatic and affable. My innate air of superiority \nfascinates simple people. I love having all my eyes on me.","notes":"See bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 4.","positive":"I am charismatic and affable. My innate air of superiority fascinates simple people. I love having all my eyes on me.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241645,"modifiedTime":1783973241645,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"pH46Mx1IySiVMzv8","name":"Dark Ego Descriptor","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"I am linked to Dionysus and we share pain and perceptions. He will \nalways know where I am and vice versa. For me, that’s the most \nhumiliating part of the curse.","notes":"See bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 4.","positive":"I am linked to Dionysus and we share pain and perceptions. He will always know where I am and vice versa. For me, that’s the most humiliating part of the curse.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241645,"modifiedTime":1783973241645,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"ixp1GR9k5NIfO7Bd","name":"The Beast","type":"gift","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/icon-gift.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"Dionysus is an NPC fully under your control, \nwith the following profile:\nOL Medium 5 – (Wounds: as Bella’s current value) \nDescriptor: I am a powerful and feral beastman. Only Bella’s scent \nkeeps me under control.\nGift - Monstrous: If he intends to kill someone, Dionysus may \nact twice in each Exchange. Once per Scene, Dionysus can break \nor lift even a large object with extreme ease. \nDuring Scenes, you decide how Dionysus acts. Any Wound one \nof you suffers also applies to the other. When Dionysus is within \na few steps, you receive 1 Penalty to each Check due to the strong \ndisgust you feel for him.","notes":"See bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 4.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241645,"modifiedTime":1783973241645,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"dEKP4Pt4TPTUURQx","name":"The Beauty","type":"gift","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/icon-gift.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"Once per Scene, when you meet a new subject, \nyou may spend 1 Soma and declare that you have met them in the \npast and that you made some kind of deal with them. Create, in \nagreement with the Storyteller, an Agenda for them representing \nthe deal. If you take the time to talk to someone, the Storyteller \nmust reveal a clue about their current Agenda or a drawback of \none of their Descriptors. When someone shows a strong interest \nin you, Dionysus, if present, loses the use of the Monstrous Gift \nbecause of the strong jealousy and shame he feels for himself.","notes":"See bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 4.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241645,"modifiedTime":1783973241645,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"fxdo949lsr9WhhzJ","name":"Dark Ego - Beasts in Body and Soul","type":"darkEgo","img":"icons/svg/terror.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"When you reveal your \ntrue nature everyone is horrified. One is a beast in body, while the other \nis a beast in her soul. Y ou receive 3 Savagery Tokens that you can spend \nduring the Scene to: \n1. Inflict 1 additional Wound, if Dionysus spends an action to help you in \nthe attack. The Wound will be a strikingly bloody gash.\n2. Have a minor NPC lose their action as they are intimidated, having \nwitnessed the fury of Dionysus.\n3. If Dionysus is not present in the Scene, he can appear immediately \n(possibly tearing a new opening in the environment, demolishing any \npossible obstacle) to support you. \n4. Perform a second action in the Exchange, if Dionysus spends one of his \nto open the way for you.","notes":"See bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 4.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0,"trigger":"Unleash the feral power of Dionysus, or humiliate or betray \nsomeone, revealing your true nature."},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241645,"modifiedTime":1783973241645,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"Lkj7KiyLZlDsDvMs","name":"A leather whip and metal needles","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"A leather whip and metal needles","notes":"See bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 4.","quantity":1},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241645,"modifiedTime":1783973241645,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"1GdTTKl9fdpk1aPX","name":"A noble dress","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"A noble dress","notes":"See bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 4.","quantity":1},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241645,"modifiedTime":1783973241645,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"8q7qXsDXuh8V6wM3","name":"Fine dresses and jewelry","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"Fine dresses and jewelry","notes":"See bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 4.","quantity":1},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241645,"modifiedTime":1783973241645,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"y8puTKX2yqz6SxL6","name":"A rose that never fades","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"A rose that never fades","notes":"See bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 4.","quantity":1},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241645,"modifiedTime":1783973241645,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"TC0QO2nhmSK8uDbm","name":"A bag with dried meat with which to keep Dionysus’ hunger at bay","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"A bag with dried meat with which to keep Dionysus’ hunger at bay","notes":"See bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 4.","quantity":1},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241645,"modifiedTime":1783973241645,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"jgdQvZ0YktCI0BJi","name":"Soaps and feminine perfumes","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"Soaps and feminine perfumes","notes":"See bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 4.","quantity":1},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241645,"modifiedTime":1783973241645,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"KCMLe0YHCrvaS03W","name":"A poisoned stiletto that I keep hidden for any eventuality","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"A poisoned stiletto that I keep hidden for any eventuality","notes":"See bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 4.","quantity":1},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241645,"modifiedTime":1783973241645,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"LwAMPpLwulbQr1Fu","name":"Source Sheet","type":"storyElement","img":"icons/svg/scroll.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"<p><strong>The Broken Ones</strong></p><p>bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 4.</p>","notes":"bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 4"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241645,"modifiedTime":1783973241645,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}],"effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"pregenSlug":"the-broken-ones-beauty-and-her-beast","pregenCollection":"The Broken Ones","source":"bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf","pages":"4"}},"system":{"details":{"concept":"The Broken Ones","origin":"Beauty and her Beast","role":"Hunter of the Order","notes":"I am Bellina Cantalupo, but everyone calls me Bella. I was once a servant to the bride of the monstrous Dionysus \nGonsalva. I played my cards well, charmed the nobleman, and rose to power. Unfortunately, the Order got in the \nway and sabotaged everything I had built. As a punishment, I was magically bound to Dionysus and now our \nsouls are intertwined. I feel his pain and his beastly instincts. Dionysus perceives, in turn, my disgust for him, \nbut it doesn’t affect the mad love he feels for me. I serve the Order in the hope of gaining its grace and being \nreleased from this punishment. But, deep down in my heart, I still long for the power that I was denied being born \na peasant, but that I know I deserve."},"resources":{"soma":{"value":6,"max":6},"xp":0,"wounds":{"value":0,"max":3},"darkness":{"value":0,"max":6}},"opposition":{"defaultLevel":5,"modifier":0},"bookmark":{"wound1":"","wound2":"","wound3":"","extraWound":""}},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241646,"modifiedTime":1783973241646,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"fgUPyDrK8LZWQetx","name":"Bloodwhite","type":"hunter","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/avatars/pregens/the-broken-ones-bloodwhite.png","items":[{"_id":"PoeTxaYNQa6FRcql","name":"Descriptor 1","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"I am a mutant and can alter my body as I wish. The Order uses \nmy unique abilities to support other Hunters. When it changes, \nmy body emits a particular hormone that arouses those close \nto me.","notes":"See bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 6.","positive":"I am a mutant and can alter my body as I wish. The Order uses my unique abilities to support other Hunters. When it changes, my body emits a particular hormone that arouses those close to me.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241646,"modifiedTime":1783973241646,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"NqZd9pRsnOFMyPY8","name":"Descriptor 2","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"My touch is capable of mutating other beings with devastating \nresults. The flesh deforms before it explodes. When I am in the \ngrip of strong emotions, I lose control of my power and I am \nafraid to touch the people I care about.","notes":"See bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 6.","positive":"My touch is capable of mutating other beings with devastating results. The flesh deforms before it explodes. When I am in the grip of strong emotions, I lose control of my power and I am afraid to touch the people I care about.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241646,"modifiedTime":1783973241646,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"YpeEaNL3h6tg6b23","name":"Descriptor 3","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"I am a good girl and believe in the power of love and justice. My \npure gaze reaches the hearts of the people close to me. I try to \navoid those that look at me with disgust, believing me to be a \nmonster.","notes":"See bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 6.","positive":"I am a good girl and believe in the power of love and justice. My pure gaze reaches the hearts of the people close to me. I try to avoid those that look at me with disgust, believing me to be a monster.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241646,"modifiedTime":1783973241646,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"398ofO7eaA9Wvvc1","name":"Mutant","type":"gift","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/icon-gift.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"Y ou start the Scenario with 3 Mutation Tokens. \nY ou may spend 1 Mutation Token to modify a part of your body, \nsuch as turning your arms into wings or your skin into a thick \ncarapace. Create a Descriptor that represents the mutation. Y ou \ngain 1 Additional Success whenever you take advantage of your \nmutation. Whenever you change shape, the Storyteller can decide \nthat the hormone emitted by your body bewilders the mind of an \nNPC nearby, creating a specific Agenda for them that leads them \nto seek you in some way. Y our mutations remain until the end of \nthe Scene. Once per Scenario, the Storyteller can declare that this \nGift is activated without you realizing it and give you 1 Mutation \nToken.","notes":"See bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 6.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241646,"modifiedTime":1783973241646,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"NSHpPh5KwwMeHLdq","name":"Mutagenic Touch","type":"gift","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/icon-gift.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"Y ou can inflict 1 Wound to a living \nbeing with the touch of your hand. If you kill the target this way, \nit will explode in a gruesome way, scaring everyone present. The \nmost impressionable NPCs, at the Storyteller’s discretion, will \nthen try to avoid any confrontation with you. When you achieve \nan Outcome with an Increment with your touch and kill someone, \nyour body assimilates part of the exploded flesh, and you may \nrecover 1 Mutation Token or 1 Soma.","notes":"See bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 6.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241646,"modifiedTime":1783973241646,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"AyLNCkYHvzX6wrzE","name":"Dark Ego - Pure Innocence","type":"darkEgo","img":"icons/svg/terror.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"When you appeal to the \npurity of your heart, even the foulest spell is broken. When you \nactivate your Dark Ego during a Scene, you become immune to \nany effect of fear or mind control, and all subjects you consider evil \nlower their Opposition Level by 1 in your presence. Y ou can spend 1 \nMutation Token to give 1 Additional Success to the first action of all \nallies who admire you for who you are.","notes":"See bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 6.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0,"trigger":"Open your heart and appeal to the goodness of those close to \nyou, revealing who you are, or sacrifice something of yourself for others.\nXP\nSoma\n 5"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241646,"modifiedTime":1783973241646,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"ZhAqApLDk3FrTFwb","name":"A precious dress","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"A precious dress","notes":"See bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 6.","quantity":1},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241646,"modifiedTime":1783973241646,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"axbkH1OWvuzdftQ9","name":"A swallow-shaped hair clip, a gift from my mother","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"A swallow-shaped hair clip, a gift from my mother","notes":"See bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 6.","quantity":1},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241646,"modifiedTime":1783973241646,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"jnOooTsU2Nf5iv8I","name":"An old gun, a gift from a group of seven mercenaries who defended me for a long time","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"An old gun, a gift from a group of seven mercenaries who defended me for a long time","notes":"See bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 6.","quantity":1},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241646,"modifiedTime":1783973241646,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"q3uLcDdq5UjuYvNz","name":"The coat of arms of my noble family","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"The coat of arms of my noble family","notes":"See bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 6.","quantity":1},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241646,"modifiedTime":1783973241646,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"gQa5Uuxa4HX24GAf","name":"A few small animals from the woods that follow me, attracted by my smell","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"A few small animals from the woods that follow me, attracted by my smell","notes":"See bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 6.","quantity":1},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241646,"modifiedTime":1783973241646,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"DMjeMZZSnzBcfQ0I","name":"Source Sheet","type":"storyElement","img":"icons/svg/scroll.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"<p><strong>The Broken Ones</strong></p><p>bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 6.</p>","notes":"bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 6"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241646,"modifiedTime":1783973241646,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}],"effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"pregenSlug":"the-broken-ones-bloodwhite","pregenCollection":"The Broken Ones","source":"bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf","pages":"6"}},"system":{"details":{"concept":"The Broken Ones","origin":"Bloodwhite","role":"Hunter of the Order","notes":"<p><strong>The Broken Ones</strong></p><p>bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 6.</p>"},"resources":{"soma":{"value":5,"max":5},"xp":0,"wounds":{"value":0,"max":3},"darkness":{"value":0,"max":6}},"opposition":{"defaultLevel":5,"modifier":0},"bookmark":{"wound1":"","wound2":"","wound3":"","extraWound":""}},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241646,"modifiedTime":1783973241646,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"rl4ro5zNZF0k3nlp","name":"Wound. Carlo the LivingPuppet","type":"hunter","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/avatars/pregens/the-broken-ones-wound-carlo-the-livingpuppet.png","items":[{"_id":"Xlwfzma0JXxGpKVX","name":"Descriptor 1","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"My life is animated by the magic of lies, and for this reason \nI am skilled at recognizing and using both falsehoods and \nmagic. Even if admitting it is hurtful, my own life is a lie and \nI move only because I pretend to be a real child.","notes":"See bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 8.","positive":"My life is animated by the magic of lies, and for this reason I am skilled at recognizing and using both falsehoods and magic. Even if admitting it is hurtful, my own life is a lie and I move only because I pretend to be a real child.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241646,"modifiedTime":1783973241646,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"vA8ilNOw8Cyv0KDk","name":"Descriptor 2","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"I want to prove that I am a good boy, and that is why I strive \nto perform every task that is assigned to me. I naively tend to \ntrust adults blindly, even if I just met them.","notes":"See bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 8.","positive":"I want to prove that I am a good boy, and that is why I strive to perform every task that is assigned to me. I naively tend to trust adults blindly, even if I just met them.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241646,"modifiedTime":1783973241646,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"fFp8xXwZ41UGIB6X","name":"Lies","type":"gift","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/icon-gift.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"When you tell a lie, you can temporarily make it a \nreality. Create a Descriptor that represents your lie and concerns \nsomething about you that you pride yourself on, such as: I have the \nstrength of five men, or I can fly through the air. The Descriptor \nremains throughout the Scene, and you gain 1 Additional Success \nthe first time you use it for an action. Each time you make use of this \nGift you receive 1 Lie Token. Y our nose will grow in proportion \nto the amount of Lie Tokens you have. During the Scenario the \nStoryteller can spend 1 Lie Token to give you 1 Penalty on a Check, \ndescribing how your clumsy puppet body prevents you from \nperforming at your best. With every Lie Token spent, your nose \nshrinks closer back to normal.","notes":"See bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 8.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241646,"modifiedTime":1783973241646,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"07DD9ZbyFdsQzyFd","name":"Always in the Middle of Trouble","type":"gift","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/icon-gift.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"Once per Scene, \nwhen you face a danger or problem arising from a previous choice \nyou have made, you recover 1 Soma and get 2 XP . When you do \nwhat an NPC asks and trust them without asking questions, you \ncan discard 1 Lie Token.","notes":"See bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 8.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241646,"modifiedTime":1783973241646,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"e4wXNDY1iNUxPTRc","name":"Dark Ego - Soulless Puppet","type":"darkEgo","img":"icons/svg/terror.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"Y our body is made of wood and \nso you ignore any penalty derived from dangers that would affect a living \nbeing. Y ou receive 1 Additional Success to all your Defense Checks. Y ou \ncan communicate with other puppets or toys who can tell you something \nat the Storyteller’s discretion. If you stay still, you will pass as a common \npuppet in the eyes of those who see you and you cannot be discovered \nexcept with special skills or magic.","notes":"See bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 8.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0,"trigger":"Make obvious use of the wooden properties of your body to perform \nan action, or have your nose grow dramatically (i.e. when you accumulate \nthe third Lie Token), proving to everyone that you are not human."},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241646,"modifiedTime":1783973241646,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"X7BRUA3Wc737S8Dt","name":"A school coat","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"A school coat","notes":"See bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 8.","quantity":1},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241646,"modifiedTime":1783973241646,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"1UkFbR8SDv0EkyHa","name":"An old textbook","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"An old textbook","notes":"See bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 8.","quantity":1},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241646,"modifiedTime":1783973241646,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"Is5fjNYOMiZgjzEj","name":"A map to the famous Field of Miracles","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"A map to the famous Field of Miracles","notes":"See bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 8.","quantity":1},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241646,"modifiedTime":1783973241646,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"7gEC0yFEnDoZe5WW","name":"A small bag with some junk taken from the stomach of a fish","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"A small bag with some junk taken from the stomach of a fish","notes":"See bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 8.","quantity":1},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241646,"modifiedTime":1783973241646,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"nhiWP0UpTQGyX5ZJ","name":"A miraculous medicine, gift of a Fairy","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"A miraculous medicine, gift of a Fairy","notes":"See bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 8.","quantity":1},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241646,"modifiedTime":1783973241646,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"8kam2uGUM17FSj8E","name":"Source Sheet","type":"storyElement","img":"icons/svg/scroll.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"<p><strong>The Broken Ones</strong></p><p>bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 8.</p>","notes":"bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 8"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241646,"modifiedTime":1783973241646,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}],"effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"pregenSlug":"the-broken-ones-wound-carlo-the-livingpuppet","pregenCollection":"The Broken Ones","source":"bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf","pages":"8"}},"system":{"details":{"concept":"The Broken Ones","origin":"Wound. Carlo the LivingPuppet","role":"Hunter of the Order","notes":"<p><strong>The Broken Ones</strong></p><p>bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 8.</p>"},"resources":{"soma":{"value":6,"max":6},"xp":0,"wounds":{"value":0,"max":3},"darkness":{"value":0,"max":6}},"opposition":{"defaultLevel":5,"modifier":0},"bookmark":{"wound1":"","wound2":"","wound3":"","extraWound":""}},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241646,"modifiedTime":1783973241646,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"SGqiDf5WLWMdMXhr","name":"Hatta Carter","type":"hunter","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/avatars/pregens/the-broken-ones-hatta-carter.png","items":[{"_id":"lrSXmQoZcfrn1brH","name":"Descriptor 1","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"I am obsessed with time and when I can plan an action out, I can \ncomplete it half the time a normal person would need. Sometimes \nI lose focus on what I am doing, using twice as much time to \ncomplete the simplest actions.","notes":"See bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 10.","positive":"I am obsessed with time and when I can plan an action out, I can complete it half the time a normal person would need. Sometimes I lose focus on what I am doing, using twice as much time to complete the simplest actions.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241647,"modifiedTime":1783973241647,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"5kxos0NIGo60KqLb","name":"Descriptor 2","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"I am a good toymaker and the small automata I build can \nperform the most varied tasks. All my creations have a touch \nof my madness and sometimes they don’t work exactly as they \nshould.","notes":"See bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 10.","positive":"I am a good toymaker and the small automata I build can perform the most varied tasks. All my creations have a touch of my madness and sometimes they don’t work exactly as they should.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241647,"modifiedTime":1783973241647,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"HNUOTT0ELCLEHtOe","name":"Time Watches","type":"gift","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/icon-gift.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"When you want to use time to your \nadvantage, you can twist the stem on one of your watches and choose \nfrom the following. \n1. Slow the World Down: Receive 1 Additional Success to your \nnext Position Check.\n2. Speed up the Hatter: Y ou can act immediately (unless you \nhave already done so during the Exchange) by interrupting anyone’s \naction, regardless of what else might be happening in the narrative. \nWhen you use your watches, you gain 1 Time Token. During the \nScenario, the Storyteller can spend 1 Time Token to freeze you a few \nseconds in time and give you 2 Penalties to a Defense Check. If you \ntake an Interlude and drink some good tea, you can discard all the \nTime Tokens you have accumulated.","notes":"See bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 10.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241647,"modifiedTime":1783973241647,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"T6W8MVlS2t13rQkV","name":"Playmates","type":"gift","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/icon-gift.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"Y ou own three automated dolls, The Little \nHatter, The Hare, and The Dormouse. Each automaton can perform \nsmall tasks, such as picking up and carrying items or delivering a \nmessage. Each doll has a special ability.\nThe Little Hatter can explode, inflicting 1 Wound to everyone \nwithin ten feet of it. \nThe Hare can always find a way, even through narrow places or \nclosed doors. \nThe Dormouse can fall asleep and deactivate to discard 1 Time \nToken. \nDuring Interludes, repair all automata.","notes":"See bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 10.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241647,"modifiedTime":1783973241647,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"GHyoiegNEgKsiKJ8","name":"Dark Ego - Mad like a Hatter","type":"darkEgo","img":"icons/svg/terror.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"When you give free rein to \nyour madness, reality bends itself to prove you right. Declare something \ncrazy such as That door leads to the opposite side of town, or This pair \nof glasses allows you to see ghosts and create a Descriptor. Y our madness \nmust always concern an object and its crazy use. Y ou cannot directly affect \nor interact with living beings. Suffer 1 Wound caused by the fatigue of \nturning your madness into reality. Y our madness lasts throughout the \nScene. If at least one subject is amazed by what you do with your madness, \nyou gain 1 Soma.","notes":"See bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 10.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0,"trigger":"Behave and talk like a crazy person, not worrying about the \nreactions of those around you."},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241647,"modifiedTime":1783973241647,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"kMBhfwX91Ce06ihw","name":"A valuable and improbably tall top hat","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"A valuable and improbably tall top hat","notes":"See bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 10.","quantity":1},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241647,"modifiedTime":1783973241647,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"cmHWzGcNBH8osdgI","name":"Evening clothes","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"Evening clothes","notes":"See bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 10.","quantity":1},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241647,"modifiedTime":1783973241647,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"6TujfkMfO4NjdKBT","name":"Watchmaker’s shirts and glasses","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"Watchmaker’s shirts and glasses","notes":"See bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 10.","quantity":1},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241647,"modifiedTime":1783973241647,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"xWNad001pRz01isj","name":"A complete set of over twenty watches","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"A complete set of over twenty watches","notes":"See bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 10.","quantity":1},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241647,"modifiedTime":1783973241647,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"WcozqjpJiB74cD8Z","name":"My precious toys","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"My precious toys","notes":"See bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 10.","quantity":1},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241647,"modifiedTime":1783973241647,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"QXJ2AL5nhzbC2f6w","name":"A modified gun that can shoot multifunction bullets","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"A modified gun that can shoot multifunction bullets","notes":"See bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 10.","quantity":1},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241647,"modifiedTime":1783973241647,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"cXXyOrdSMmhIwYhR","name":"A fancy tea set","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"A fancy tea set","notes":"See bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 10.","quantity":1},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241647,"modifiedTime":1783973241647,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"uIADSqRsKFz1b9XZ","name":"Source Sheet","type":"storyElement","img":"icons/svg/scroll.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"<p><strong>The Broken Ones</strong></p><p>bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 10.</p>","notes":"bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 10"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241647,"modifiedTime":1783973241647,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}],"effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"pregenSlug":"the-broken-ones-hatta-carter","pregenCollection":"The Broken Ones","source":"bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf","pages":"10"}},"system":{"details":{"concept":"The Broken Ones","origin":"Hatta Carter","role":"Hunter of the Order","notes":"<p><strong>The Broken Ones</strong></p><p>bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 10.</p>"},"resources":{"soma":{"value":6,"max":6},"xp":0,"wounds":{"value":0,"max":3},"darkness":{"value":0,"max":6}},"opposition":{"defaultLevel":5,"modifier":0},"bookmark":{"wound1":"","wound2":"","wound3":"","extraWound":""}},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241647,"modifiedTime":1783973241647,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"xnX4tRKmyO5dpX9y","name":"The Knight with a Hundred Heads","type":"hunter","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/avatars/pregens/the-broken-ones-the-knight-with-a-hundred-heads.png","items":[{"_id":"xHdG7v74IcYm3S4b","name":"Descriptor 1","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"I am a swordsman and a Hussar knight with finely honed \ncombat skills. Ordog is more than a common horse and he \noften saved me with his magic. Sometimes I wonder who the \nreal Hunter of the Order is.","notes":"See bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 12.","positive":"I am a swordsman and a Hussar knight with finely honed combat skills. Ordog is more than a common horse and he often saved me with his magic. Sometimes I wonder who the real Hunter of the Order is.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241647,"modifiedTime":1783973241647,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"DEloYWu0jr4Ac7Dr","name":"Descriptor 2","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"I am a tenacious defender and in my previous life, I always \nstood my ground, never retreating. The memory of my loved \nones makes me melancholic and I cannot forgive those who \nhurt families.","notes":"See bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 12.","positive":"I am a tenacious defender and in my previous life, I always stood my ground, never retreating. The memory of my loved ones makes me melancholic and I cannot forgive those who hurt families.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241647,"modifiedTime":1783973241647,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"vdBIvoFvOyi5Ca4O","name":"Ordog the Trusty Horse","type":"gift","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/icon-gift.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"Ordog is a strange horseshaped entity. He can speak and is uncannily smart, but he is very \nsarcastic and capricious. Ordog will always know how to find you \nand will overcome all obstacles to reach you. When you ask for his \nhelp, Ordog will manifest his magical power and the Storyteller \nwill create a Descriptor that will allow him to do incredible things, \nsuch as fly or pass through the walls. The Storyteller has full \ncontrol of Ordog’s will and whims, so expect to have to promise \nhim something or convince him of your reasons.","notes":"See bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 12.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241647,"modifiedTime":1783973241647,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"TyAnyz31r1GLvqJk","name":"The Bridge","type":"gift","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/icon-gift.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"When you protect a place or honor an oath \nyou have taken, nothing can overwhelm you. Once per Scene, you \nmay declare an oath in which you swear to defend something and \ngain 3 Oath Tokens. As long as you act to fulfill your oath, you can \nspend 1 Token to:\n1. Resist being separated from what you are defending.\n2. Gain 1 Additional Success for a Defense Check.\n3. Inflict 1 additional Wound to an enemy, but only if this allows \nyou to eliminate them. If you do, you must decapitate them. \nIf you break your oath, the magic that animates you weakens and \nthe Storyteller gains 1 Sleep Token that they can spend at any time \nto have you automatically fail a Check.\nThe Knight with \na Hundred\nHeads","notes":"See bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 12.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241647,"modifiedTime":1783973241647,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"Wggrnkx27H9iNaPE","name":"Dark Ego - The Headless Knight","type":"darkEgo","img":"icons/svg/terror.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"Y ou are an immortal \nvengeful spirit. When you suffer your last Wound, you dissolve into \nthin air to return at the beginning of the next Scene having recovered 2","notes":"See bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 12.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0,"trigger":""},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241647,"modifiedTime":1783973241647,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"gaTCYfF83gWdv32A","name":"A worn and colorful military uniform","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"A worn and colorful military uniform","notes":"See bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 12.","quantity":1},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241647,"modifiedTime":1783973241647,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"XOVMgsjOo9sHDUl0","name":"My trusty dueling saber","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"My trusty dueling saber","notes":"See bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 12.","quantity":1},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241647,"modifiedTime":1783973241647,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"qEbXLInnBZRQR2Pa","name":"A pair of finely made guns","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"A pair of finely made guns","notes":"See bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 12.","quantity":1},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241647,"modifiedTime":1783973241647,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"eczHh7ywt477hshZ","name":"A large tricorn hat covering my head","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"A large tricorn hat covering my head","notes":"See bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 12.","quantity":1},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241647,"modifiedTime":1783973241647,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"orBhAlxSKQ2gqelx","name":"A pocket watch","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"A pocket watch","notes":"See bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 12.","quantity":1},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241647,"modifiedTime":1783973241647,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"Pv39DxLXLl31DgCx","name":"A braid of hair which belonged to the one I loved","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"A braid of hair which belonged to the one I loved","notes":"See bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 12.","quantity":1},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241647,"modifiedTime":1783973241647,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"Ooo66xVqY5WEakmo","name":"A letter from a comrade fallen in battle","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"A letter from a comrade fallen in battle","notes":"See bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 12.","quantity":1},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241647,"modifiedTime":1783973241647,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"o50xTBKaF9YduDkH","name":"A large scarf with which to wrap my face and hide my missing head","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"A large scarf with which to wrap my face and hide my missing head","notes":"See bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 12.","quantity":1},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241647,"modifiedTime":1783973241647,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"bl9yMues3PGMNgGu","name":"Source Sheet","type":"storyElement","img":"icons/svg/scroll.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"<p><strong>The Broken Ones</strong></p><p>bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 12.</p>","notes":"bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 12"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241647,"modifiedTime":1783973241647,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}],"effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"pregenSlug":"the-broken-ones-the-knight-with-a-hundred-heads","pregenCollection":"The Broken Ones","source":"bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf","pages":"12"}},"system":{"details":{"concept":"The Broken Ones","origin":"The Knight with a Hundred Heads","role":"Hunter of the Order","notes":"<p><strong>The Broken Ones</strong></p><p>bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 12.</p>"},"resources":{"soma":{"value":7,"max":7},"xp":0,"wounds":{"value":0,"max":3},"darkness":{"value":0,"max":6}},"opposition":{"defaultLevel":5,"modifier":0},"bookmark":{"wound1":"","wound2":"","wound3":"","extraWound":""}},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241647,"modifiedTime":1783973241647,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"c56zCGegdLD5DMQc","name":"Iskra the Young Wolf","type":"hunter","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/avatars/pregens/the-broken-ones-iskra-the-young-wolf.png","items":[{"_id":"BvUyqVnB2F4xAH3e","name":"Descriptor 1","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"After another year of education and training, I finally found in the Order my new pack and made the \nHunters my trusted hunting companions. I serve the Order with strength and dedication, happy to do \neverything the alpha Hunter asks of me.","notes":"See bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 14.","positive":"After another year of education and training, I finally found in the Order my new pack and made the Hunters my trusted hunting companions. I serve the Order with strength and dedication, happy to do everything the alpha Hunter asks of me.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241647,"modifiedTime":1783973241647,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"bx5DP6QAHzxHMf4b","name":"Descriptor 2","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"When I am calm, I still look like a small and helpless child \nand, thanks to this, adults tend to underestimate me. I struggle to \nbehave like a normal child, but I can’t keep my wolfish side leashed \nforever.","notes":"See bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 14.","positive":"When I am calm, I still look like a small and helpless child and, thanks to this, adults tend to underestimate me. I struggle to behave like a normal child, but I can’t keep my wolfish side leashed forever.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241647,"modifiedTime":1783973241647,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"S9j04snAvCOKwCBL","name":"Descriptor 3","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"I perform my best when I’m cooperating with my hunting \ncompanions. I quickly learn the strengths and weaknesses of the \npack. I follow every order of anyone I consider more important \nthan me within the pack, without hesitation or remorse.","notes":"See bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 14.","positive":"I perform my best when I’m cooperating with my hunting companions. I quickly learn the strengths and weaknesses of the pack. I follow every order of anyone I consider more important than me within the pack, without hesitation or remorse.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241647,"modifiedTime":1783973241647,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"rx4HRwAS8UduuaIG","name":"Dark Ego Descriptor","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"Iskra the\n Young\nWolf I am a wolf child and I defend myself with fangs and claws. My \nsense of smell is infallible. I’m young and I know little about the \nworld, so I am easily intimidated when I face something I don’t \nknow.","notes":"See bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 14.","positive":"Iskra the Young Wolf I am a wolf child and I defend myself with fangs and claws. My sense of smell is infallible. I’m young and I know little about the world, so I am easily intimidated when I face something I don’t know.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241648,"modifiedTime":1783973241648,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"fzwj3zBsNNAjwcXx","name":"The Red Hood","type":"gift","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/icon-gift.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"Y ou can spend 1 Soma to look exactly like \na common child. Create a Descriptor that contains one of the words \nPretty, Small, or Sweet. As long as you maintain your disguise, no \nadult will notice you or consider you a potential danger. Receive 2 \nAdditional Successes to the first action you take when you decide to \ndrop your disguise and reveal who you are.","notes":"See bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 14.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241648,"modifiedTime":1783973241648,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"y4ej5KaKhKoaJSH6","name":"Pack","type":"gift","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/icon-gift.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"When you coordinate and act with one or more of your \nteammates against a common threat, you both get 1 Additional Success \nfor your Position Check. At the end of the Scene, if you have resolved \na significant issue thanks to the collaboration with your companions, \nyou recover 1 Soma.\nIwas abandoned by my mother in a large forest and survived by joining a pack of werewolves. After \na year of honing my predatory skills, I tracked down the woman I once called “Mother” and sank \nmy fangs into her throat. My pack was dismantled by a group of Hunters and the Order captured me.","notes":"See bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 14.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241648,"modifiedTime":1783973241648,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"RG1dV8MWpe0nIdAA","name":"Dark Ego - The Young Wolf","type":"darkEgo","img":"icons/svg/terror.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"Unleash your feral side, ready to bite anyone who opposes your pack. If you get an Outcome with an \nIncrement on a Position Check, you can spend the Increment to take an \nadditional action immediately. Y ou can also inflict 1 Wound on yourself \nto perform an additional action after your normal action. Y ou can’t \nperform more than 3 actions per Exchange. Y ou may spend 1 Soma \nto memorize the smell of a person you are interacting with. Y ou will \nalways recognize them and it will be easy for you to follow their tracks \neven after a long time.","notes":"See bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 14.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0,"trigger":"Give free rein to your feral side or fulfill a task for your pack with your wolf skills.\nXP\nSoma\n 6"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241648,"modifiedTime":1783973241648,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"kcIX8jdPsmvBQeBR","name":"A red cape of fine workmanship, embroidered with the coat of arms of the Order","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"A red cape of fine workmanship, embroidered with the coat of arms of the Order","notes":"See bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 14.","quantity":1},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241648,"modifiedTime":1783973241648,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"W46CUmfkaLlqgPCU","name":"A wolf mask carved in wood","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"A wolf mask carved in wood","notes":"See bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 14.","quantity":1},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241648,"modifiedTime":1783973241648,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"CFiXI2IEX2d79tHW","name":"A broken clay doll, a memento of one of my few happy memories of my mother","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"A broken clay doll, a memento of one of my few happy memories of my mother","notes":"See bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 14.","quantity":1},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241648,"modifiedTime":1783973241648,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"0kaBORhnRXDFJZ1r","name":"A fang from the leader of my old pack","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"A fang from the leader of my old pack","notes":"See bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 14.","quantity":1},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241648,"modifiedTime":1783973241648,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"L6rrs33PpZeBpmbA","name":"A rag doll depicting a well-dressed girl, a gift from my beloved grandmother","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"A rag doll depicting a well-dressed girl, a gift from my beloved grandmother","notes":"See bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 14.","quantity":1},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241648,"modifiedTime":1783973241648,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"5rkFIGNay23CMcd4","name":"Source Sheet","type":"storyElement","img":"icons/svg/scroll.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"<p><strong>The Broken Ones</strong></p><p>bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 14.</p>","notes":"bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 14"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241648,"modifiedTime":1783973241648,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}],"effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"pregenSlug":"the-broken-ones-iskra-the-young-wolf","pregenCollection":"The Broken Ones","source":"bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf","pages":"14"}},"system":{"details":{"concept":"The Broken Ones","origin":"Iskra the Young Wolf","role":"Hunter of the Order","notes":"After another year of education and training, I finally found in the Order my new pack and made the \nHunters my trusted hunting companions. I serve the Order with strength and dedication, happy to do \neverything the alpha Hunter asks of me."},"resources":{"soma":{"value":6,"max":6},"xp":0,"wounds":{"value":0,"max":3},"darkness":{"value":0,"max":6}},"opposition":{"defaultLevel":5,"modifier":0},"bookmark":{"wound1":"","wound2":"","wound3":"","extraWound":""}},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241648,"modifiedTime":1783973241648,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"HNZe6qeZ9UiUjZdS","name":"The Gang of three Pigs","type":"hunter","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/avatars/pregens/the-broken-ones-the-gang-of-three-pigs.png","items":[{"_id":"o1An5fhLPpp9FFJO","name":"Descriptor 1","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"We are three brothers who renounced their names to become emissaries of the God Under the Mine. We \nwere a group of anarchists and rebels, but the Order captured us, forcing us to become Hunters. We carry with \nus the last piece of the God Under the Mine, an ancient and powerful creature. We keep the remains of the God a \nsecret so that the Order won’t get their grubby hands on it. By feeding on it, our bodies can regenerate and even \nreturn from death, effectively making our gang immortal.","notes":"See bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 16.","positive":"We are three brothers who renounced their names to become emissaries of the God Under the Mine. We were a group of anarchists and rebels, but the Order captured us, forcing us to become Hunters. We carry with us the last piece of the God Under the Mine, an ancient and powerful creature. We keep the remains of the God a secret so that the Order won’t get their grubby hands on it. By feeding on it, our bodies can regenerate and even return from death, effectively making our gang immortal.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241648,"modifiedTime":1783973241648,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"ssd0tqtX3UnZIsUK","name":"Descriptor 2","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"We are a gang and we use numerical superiority \nto overcome our human limitations. Our faces \nare always covered by a pig’s head mask, \nintimidating ordinary people.","notes":"See bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 16.","positive":"We are a gang and we use numerical superiority to overcome our human limitations. Our faces are always covered by a pig’s head mask, intimidating ordinary people.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241648,"modifiedTime":1783973241648,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"pxkviZNYvCOt8rSQ","name":"Descriptor 3","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"Thanks to the flesh of the God Under the Mine, \nour body is able to regenerate. We do not fear \npain or disease. Preserving the God’s meat is an \nobsession for us, and is more important than \nanything else.","notes":"See bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 16.","positive":"Thanks to the flesh of the God Under the Mine, our body is able to regenerate. We do not fear pain or disease. Preserving the God’s meat is an obsession for us, and is more important than anything else.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241648,"modifiedTime":1783973241648,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"nJM7GByFQUbkU2cR","name":"Dark Ego Descriptor","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"We are capable builders and there is no building that we cannot fortify or infiltrate. We \nare very protective of what we think is ours.","notes":"See bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 16.","positive":"We are capable builders and there is no building that we cannot fortify or infiltrate. We are very protective of what we think is ours.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241648,"modifiedTime":1783973241648,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"QLU0VyhtrNJnULE5","name":"Gang","type":"gift","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/icon-gift.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"Y ou can act as three independent \ncharacters using all the same Descriptors, Gifts and \nSoma. Each gang member has 1 single Wound, for a \ntotal of 3. Each of you is skilled at something.\nThe eldest gains 1 Additional Success in actions \ninvolving repairing or tampering with the \nenvironment. \nThe middle brother gains 1 Additional Success in \nactions to construct or tamper with objects.\nThe youngest gains 1 Additional Success in actions \nnot related to any kind of obligation or duty towards \nthe gang or the current mission.","notes":"See bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 16.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241648,"modifiedTime":1783973241648,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"Y89zehE9ZTpYFFdH","name":"Eating the Divine","type":"gift","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/icon-gift.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"By eating the flesh, \nyou can regenerate your bodies and even return \nfrom death. At the end of each Scene, each member \nrecovers their Wound as long as at least one of the \nBrothers is still alive to activate the power of this Gift. \nOnce per Scenario, one of you can spend 1 Soma to \nheal immediately from 1 Wound and come back to \nlife instantly.","notes":"See bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 16.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241648,"modifiedTime":1783973241648,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"QHlch76mxAEjTbI1","name":"Dark Ego - Our Home","type":"darkEgo","img":"icons/svg/terror.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"When you arrive in a new location, you can take the \ntime to examine, alter, and repair it. Y ou may use one of the following options for each \npresent gang member.\n1. Escape route: Detail a Descriptor that represents an escape route that only you \nmay open.\n2. Trap: Detail a Descriptor that describes how your trap activates and hurts intruders. \nThose who enter the perimeter will trigger it, suffering 1 Wound. Skilled and attentive \nindividuals may require a Position Check to fall into your trap.\n3. Improvement: Create a Descriptor that represents an improvement you make to \nthe environment. Y ou get 1 Additional Success when you make use of your improvement \nduring an action.\n4. Alter: Detail a Descriptor that represents a new feature of the site that only you can \nactivate.","notes":"See bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 16.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0,"trigger":"Take time to work on a location and make it your own."},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241648,"modifiedTime":1783973241648,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"WKFQQX00BpuywbmD","name":"Pig’s head masks","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"Pig’s head masks","notes":"See bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 16.","quantity":1},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241648,"modifiedTime":1783973241648,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"O470Fod0ix3cONL0","name":"Carpenter’s tool bags","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"Carpenter’s tool bags","notes":"See bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 16.","quantity":1},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241648,"modifiedTime":1783973241648,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"urNyYLOQLwzTlmIZ","name":"Lots of bricks","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"Lots of bricks","notes":"See bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 16.","quantity":1},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241648,"modifiedTime":1783973241648,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"U0eNmYVyeAFyIlMo","name":"Lots of wood","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"Lots of wood","notes":"See bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 16.","quantity":1},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241648,"modifiedTime":1783973241648,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"rrrnzs675ARtQVCM","name":"Lots of dried straw","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"Lots of dried straw","notes":"See bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 16.","quantity":1},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241648,"modifiedTime":1783973241648,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"fqDU39XcKSYVofaJ","name":"Picks and hammers","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"Picks and hammers","notes":"See bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 16.","quantity":1},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241648,"modifiedTime":1783973241648,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"eqtbHftbdYT54KA3","name":"Miners’ lanterns","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"Miners’ lanterns","notes":"See bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 16.","quantity":1},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241648,"modifiedTime":1783973241648,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"1w7LefsTOmemiALV","name":"Heavy leather work coats","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"Heavy leather work coats","notes":"See bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 16.","quantity":1},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241648,"modifiedTime":1783973241648,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"UxXS4OM6ZKMFeoFg","name":"A reinforced case containing the flesh of the God Under the Mine","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"A reinforced case containing the flesh of the God Under the Mine","notes":"See bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 16.","quantity":1},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241648,"modifiedTime":1783973241648,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"7Z2TpSKkXraPEOQw","name":"Three keys","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"Three keys","notes":"See bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 16.","quantity":1},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241648,"modifiedTime":1783973241648,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"pkrHkYwwcPOptGRy","name":"Source Sheet","type":"storyElement","img":"icons/svg/scroll.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"<p><strong>The Broken Ones</strong></p><p>bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 16.</p>","notes":"bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 16"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241648,"modifiedTime":1783973241648,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}],"effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"pregenSlug":"the-broken-ones-the-gang-of-three-pigs","pregenCollection":"The Broken Ones","source":"bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf","pages":"16"}},"system":{"details":{"concept":"The Broken Ones","origin":"The Gang of three Pigs","role":"Hunter of the Order","notes":"We are three brothers who renounced their names to become emissaries of the God Under the Mine. We \nwere a group of anarchists and rebels, but the Order captured us, forcing us to become Hunters. We carry with \nus the last piece of the God Under the Mine, an ancient and powerful creature. We keep the remains of the God a \nsecret so that the Order won’t get their grubby hands on it. By feeding on it, our bodies can regenerate and even \nreturn from death, effectively making our gang immortal."},"resources":{"soma":{"value":6,"max":6},"xp":0,"wounds":{"value":0,"max":3},"darkness":{"value":0,"max":6}},"opposition":{"defaultLevel":5,"modifier":0},"bookmark":{"wound1":"","wound2":"","wound3":"","extraWound":""}},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241648,"modifiedTime":1783973241648,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"mzuef3Aka7F7Ivdq","name":"Morgana of the Lake","type":"hunter","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/avatars/pregens/the-broken-ones-morgana-of-the-lake.png","items":[{"_id":"cj9FFtsApB7qTiKw","name":"Descriptor 1","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"I have always had an intuitive understanding of destiny. \nDreams and visions may come over me uncontrollably, giving \nme a glimpse of the right thread to follow. I often see things \nI’ d rather not and live with the pain of finding out what will \nhappen in the future of someone I care about.","notes":"See bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 18.","positive":"I have always had an intuitive understanding of destiny. Dreams and visions may come over me uncontrollably, giving me a glimpse of the right thread to follow. I often see things I’ d rather not and live with the pain of finding out what will happen in the future of someone I care about.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241649,"modifiedTime":1783973241649,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"601XIffXSf74V1Bq","name":"Descriptor 2","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"I am a skilled illusionist. Thanks to my power, I can conjure \ntricks of light and mirages. I am hopelessly attracted to mirrors \nand sleights of hand.","notes":"See bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 18.","positive":"I am a skilled illusionist. Thanks to my power, I can conjure tricks of light and mirages. I am hopelessly attracted to mirrors and sleights of hand.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241649,"modifiedTime":1783973241649,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"x1O1AMb8kGJS0z5S","name":"Weaver of Destiny","type":"gift","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/icon-gift.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"Once per Scene, you can give a goal \nto an ally, such as Defeat that enemy or Retrieve that item. As \nlong as your ally acts to fulfill the destiny you have indicated to \nthem, they get 1 Additional Success to all their actions. However, \nif at the end of the Scene you have not achieved your goal, you will \nboth suffer 1 Wound due to the magical backlash of destiny. When \nfaced with one or more choices, you can spend 1 Soma and ask the \nUniverse to help you decide. Choose a Keyword such as enemy, \ndanger, or something else and the Storyteller will tell you which \nof the possibilities in front of you is the most related to the word \nyou have chosen.","notes":"See bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 18.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241649,"modifiedTime":1783973241649,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"9mSJWBFqT2SqxSPS","name":"Illusion","type":"gift","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/icon-gift.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"Y ou may spend 1 Soma to create up to three \nillusions and move them as you like. Create a Descriptor that \nrepresents your illusions. Every illusion is a distortion of the \nvisual field. Y ou may make them more believable by adding 1 \nelement, choosing from between sound, smell, or tactility. Y our \nillusions are realistic, but they will be exposed if closely examined. \nAlternatively, you may spend 1 Soma to create three illusory \ncopies of yourself to confuse watchers. Y ou gain 3 Additional \nSuccesses for the first Defense Check you make. Y ou then subtract \n1 Additional Success (down to zero) for each additional Defense \nCheck you must take.","notes":"See bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 18.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241649,"modifiedTime":1783973241649,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"Yvux6kf9GqLndmO0","name":"Dark Ego - The Supreme Fairy","type":"darkEgo","img":"icons/svg/terror.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"Y ou can unleash your true \nfairy essence and alter reality itself. When you do this, you suffer 1 Wound \nand choose an effect:\n1. Making the Unreal a Reality: One of your illusions becomes \nreal. If necessary, the Storyteller must create an ad hoc profile.\n2. Supreme Fairy: Y ou may replicate a Gift with a magical effect you \nhave witnessed at least once during the Scenario, for the duration of the \nScene.\n3. Lady of Destiny: Y ou can change the fate of a Minor NPC by \nrewriting its Descriptor and Agenda. This may not affect particularly \npowerful NPCs or enemies, at the Storyteller’s discretion.","notes":"See bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 18.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0,"trigger":"Evoke your true potential when experiencing a strong emotion or \nwhen you find yourself in a magically charged location, and let yourself be \nflooded with power."},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241649,"modifiedTime":1783973241649,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"kuxwCyB8M9Q3cgLv","name":"A practical, street artist’s dress","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"A practical, street artist’s dress","notes":"See bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 18.","quantity":1},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241649,"modifiedTime":1783973241649,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"9NA7GRtKoq2DPfyc","name":"A silver headband, a gift from someone I have forgotten","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"A silver headband, a gift from someone I have forgotten","notes":"See bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 18.","quantity":1},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241649,"modifiedTime":1783973241649,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"9YAEz9SuFdaZQGTo","name":"A small diary where I transcribe my dreams","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"A small diary where I transcribe my dreams","notes":"See bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 18.","quantity":1},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241649,"modifiedTime":1783973241649,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"dkQiA6GQO5q4EmQn","name":"An ancient coin engraved with the word Camelot","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"An ancient coin engraved with the word Camelot","notes":"See bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 18.","quantity":1},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241649,"modifiedTime":1783973241649,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"wYzDjjR1C9iRfIlx","name":"Two wooden dolls I hold in my sleep, a witch and a warlock","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"Two wooden dolls I hold in my sleep, a witch and a warlock","notes":"See bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 18.","quantity":1},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241649,"modifiedTime":1783973241649,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"bP1UXhpW5LiBjebs","name":"Source Sheet","type":"storyElement","img":"icons/svg/scroll.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"<p><strong>The Broken Ones</strong></p><p>bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 18.</p>","notes":"bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 18"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241649,"modifiedTime":1783973241649,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}],"effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"pregenSlug":"the-broken-ones-morgana-of-the-lake","pregenCollection":"The Broken Ones","source":"bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf","pages":"18"}},"system":{"details":{"concept":"The Broken Ones","origin":"Morgana of the Lake","role":"Hunter of the Order","notes":"<p><strong>The Broken Ones</strong></p><p>bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 18.</p>"},"resources":{"soma":{"value":5,"max":5},"xp":0,"wounds":{"value":0,"max":3},"darkness":{"value":0,"max":6}},"opposition":{"defaultLevel":5,"modifier":0},"bookmark":{"wound1":"","wound2":"","wound3":"","extraWound":""}},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241649,"modifiedTime":1783973241649,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"zspv6Bhv7clRxoSQ","name":"OZena the Suffering","type":"hunter","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/avatars/pregens/the-broken-ones-ozena-the-suffering.png","items":[{"_id":"THJzid1YB2umLkmE","name":"Descriptor 1","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"Even if sometimes the memories of my “past in the future” resurface, making me homesick... What if the Order \nis deceiving me as Henkle did? Am I always meant to be just a pawn in someone else’s game?","notes":"See bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 20.","positive":"Even if sometimes the memories of my “past in the future” resurface, making me homesick... What if the Order is deceiving me as Henkle did? Am I always meant to be just a pawn in someone else’s game?","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241649,"modifiedTime":1783973241649,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"pFJ6N6d05YliUlTW","name":"Descriptor 2","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"I trained to be an efficient fighter and assassin, taking \nadvantage of the magical shoes I took from my first \nvictim. The disease that afflicts me disfigures my face and I \nam ashamed of my condition.","notes":"See bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 20.","positive":"I trained to be an efficient fighter and assassin, taking advantage of the magical shoes I took from my first victim. The disease that afflicts me disfigures my face and I am ashamed of my condition.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241649,"modifiedTime":1783973241649,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"Ksd1It3n5hLlNdYt","name":"Descriptor 3","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"I have been leading a band of followers for a long time and I \nknow how a leader should behave. I’m good at imposing my \nwill on others. Even though I am often offered loyalty, being \na stranger far from my home in time and space makes it \ndifficult to trust others.","notes":"See bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 20.","positive":"I have been leading a band of followers for a long time and I know how a leader should behave. I’m good at imposing my will on others. Even though I am often offered loyalty, being a stranger far from my home in time and space makes it difficult to trust others.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241649,"modifiedTime":1783973241649,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"OdqCfqM6aiUsmDtG","name":"Dark Ego Descriptor","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"I am a person out of her time and largely immune to those who use spells and \nmagic. I have a natural talent for fighting those who use magic. I hate witches \nand sorcerers because, despite their power, they can’t heal me.","notes":"See bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 20.","positive":"I am a person out of her time and largely immune to those who use spells and magic. I have a natural talent for fighting those who use magic. I hate witches and sorcerers because, despite their power, they can’t heal me.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241649,"modifiedTime":1783973241649,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"bUfWhfKdllpgVzzl","name":"The Silver Shoes","type":"gift","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/icon-gift.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"When you move, you can teleport \nfor short distances, and this allows you to automatically elude \nany attempt to impede or prevent your movements. Y ou need to \nsee where you intend to reappear. If you’re holding someone’s \nhand, you can spend 1 Soma to bring them with you. Once \nduring the Scenario, you may make a longer trip, even of \nseveral miles, but only to a place that you have seen at least once \nbefore.","notes":"See bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 20.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241649,"modifiedTime":1783973241649,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"9R6E7UYwYKjrFHPQ","name":"Experience of a Dark Journey","type":"gift","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/icon-gift.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"Y ou have \naccomplished many missions with strange companions and \nhave learned something from each of them. Y ou can invoke \neach of these effects once per Scenario.\n1. Tough as Tin: Ignore 1 Wound you should suffer from \nphysical damage. \n2. The Bravery of a Lion: Y ou gain 2 Additional Successes \nwhen you throw yourself against a great danger without caring \nabout the consequences.\n3. The Brain of a Genius Scarecrow: The Storyteller \nwill provide you with useful information about a place, \npersonality, or event you are dealing with. The information you \ngain is always useful to what you’re doing.\nI am a young American girl from 1939. Because of a magic tornado, I crashed into Broken Europe with a \nstrange doctor named Norman Henkle. I am suffering from a rare form of OZena, which disfigures my face \nand has blighted my life ever since I was a child. Dr. Henkle deceived me with the promise of a cure and a way \nback to my time, asking me to become a witch hunter. I committed crimes, even murders, until the Order put \nan end to my madness. I was forgiven and found in the Order a new home that I don’t want to run away from.","notes":"See bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 20.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241649,"modifiedTime":1783973241649,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"01DLuTuaTX54VIzj","name":"Dark Ego - From Another World","type":"darkEgo","img":"icons/svg/terror.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"As a creature displaced in time, you \nare naturally resistant to magic. Y ou gain 2 Additional Successes when defending \nyourself from a danger associated with magic. When you inflict 1 Wound on a \nbeing associated with magic, you prevent them from using their powers (Gifts and \nDescriptors) during their next action. Blocking the powers of particularly powerful \nopponents and Hunters may require a Position Check. When you touch a magic or \nenchanted object, you can spend 1 Soma to temporarily interrupt its power. The \nduration of this effect is decided by the Storyteller.","notes":"See bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 20.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0,"trigger":"Reveal that you’re from another time through a gesture or a word. \nAlternatively, act threatening towards a magical being."},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241649,"modifiedTime":1783973241649,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"apG8qBvhhu6KZYLn","name":"A green cape with a wide and drooping hood","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"A green cape with a wide and drooping hood","notes":"See bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 20.","quantity":1},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241649,"modifiedTime":1783973241649,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"X9kng4KmZgcU8sdh","name":"A blade of modern design","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"A blade of modern design","notes":"See bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 20.","quantity":1},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241649,"modifiedTime":1783973241649,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"11hYl9G4miyKpu0N","name":"A bag full of small objects from my time","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"A bag full of small objects from my time","notes":"See bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 20.","quantity":1},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241649,"modifiedTime":1783973241649,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"RvlfnvR8bXusntWp","name":"A mask of delicate workmanship that depicts a suffering face","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"A mask of delicate workmanship that depicts a suffering face","notes":"See bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 20.","quantity":1},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241649,"modifiedTime":1783973241649,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"g2SJQUOtioP4QnP4","name":"My trusty silver shoes","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"My trusty silver shoes","notes":"See bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 20.","quantity":1},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241649,"modifiedTime":1783973241649,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"uQn5LPthrHCmAJ1k","name":"A series of stilettos hidden in my blond hair","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"A series of stilettos hidden in my blond hair","notes":"See bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 20.","quantity":1},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241649,"modifiedTime":1783973241649,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"wMDFmqpYNzvsbjuA","name":"The medal of my dear deceased dog","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"The medal of my dear deceased dog","notes":"See bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 20.","quantity":1},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241649,"modifiedTime":1783973241649,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"47hHQiM7j5T5sPBv","name":"Source Sheet","type":"storyElement","img":"icons/svg/scroll.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"<p><strong>The Broken Ones</strong></p><p>bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 20.</p>","notes":"bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 20"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241649,"modifiedTime":1783973241649,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}],"effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"pregenSlug":"the-broken-ones-ozena-the-suffering","pregenCollection":"The Broken Ones","source":"bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf","pages":"20"}},"system":{"details":{"concept":"The Broken Ones","origin":"OZena the Suffering","role":"Hunter of the Order","notes":"Even if sometimes the memories of my “past in the future” resurface, making me homesick... What if the Order \nis deceiving me as Henkle did? Am I always meant to be just a pawn in someone else’s game?"},"resources":{"soma":{"value":6,"max":6},"xp":0,"wounds":{"value":0,"max":3},"darkness":{"value":0,"max":6}},"opposition":{"defaultLevel":5,"modifier":0},"bookmark":{"wound1":"","wound2":"","wound3":"","extraWound":""}},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241649,"modifiedTime":1783973241649,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"fh0x6pzWUMXLhzpA","name":"Sherazade the Weaver of Tales","type":"hunter","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/avatars/pregens/the-broken-ones-sherazade-the-weaver-of-tales.png","items":[{"_id":"RULHqvOhbFhj5iI1","name":"Descriptor 1","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"I hate violence in all its forms and all I wish to do is brighten people’s hearts through stories \nand poems.","notes":"See bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 22.","positive":"I hate violence in all its forms and all I wish to do is brighten people’s hearts through stories and poems.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241650,"modifiedTime":1783973241650,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"jWpXp8NGezoBu68n","name":"Descriptor 2","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"I know over a thousand stories and from each one I draw \na lesson with which to face dangers. I’ d do anything to \nlearn a new story.","notes":"See bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 22.","positive":"I know over a thousand stories and from each one I draw a lesson with which to face dangers. I’ d do anything to learn a new story.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241650,"modifiedTime":1783973241650,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"SOEMkcSdGlNUNq2I","name":"Descriptor 3","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"I know the delicate art of flattery and I know how to best \ncompliment others to make them feel good. I will not \ntolerate those who use violence.","notes":"See bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 22.","positive":"I know the delicate art of flattery and I know how to best compliment others to make them feel good. I will not tolerate those who use violence.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241650,"modifiedTime":1783973241650,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"0AfYVXeAyOVcTzuH","name":"Dark Ego Descriptor","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"Sherazade \nthe Weaver of \nTales\nMy stories become reality. Shadows, those ubiquitous reflections of \nreality, can interact with me. A life among the shadows in my bedroom \nhas made it hard for me to bear sunlight.","notes":"See bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 22.","positive":"Sherazade the Weaver of Tales My stories become reality. Shadows, those ubiquitous reflections of reality, can interact with me. A life among the shadows in my bedroom has made it hard for me to bear sunlight.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241650,"modifiedTime":1783973241650,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"k2fPQ4t08c1JCzeq","name":"The Tale","type":"gift","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/icon-gift.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"Y ou start each Scenario with 3 Story Tokens. \nOnce per Scene, you may tell a short story. If you do, spend \n1 Story Token and declare a Keyword that appears in your \nnarrative, then mark it down on your Sheet. During the \nScenario, if a Keyword you have marked is introduced during \na Scene by the Storyteller (for example, the Keyword is Soldier \nand you come across Soldiers), erase the word to get 1 XP and \n2 Additional Successes for either your next action or that of \none of your allies. When you learn an interesting new story, \nyou receive 1 Story Token.","notes":"See bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 22.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241650,"modifiedTime":1783973241650,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"EDSpX6a4QW9K4amc","name":"Words Like Honey","type":"gift","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/icon-gift.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"Y ou can speak beautiful words \nto bring out a memory, an emotion, or a fear. Spend 1 Story \nToken and choose one Keyword. Each NPC or Hunter who \nhas listened to you and is connected to the Keyword will \nbe overwhelmed by their emotions and will have to create \na relevant Descriptor and keep it throughout the Scene. \nParticularly powerful subjects and Hunters who oppose your \npower may require a Position Check. Y our allies receive 1 \nAdditional Success in the first action they take when using \nany Descriptor created by this Gift.\nI am the greatest storyteller that has ever lived, having learned my skills after serving a \nwealthy sultan for many years. I can’t remember why I left, but I suddenly found myself in \nEurope, where I used my skills against the Order and the Hunters. After my defeat, I was \nforgiven, for it was clear to my jailers that a dark force had clouded my mind. I serve the Order \nto regain my freedom, but also to find the one who corrupted my heart, forcing me to do harm.","notes":"See bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 22.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241650,"modifiedTime":1783973241650,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"l5JS02yIBQ9u1mhp","name":"Dark Ego - One Thousand and One Nights","type":"darkEgo","img":"icons/svg/terror.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"One of the \ncharacters in a story you told during the Session comes to life as a Shadow. \nCreate a Descriptor for them, ensuring it is driven to support you. The \nShadow could, for example, fly or walk on water. The Shadow thus created \nwill be at your service and will do whatever you order with an OL Medium 5 \nand 1 Wound. For each Story Token you decide to spend, you can summon \nan additional Shadow. Y our Shadows do not speak and cannot act in places \nwhere there is more light than darkness.","notes":"See bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 22.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0,"trigger":"Manifest your affinity for the shadows or tell a dark story full of \nfear and monsters.\nXP\nSoma\n 6"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241650,"modifiedTime":1783973241650,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"mF20wV3IR6wEw7D5","name":"Precious oriental dresses","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"Precious oriental dresses","notes":"See bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 22.","quantity":1},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241650,"modifiedTime":1783973241650,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"3BNWEzG3SDsZzbnY","name":"A veil of red silk with which to cover my face","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"A veil of red silk with which to cover my face","notes":"See bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 22.","quantity":1},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241650,"modifiedTime":1783973241650,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"TFePXAujqrZgNzNl","name":"A huge storybook","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"A huge storybook","notes":"See bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 22.","quantity":1},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241650,"modifiedTime":1783973241650,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"vg49b2hcsowpevkL","name":"Incense and perfumes","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"Incense and perfumes","notes":"See bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 22.","quantity":1},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241650,"modifiedTime":1783973241650,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"NGzXN2KTnGpyfKOj","name":"A bag full of gifts given by adoring nobles, who had been enthralled by the stories I told","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"A bag full of gifts given by adoring nobles, who had been enthralled by the stories I told","notes":"See bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 22.","quantity":1},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241650,"modifiedTime":1783973241650,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"zMA5dBk0Q9pZrC5k","name":"A small dagger coated with poison","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"A small dagger coated with poison","notes":"See bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 22.","quantity":1},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241650,"modifiedTime":1783973241650,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"H9LkuYPir7fBTRnf","name":"The comb with which I brushed the hair of my beloved sister","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"The comb with which I brushed the hair of my beloved sister","notes":"See bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 22.","quantity":1},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241650,"modifiedTime":1783973241650,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"0bPxGmqp242NMdcz","name":"The egg of a strange creature that was given to me as a gift by Sinbad, the Traveler of a Thousand Seas","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"The egg of a strange creature that was given to me as a gift by Sinbad, the Traveler of a Thousand Seas","notes":"See bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 22.","quantity":1},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241650,"modifiedTime":1783973241650,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"Y7dGOag8Fr2LzTki","name":"Source Sheet","type":"storyElement","img":"icons/svg/scroll.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"<p><strong>The Broken Ones</strong></p><p>bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 22.</p>","notes":"bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 22"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241650,"modifiedTime":1783973241650,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}],"effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"pregenSlug":"the-broken-ones-sherazade-the-weaver-of-tales","pregenCollection":"The Broken Ones","source":"bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf","pages":"22"}},"system":{"details":{"concept":"The Broken Ones","origin":"Sherazade the Weaver of Tales","role":"Hunter of the Order","notes":"I hate violence in all its forms and all I wish to do is brighten people’s hearts through stories \nand poems."},"resources":{"soma":{"value":6,"max":6},"xp":0,"wounds":{"value":0,"max":3},"darkness":{"value":0,"max":6}},"opposition":{"defaultLevel":5,"modifier":0},"bookmark":{"wound1":"","wound2":"","wound3":"","extraWound":""}},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241650,"modifiedTime":1783973241650,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"DFhpwIxDX7t7Bfc2","name":"Talia the Sleeper","type":"hunter","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/avatars/pregens/the-broken-ones-talia-the-sleeper.png","items":[{"_id":"rYhRbW2iQ1wPiTTa","name":"Descriptor 1","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"I am a cursed daughter, born from a forbidden love, destined to sleep forever. However, \nmy mind is alert and I perceive what is happening in the world around me. The curse that \nafflicts me allows me to manipulate objects, which is why the Order kept me alive after saving \nme from the castle that was my home and prison. As a Hunter, I am committed to ending \ninjustice and I hope to find a cure for my curse. However, the only thing I truly wish to find is \nsomeone who won’t break my heart.","notes":"See bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 24.","positive":"I am a cursed daughter, born from a forbidden love, destined to sleep forever. However, my mind is alert and I perceive what is happening in the world around me. The curse that afflicts me allows me to manipulate objects, which is why the Order kept me alive after saving me from the castle that was my home and prison. As a Hunter, I am committed to ending injustice and I hope to find a cure for my curse. However, the only thing I truly wish to find is someone who won’t break my heart.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241650,"modifiedTime":1783973241650,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"O56Uc0WUsSUOnoi8","name":"Descriptor 2","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"My body floats, carried by my power, ignoring obstacles of all \nkinds. I can use my very long hair as if it were my hands. I \ntravel in a heavy nun’s habit and wear a mask to hide my true \ncondition from the world.","notes":"See bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 24.","positive":"My body floats, carried by my power, ignoring obstacles of all kinds. I can use my very long hair as if it were my hands. I travel in a heavy nun’s habit and wear a mask to hide my true condition from the world.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241650,"modifiedTime":1783973241650,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"uZakjT9eq0DQ9H48","name":"Descriptor 3","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"I can communicate with those who are asleep or \nunderstand their desires and fears through dreams. I hate \nit when there are too many people around. The buzz of their \nlives reminds me of what I can’t have.","notes":"See bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 24.","positive":"I can communicate with those who are asleep or understand their desires and fears through dreams. I hate it when there are too many people around. The buzz of their lives reminds me of what I can’t have.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241650,"modifiedTime":1783973241650,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"4SYJF1EOcEaq23VW","name":"Dark Ego Descriptor","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"I can move objects with the power of thought alone. Through this power, \nI am able to manifest my presence in the world. My real body is immobile \nand locked in eternal sleep, at the mercy of the world. I long for the \nleast caress, which would remind me of being alive.","notes":"See bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 24.","positive":"I can move objects with the power of thought alone. Through this power, I am able to manifest my presence in the world. My real body is immobile and locked in eternal sleep, at the mercy of the world. I long for the least caress, which would remind me of being alive.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241650,"modifiedTime":1783973241650,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"6YmYNdNpQH5ZrIWE","name":"The Cloak","type":"gift","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/icon-gift.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"Y our large nun’s cloak floats to defend you from \nthe world and contains many small items that you can manipulate. \nThanks to this Gift you are able to float and hover in the air, but \nalways at a speed equal to the pace of a human. Once per Scene, \nyou may:\n1. Hide an object inside your cloak, hiding it from everyone (even \nwhen searching through magic).\n2. Extract from your cloak an object that you need. It can be rare \nand peculiar, but not magic or unique.","notes":"See bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 24.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241650,"modifiedTime":1783973241650,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"DjG1TOTxy9sJWAl8","name":"In the Dream","type":"gift","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/icon-gift.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"Once per Scene, you can freely \ncommunicate with a subject who is unconscious through a \ndream. Alternatively, you may choose to spend 1 Soma to “read” \nthe dreams of a conscious subject. The Storyteller will reveal all or \npart of the subject’s Agenda to you through the narration of one \nof their dreams. Particularly powerful subjects and Hunters may \nrequire a Position Check to be able to capture their dreams.","notes":"See bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 24.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241650,"modifiedTime":1783973241650,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"TVpgljs2sjfwXLn9","name":"Dark Ego - The Sleeping Will","type":"darkEgo","img":"icons/svg/terror.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"Y ou can use your power to \nmanipulate the objects around you. Y ou can make small items float or \nthrow them like weapons. Y ou can affect your surroundings up to 30 feet \naway. Y ou can act up to 3 times in an Exchange, manipulating the world \naround you, but you cannot act more than once against the same target. \nOnce per Scene, you can focus all 3 actions on a single large object (like a \nhouse) and manipulate it to your liking.","notes":"See bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 24.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0,"trigger":"Shed your cloak, revealing your helpless body or exposing yourself \nto others by manipulating the world around you."},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241650,"modifiedTime":1783973241650,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"BLQIqhCneQRoGbh6","name":"A large nun’s cloak","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"A large nun’s cloak","notes":"See bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 24.","quantity":1},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241650,"modifiedTime":1783973241650,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"B7F2985IGVepf44b","name":"A long hood with a veil hiding my face","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"A long hood with a veil hiding my face","notes":"See bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 24.","quantity":1},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241650,"modifiedTime":1783973241650,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"JJ5i6zBLBq1MkWIC","name":"Objects and small things that float under my cloak","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"Objects and small things that float under my cloak","notes":"See bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 24.","quantity":1},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241650,"modifiedTime":1783973241650,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"C22o1w61TWK8sHEO","name":"A piece of ivy that has remained clinging to my left arm","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"A piece of ivy that has remained clinging to my left arm","notes":"See bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 24.","quantity":1},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241650,"modifiedTime":1783973241650,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"aDnHZPlDQIT0a4AL","name":"The diary in which I wrote about my sad life before the curse","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"The diary in which I wrote about my sad life before the curse","notes":"See bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 24.","quantity":1},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241651,"modifiedTime":1783973241651,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"7pBkMjDSWYQ41hCM","name":"Source Sheet","type":"storyElement","img":"icons/svg/scroll.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"<p><strong>The Broken Ones</strong></p><p>bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 24.</p>","notes":"bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 24"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241651,"modifiedTime":1783973241651,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}],"effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"pregenSlug":"the-broken-ones-talia-the-sleeper","pregenCollection":"The Broken Ones","source":"bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf","pages":"24"}},"system":{"details":{"concept":"The Broken Ones","origin":"Talia the Sleeper","role":"Hunter of the Order","notes":"I am a cursed daughter, born from a forbidden love, destined to sleep forever. However, \nmy mind is alert and I perceive what is happening in the world around me. The curse that \nafflicts me allows me to manipulate objects, which is why the Order kept me alive after saving \nme from the castle that was my home and prison. As a Hunter, I am committed to ending \ninjustice and I hope to find a cure for my curse. However, the only thing I truly wish to find is \nsomeone who won’t break my heart."},"resources":{"soma":{"value":7,"max":7},"xp":0,"wounds":{"value":0,"max":3},"darkness":{"value":0,"max":6}},"opposition":{"defaultLevel":5,"modifier":0},"bookmark":{"wound1":"","wound2":"","wound3":"","extraWound":""}},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241651,"modifiedTime":1783973241651,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"M9YZNVHZzJ7NAmbo","name":"Yvonne of the Dark","type":"hunter","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/avatars/pregens/the-broken-ones-yvonne-of-the-dark.png","items":[{"_id":"KxdpWVJSRNIR410X","name":"Descriptor 1","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"I died with my beloved candles in my hand and \nwas reborn with the power to control fire. I hate \nstaying in the darkness and I always want at least \na small source of light.","notes":"See bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 26.","positive":"I died with my beloved candles in my hand and was reborn with the power to control fire. I hate staying in the darkness and I always want at least a small source of light.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241651,"modifiedTime":1783973241651,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"sD7e1baguX895RkY","name":"Descriptor 2","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"I have no choice but to remain in my childish \nbody for eternity. I have a sweet smile and \npeople often feel protective towards me. Animals \nperceive me for who I really am and they act up \nin my presence.","notes":"See bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 26.","positive":"I have no choice but to remain in my childish body for eternity. I have a sweet smile and people often feel protective towards me. Animals perceive me for who I really am and they act up in my presence.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241651,"modifiedTime":1783973241651,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"THbScmOrdMv8RZBN","name":"Light the Flame","type":"gift","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/icon-gift.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"Y ou can manipulate fire, as \nlong as there is already a flame in the environment. \nDecide whether to increase or decrease its size or \nintensity, as well as the direction it burns. Y ou can \nalso manipulate the flame to hit something within \nnine feet of it. Y ou gain 1 Additional Success to each \naction you take while manipulating fire. The first time \nyou use this Gift in a Scene, the Storyteller may decide \nthat your action will spread the flames in some way.","notes":"See bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 26.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241651,"modifiedTime":1783973241651,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"0rABW0VedKU8zMBv","name":"Innocent Smile","type":"gift","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/icon-gift.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"When you talk to someone, \nyou can spend 1 Soma to provoke their sympathy (the \nStoryteller will evaluate whether or not the subject is \nsensitive to your influence) to create an Agenda in \nwhich the target feels somehow responsible for you. \nDuring a Scene, if the location is crowded, you can \nact or move without anyone noticing.","notes":"See bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 26.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241651,"modifiedTime":1783973241651,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"v8NdPwxOWEf8Dn3g","name":"Dark Ego – Solitary Ghost","type":"darkEgo","img":"icons/svg/terror.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"When you decide to take on your ghostly \nform, you receive 1 Solitude Token and become intangible. Y ou cannot have any kind \nof physical interaction with the world (not even talking) and no one can touch you, \nexcept through magic. However, you do not become invisible to the human eye and so \nthose who see you will understand that you are a ghost. In the form of a specter, your \naffinity to fire is more intense and you gain 1 Additional Success in any action involving \nthe flames you are manipulating. In addition, you can spend 1 Soma to ignite a flame \nfrom thin air and set something on fire. The effect of this Gift lasts until you decide to \nstop it, but the Storyteller can spend 1 Solitude Token to force you to remain ethereal \nfor a few more minutes. When you take an Interlude or spend time with someone who cares about you, remove all Solitude Tokens. When you use this Gift without satisfying \nthe Activator, you can ignore the Wound and take 1 Solitude Token instead.","notes":"See bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 26.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0,"trigger":"React angrily when the world ignores you or makes it clear to you that no one cares about you."},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241651,"modifiedTime":1783973241651,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"55XppiujrtVVlCqf","name":"A worn-out cape","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"A worn-out cape","notes":"See bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 26.","quantity":1},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241651,"modifiedTime":1783973241651,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"Nrfwes4e5Wz1inUI","name":"A bag full of candles","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"A bag full of candles","notes":"See bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 26.","quantity":1},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241651,"modifiedTime":1783973241651,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"syGwae9oXW2gy1Nw","name":"A tinderbox and dry sticks","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"A tinderbox and dry sticks","notes":"See bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 26.","quantity":1},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241651,"modifiedTime":1783973241651,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"wR7cdb7sQRAb0qWR","name":"Alcohol and other flammable substances","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"Alcohol and other flammable substances","notes":"See bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 26.","quantity":1},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241651,"modifiedTime":1783973241651,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"wYHsBdwcSJDls4PH","name":"Some coins received as charity","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"Some coins received as charity","notes":"See bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 26.","quantity":1},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241651,"modifiedTime":1783973241651,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"no6qDZFO5wh4Ks1k","name":"A small rosary donated by someone I don’t remember","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"A small rosary donated by someone I don’t remember","notes":"See bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 26.","quantity":1},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241651,"modifiedTime":1783973241651,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"IXIavzoOz0D3MBtF","name":"Source Sheet","type":"storyElement","img":"icons/svg/scroll.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"<p><strong>The Broken Ones</strong></p><p>bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 26.</p>","notes":"bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 26"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241651,"modifiedTime":1783973241651,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}],"effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"pregenSlug":"the-broken-ones-yvonne-of-the-dark","pregenCollection":"The Broken Ones","source":"bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf","pages":"26"}},"system":{"details":{"concept":"The Broken Ones","origin":"Yvonne of the Dark","role":"Spirit Hunter","notes":"<p><strong>The Broken Ones</strong></p><p>bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 26.</p>"},"resources":{"soma":{"value":6,"max":6},"xp":0,"wounds":{"value":0,"max":3},"darkness":{"value":0,"max":6}},"opposition":{"defaultLevel":5,"modifier":0},"bookmark":{"wound1":"","wound2":"","wound3":"","extraWound":""}},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241651,"modifiedTime":1783973241651,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"ea2QBaJsgMhAwSor","name":"Miss Snow and Lady Storm","type":"hunter","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/avatars/pregens/lost-stories-miss-snow-and-lady-storm.png","items":[{"_id":"TNuFjoXJ94GuttZa","name":"Descriptor 1","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"Y ou can spend 1 Soma when you use this Gift to blow a kiss to the target, \nthus avoiding physical contact.","notes":"See bt-ls-hunters-sheets-1.2-eng-BASE-SCREEN.pdf, pages 2.","positive":"Y ou can spend 1 Soma when you use this Gift to blow a kiss to the target, thus avoiding physical contact.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241651,"modifiedTime":1783973241651,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"V0uncA5fuNXKqmaV","name":"Descriptor 2","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"I am a novice a powerful sorceress with limited power total control \nover cold and snow. My magic can come with dangerous, unintended \nconsequences cause small unwanted effects.","notes":"See bt-ls-hunters-sheets-1.2-eng-BASE-SCREEN.pdf, pages 2.","positive":"I am a novice a powerful sorceress with limited power total control over cold and snow. My magic can come with dangerous, unintended consequences cause small unwanted effects.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241651,"modifiedTime":1783973241651,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"fDTs5jdC8jBrGwKQ","name":"Descriptor 3","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"I am good at understanding dominating people. I have a unique \nability to comprehend their desires. I tend to distrust even close allies \ntrust those I don’t know.","notes":"See bt-ls-hunters-sheets-1.2-eng-BASE-SCREEN.pdf, pages 2.","positive":"I am good at understanding dominating people. I have a unique ability to comprehend their desires. I tend to distrust even close allies trust those I don’t know.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241651,"modifiedTime":1783973241651,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"NFZ2QilmZqiwekwA","name":"Dark Ego Descriptor","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"Cold and frost have no effect on me are extensions of my soul and I feel \na great affinity for winter. My heart of pure ice delights is easily touched \nwhen I see others suffer.","notes":"See bt-ls-hunters-sheets-1.2-eng-BASE-SCREEN.pdf, pages 2.","positive":"Cold and frost have no effect on me are extensions of my soul and I feel a great affinity for winter. My heart of pure ice delights is easily touched when I see others suffer.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241651,"modifiedTime":1783973241651,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"Fsk1eT2UTyBMPvgz","name":"Snow Sorceress","type":"gift","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/icon-gift.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"Y ou can use magic to create and manipulate the \ncold. Describe the effects of a spell that has one of the following Keywords \nas a condition: Ice, Snow, or Frost. Y ou could, for example, Create an Ice \nBridge to cross a crevasse or Freeze an Enemy to immobilize it. Pay a cost \nof 1 to 3 Soma, decided by the Storyteller, to activate the spell. The effects \nyou describe last until the end of the Scene. The Soma cost is increased by \n1 when environmental conditions are not compatible with cold. Y ou can \ndecide to lower the cost of the spell by 1 Soma, but this will cause a minor \nmagical accident on par with an Outcome with a Cost.","notes":"See bt-ls-hunters-sheets-1.2-eng-BASE-SCREEN.pdf, pages 2.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241651,"modifiedTime":1783973241651,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"r8WQ89D0qN7THtqV","name":"Winter’s Kiss","type":"gift","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/icon-gift.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"In you lies the power of winter. When you give \nsomeone a chaste kiss, you can choose one of the following effects:\n1. Erase one of their memories. It must be the memory of an event in the \nScene in which you use this effect. Particularly capable Hunters and \nNPCs may require a Position Check for the effect to succeed.\n2. Make the subject immune to cold throughout the rest of the Scene. \nThis will prevent them from suffering frost Wounds and allow them to \nignore the effects of Lady Storm’s snowstorm.\n3. Make an object extremely fragile.","notes":"See bt-ls-hunters-sheets-1.2-eng-BASE-SCREEN.pdf, pages 2.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241651,"modifiedTime":1783973241651,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"30lU6qMUbXIkkkWO","name":"Dark Ego - Snow Queen","type":"darkEgo","img":"icons/svg/terror.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"The tiny fragment of a magic mirror lies in \nyour right eye, relegating the real you to oblivion. But when tears warm your \neyes, or you hear the word that represents your dominion over the cold, Lady \nStorm comes to her senses and woe to those who stand before her.\nWhile you are Lady Storm, you can lower the Soma cost of Snow Sorceress \nby 1 without creating magical accidents. In addition, you can use Winter’s \nKiss at a distance without spending Soma. If you wish, you can summon a \nsnowstorm that will sweep over your location regardless of previous weather \nconditions. Inside the storm, visibility is reduced to about three feet, and all \ninvolved lower their OL by 1 for each action. While the snowstorm rages, you \ncan use the Gift Winter’s Kiss as a free action once per Exchange. This Gift \nends, and the Hunter becomes Miss Snow once more as soon as you suffer 1 \nWound, or at the end of the Scene.","notes":"See bt-ls-hunters-sheets-1.2-eng-BASE-SCREEN.pdf, pages 2.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0,"trigger":"Cry over something that genuinely moved you. You hear the word \n“Eternity” spoken by someone who is not aware that it will awaken Lady Storm."},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241651,"modifiedTime":1783973241651,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"0zvS5szPceG65dNG","name":"A brooch in the shape of a sleigh","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"A brooch in the shape of a sleigh","notes":"See bt-ls-hunters-sheets-1.2-eng-BASE-SCREEN.pdf, pages 2.","quantity":1},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241651,"modifiedTime":1783973241651,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"kSn852d8RINUFKFI","name":"A small knife with a blade made of ice that never melts","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"A small knife with a blade made of ice that never melts","notes":"See bt-ls-hunters-sheets-1.2-eng-BASE-SCREEN.pdf, pages 2.","quantity":1},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241651,"modifiedTime":1783973241651,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"L9PgFvZOx6zQuPO1","name":"A large key to a castle whose location you ignore","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"A large key to a castle whose location you ignore","notes":"See bt-ls-hunters-sheets-1.2-eng-BASE-SCREEN.pdf, pages 2.","quantity":1},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241651,"modifiedTime":1783973241651,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"pdhbYgEgh8DSA4t6","name":"Spellbooks","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"Spellbooks","notes":"See bt-ls-hunters-sheets-1.2-eng-BASE-SCREEN.pdf, pages 2.","quantity":1},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241651,"modifiedTime":1783973241651,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"7flv7TYkTKgOrXoN","name":"A mirror fragment with a strange magical aura","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"A mirror fragment with a strange magical aura","notes":"See bt-ls-hunters-sheets-1.2-eng-BASE-SCREEN.pdf, pages 2.","quantity":1},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241651,"modifiedTime":1783973241651,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"Mr93vM5Cx97am8wA","name":"Source Sheet","type":"storyElement","img":"icons/svg/scroll.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"<p><strong>Lost Stories</strong></p><p>bt-ls-hunters-sheets-1.2-eng-BASE-SCREEN.pdf, pages 2.</p>","notes":"bt-ls-hunters-sheets-1.2-eng-BASE-SCREEN.pdf, pages 2"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241651,"modifiedTime":1783973241651,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}],"effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"pregenSlug":"lost-stories-miss-snow-and-lady-storm","pregenCollection":"Lost Stories","source":"bt-ls-hunters-sheets-1.2-eng-BASE-SCREEN.pdf","pages":"2"}},"system":{"details":{"concept":"Lost Stories","origin":"Miss Snow and Lady Storm","role":"Hunter of the Order","notes":"Y ou can spend 1 Soma when you use this Gift to blow a kiss to the target, \nthus avoiding physical contact."},"resources":{"soma":{"value":6,"max":6},"xp":0,"wounds":{"value":0,"max":3},"darkness":{"value":0,"max":6}},"opposition":{"defaultLevel":5,"modifier":0},"bookmark":{"wound1":"","wound2":"","wound3":"","extraWound":""}},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241651,"modifiedTime":1783973241651,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"ZBBwHH25anyLNABr","name":"Tremoteus Rumpel","type":"hunter","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/avatars/pregens/lost-stories-tremoteus-rumpel.png","items":[{"_id":"1XWLJUO1whsXm33S","name":"Descriptor 1","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"I have an encyclopedic memory and there is no law that I don’t \nknow. I hate to break the rules.","notes":"See bt-ls-hunters-sheets-1.2-eng-BASE-SCREEN.pdf, pages 4.","positive":"I have an encyclopedic memory and there is no law that I don’t know. I hate to break the rules.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241651,"modifiedTime":1783973241651,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"SAumJIKQDwj8zTcX","name":"Descriptor 2","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"My reputation precedes me, and my word is held in the highest \nregard by anyone with an ounce of honesty. I detest criminals and \nthose who act to harm the innocent. Big or small, a crime is still \na crime.","notes":"See bt-ls-hunters-sheets-1.2-eng-BASE-SCREEN.pdf, pages 4.","positive":"My reputation precedes me, and my word is held in the highest regard by anyone with an ounce of honesty. I detest criminals and those who act to harm the innocent. Big or small, a crime is still a crime.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241651,"modifiedTime":1783973241651,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"Yabjvt5PSw2HQBdJ","name":"Descriptor 3","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"I am a keen disputant and have an uncanny ability to detect \ndeception. I need hard evidence before I’ll accuse someone of \ndishonesty.","notes":"See bt-ls-hunters-sheets-1.2-eng-BASE-SCREEN.pdf, pages 4.","positive":"I am a keen disputant and have an uncanny ability to detect deception. I need hard evidence before I’ll accuse someone of dishonesty.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241651,"modifiedTime":1783973241651,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"amWtPe4E69ZnTn4z","name":"Examine the Evidence","type":"gift","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/icon-gift.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"Y ou can use each of the following effects \nonce per Scene: \n1. For the Record: Y ou can make a note of something a subject has said; \nyou will never forget it. Write it down because you can use it when you \nactivate your Dark Ego. By spending 1 Soma, the Storyteller will reveal a \nweakness of the subject whose words you have memorized.\n2. Consult the Laws: The Storyteller will reveal to you the customs and \nrules of a social group or place you are in. By spending 1 Soma, you \ncan create a loophole, known only to you, to the rules that have been \nrevealed.\n3. The Decisive Proof: When you examine an object, the Storyteller \nwill reveal a quality or feature that few people may notice. By spending \n1 Soma, you will learn who was the last person to own or use what you \nare examining.","notes":"See bt-ls-hunters-sheets-1.2-eng-BASE-SCREEN.pdf, pages 4.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241651,"modifiedTime":1783973241651,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"EbcJ69jV7tLgWIwA","name":"Your Honor","type":"gift","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/icon-gift.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"If you stand in front of nobles, lawmen, or leaders in \ngeneral, you can spend 1 Soma to have them recognize your name or \nreputation. If you use your identity as a strength, you gain 1 Additional \nSuccess. If you give your word in a negotiation, you gain 1 Additional \nSuccess in a possible Position Check.","notes":"See bt-ls-hunters-sheets-1.2-eng-BASE-SCREEN.pdf, pages 4.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241652,"modifiedTime":1783973241652,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"rkYkGy50uqAWHBtU","name":"Dark Ego - Shattered Pact","type":"darkEgo","img":"icons/svg/terror.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"Those who break the rules must be \npunished. Y ou gain 1 Additional Success on all Position and Defense \nChecks you make against a subject who’s acting in a way that contradicts \nthe statement you recorded using the For the Record effect. If you act \nto harm them, you also inflict 1 Additional Wound. Once per Scene, if \na subject reveals themselves as they really are, as opposed to how they \npreviously presented themselves, or if they break their word, you can \nlecture them on their dishonesty. All your companions gain 1 Additional \nSuccess on their next action.","notes":"See bt-ls-hunters-sheets-1.2-eng-BASE-SCREEN.pdf, pages 4.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0,"trigger":"Make an argument against the guilty by pointing out their \nmisdeeds."},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241652,"modifiedTime":1783973241652,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"SToA5y65uyNxz2Ul","name":"A long lawyer’s robe","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"A long lawyer’s robe","notes":"See bt-ls-hunters-sheets-1.2-eng-BASE-SCREEN.pdf, pages 4.","quantity":1},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241652,"modifiedTime":1783973241652,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"1S6ozQh0S1yrznXx","name":"A magnifying glass","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"A magnifying glass","notes":"See bt-ls-hunters-sheets-1.2-eng-BASE-SCREEN.pdf, pages 4.","quantity":1},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241652,"modifiedTime":1783973241652,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"jO4wLWueoEH6KbeL","name":"Documents and deeds from over a hundred trials","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"Documents and deeds from over a hundred trials","notes":"See bt-ls-hunters-sheets-1.2-eng-BASE-SCREEN.pdf, pages 4.","quantity":1},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241652,"modifiedTime":1783973241652,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"X4sDMGP1WBEJsxXG","name":"A fine dueling sword","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"A fine dueling sword","notes":"See bt-ls-hunters-sheets-1.2-eng-BASE-SCREEN.pdf, pages 4.","quantity":1},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241652,"modifiedTime":1783973241652,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"hJ0zzp2uUGqVH8op","name":"Property deeds and bank deposits","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"Property deeds and bank deposits","notes":"See bt-ls-hunters-sheets-1.2-eng-BASE-SCREEN.pdf, pages 4.","quantity":1},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241652,"modifiedTime":1783973241652,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"fsNMOrJIBZ1IQCCS","name":"A ring of little value given to me by my first client","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"A ring of little value given to me by my first client","notes":"See bt-ls-hunters-sheets-1.2-eng-BASE-SCREEN.pdf, pages 4.","quantity":1},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241652,"modifiedTime":1783973241652,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"AfTeGhMnm57B6ucI","name":"A scroll of recommendations written by the Pope himself","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"A scroll of recommendations written by the Pope himself","notes":"See bt-ls-hunters-sheets-1.2-eng-BASE-SCREEN.pdf, pages 4.","quantity":1},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241652,"modifiedTime":1783973241652,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"ILjYQUQGAx7kKy71","name":"Source Sheet","type":"storyElement","img":"icons/svg/scroll.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"<p><strong>Lost Stories</strong></p><p>bt-ls-hunters-sheets-1.2-eng-BASE-SCREEN.pdf, pages 4.</p>","notes":"bt-ls-hunters-sheets-1.2-eng-BASE-SCREEN.pdf, pages 4"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241652,"modifiedTime":1783973241652,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}],"effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"pregenSlug":"lost-stories-tremoteus-rumpel","pregenCollection":"Lost Stories","source":"bt-ls-hunters-sheets-1.2-eng-BASE-SCREEN.pdf","pages":"4"}},"system":{"details":{"concept":"Lost Stories","origin":"Tremoteus Rumpel","role":"Hunter of the Order","notes":"<p><strong>Lost Stories</strong></p><p>bt-ls-hunters-sheets-1.2-eng-BASE-SCREEN.pdf, pages 4.</p>"},"resources":{"soma":{"value":6,"max":6},"xp":0,"wounds":{"value":0,"max":3},"darkness":{"value":0,"max":6}},"opposition":{"defaultLevel":5,"modifier":0},"bookmark":{"wound1":"","wound2":"","wound3":"","extraWound":""}},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241652,"modifiedTime":1783973241652,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"IQr4MjdbDfExWJWs","name":"Prince Trollo the Innocent","type":"hunter","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/avatars/pregens/lost-stories-prince-trollo-the-innocent.png","items":[{"_id":"dY80l1s95VQAIAcj","name":"Descriptor 1","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"Y ou gain 1 Additional Success for each Check you make when trying \nto persuade someone to do the right thing. Once per Scenario, if you \nsuffer 1 Wound to stand up for what you believe in, you set an example \nfor those who help you. Each ally recovers 1 Soma, and a target of your \nchoice (Hunter or NPC) immediately gains an additional action they \nmust use to try to help you or get you to safety.","notes":"See bt-ls-hunters-sheets-1.2-eng-BASE-SCREEN.pdf, pages 6.","positive":"Y ou gain 1 Additional Success for each Check you make when trying to persuade someone to do the right thing. Once per Scenario, if you suffer 1 Wound to stand up for what you believe in, you set an example for those who help you. Each ally recovers 1 Soma, and a target of your choice (Hunter or NPC) immediately gains an additional action they must use to try to help you or get you to safety.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241652,"modifiedTime":1783973241652,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"UB2KBfUOVydJBszp","name":"Descriptor 2","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"I am a young prince, well-versed in the etiquette of the court. I \nam a diligent student, my favorite subjects being history and \npoetry. I am not ashamed of my strange appearance and I hate to \nhide from others.","notes":"See bt-ls-hunters-sheets-1.2-eng-BASE-SCREEN.pdf, pages 6.","positive":"I am a young prince, well-versed in the etiquette of the court. I am a diligent student, my favorite subjects being history and poetry. I am not ashamed of my strange appearance and I hate to hide from others.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241652,"modifiedTime":1783973241652,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"lqCGS9eVYqExX3rP","name":"Descriptor 3","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"I use these qualities to uphold the good name of my family. I will \nnot allow anyone to violate the ideals of justice and courage with \nwhich I was raised.","notes":"See bt-ls-hunters-sheets-1.2-eng-BASE-SCREEN.pdf, pages 6.","positive":"I use these qualities to uphold the good name of my family. I will not allow anyone to violate the ideals of justice and courage with which I was raised.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241652,"modifiedTime":1783973241652,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"vERhvFJOJPMZElHR","name":"Dark Ego Descriptor","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"I have strange powers, and my body is stronger and more resilient \nthan an ordinary child’s. While I’m not ashamed of my \nappearance, these uncanny abilities mark me as different, and I \ntry not to attract attention when I use my power.","notes":"See bt-ls-hunters-sheets-1.2-eng-BASE-SCREEN.pdf, pages 6.","positive":"I have strange powers, and my body is stronger and more resilient than an ordinary child’s. While I’m not ashamed of my appearance, these uncanny abilities mark me as different, and I try not to attract attention when I use my power.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241652,"modifiedTime":1783973241652,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"EB687YBUG5Tie0jk","name":"Noble Birth","type":"gift","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/icon-gift.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"Once per Scene, if you are in a place where your family’s \nauthority is recognized, you can gain access to a restricted location, such \nas a dungeon or castle, or a direct audience with an authority figure. \nAs a prince, you have learned everything a future ruler needs to know. \nOnce per Scene, you gain 2 Additional Successes for an action in which \nyou can demonstrate your knowledge of history and poetry, or your skill \nwith the sword. \nI learned kindness from my mother and firmness from my father.","notes":"See bt-ls-hunters-sheets-1.2-eng-BASE-SCREEN.pdf, pages 6.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241652,"modifiedTime":1783973241652,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"Vhp3NZWzWuZvwskH","name":"Good Heart","type":"gift","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/icon-gift.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"Y ou have the innocence and strength of a true ruler.","notes":"See bt-ls-hunters-sheets-1.2-eng-BASE-SCREEN.pdf, pages 6.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241652,"modifiedTime":1783973241652,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"Si3HofAoyFRqcHro","name":"Dark Ego - Oknytt’s Legacy","type":"darkEgo","img":"icons/svg/terror.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"Y ou appeal to your Dark Ego to gain \ngreat powers. If it is day, you must spend 1 Soma. If you have no Soma, \nyou take 1 Wound. If it is night, there is no cost to activate this Gift, as \nyou are a creature of the night. Y ou gain the following powers:\n1. Yellow Eyes: See perfectly in total darkness. Once per Scene, you can \nsee a target for what they really are, unmasking any disguise they may \nbe wearing. \n2. Troll Strength: Once per Scene, you can perform an act of unprecedented strength by lifting or moving a weight equal to ten men. If you \nuse your strength to harm someone, you inflict 1 Additional Wound. \n3. Stone Skin: Once per Scene, you can suffer an attack or hazard while \navoiding any Wounds. Y ou can resist almost everything, including fire, \nfalls, and weapons. Only magic can harm you. Y ou must declare the use \nof this effect before any Defense Check.","notes":"See bt-ls-hunters-sheets-1.2-eng-BASE-SCREEN.pdf, pages 6.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0,"trigger":"You tap into your heritage in front of someone you have helped \nbefore and who is unaware of your true nature."},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241652,"modifiedTime":1783973241652,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"ioVLZx9VtweDeRNP","name":"Clothes of fine workmanship","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"Clothes of fine workmanship","notes":"See bt-ls-hunters-sheets-1.2-eng-BASE-SCREEN.pdf, pages 6.","quantity":1},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241652,"modifiedTime":1783973241652,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"Y7TWuzz1WBezbn6q","name":"A small wooden crown painted with gold, given to me by my father","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"A small wooden crown painted with gold, given to me by my father","notes":"See bt-ls-hunters-sheets-1.2-eng-BASE-SCREEN.pdf, pages 6.","quantity":1},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241652,"modifiedTime":1783973241652,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"1t0b7V4QVOcedKGV","name":"A splendid short sword","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"A splendid short sword","notes":"See bt-ls-hunters-sheets-1.2-eng-BASE-SCREEN.pdf, pages 6.","quantity":1},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241652,"modifiedTime":1783973241652,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"yfUXa0tVbj23UAn2","name":"A bag containing everything needed to process milk and make butter","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"A bag containing everything needed to process milk and make butter","notes":"See bt-ls-hunters-sheets-1.2-eng-BASE-SCREEN.pdf, pages 6.","quantity":1},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241652,"modifiedTime":1783973241652,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"qXL1PvFvjJMYLyCh","name":"A precious bracelet engraved with a cradle, a gift from my mother","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"A precious bracelet engraved with a cradle, a gift from my mother","notes":"See bt-ls-hunters-sheets-1.2-eng-BASE-SCREEN.pdf, pages 6.","quantity":1},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241652,"modifiedTime":1783973241652,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"pMuf0PCkSnOlSRVT","name":"A well-worn blanket that I love and use as a cloak","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"A well-worn blanket that I love and use as a cloak","notes":"See bt-ls-hunters-sheets-1.2-eng-BASE-SCREEN.pdf, pages 6.","quantity":1},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241652,"modifiedTime":1783973241652,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"5dteOCxgbZ2V0G97","name":"A bag full of coins and valuables that I often lose","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"A bag full of coins and valuables that I often lose","notes":"See bt-ls-hunters-sheets-1.2-eng-BASE-SCREEN.pdf, pages 6.","quantity":1},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241652,"modifiedTime":1783973241652,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"Y9vXrqvxA97Rb367","name":"Source Sheet","type":"storyElement","img":"icons/svg/scroll.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"<p><strong>Lost Stories</strong></p><p>bt-ls-hunters-sheets-1.2-eng-BASE-SCREEN.pdf, pages 6.</p>","notes":"bt-ls-hunters-sheets-1.2-eng-BASE-SCREEN.pdf, pages 6"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241652,"modifiedTime":1783973241652,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}],"effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"pregenSlug":"lost-stories-prince-trollo-the-innocent","pregenCollection":"Lost Stories","source":"bt-ls-hunters-sheets-1.2-eng-BASE-SCREEN.pdf","pages":"6"}},"system":{"details":{"concept":"Lost Stories","origin":"Prince Trollo the Innocent","role":"Hunter of the Order","notes":"Y ou gain 1 Additional Success for each Check you make when trying \nto persuade someone to do the right thing. Once per Scenario, if you \nsuffer 1 Wound to stand up for what you believe in, you set an example \nfor those who help you. Each ally recovers 1 Soma, and a target of your \nchoice (Hunter or NPC) immediately gains an additional action they \nmust use to try to help you or get you to safety."},"resources":{"soma":{"value":6,"max":6},"xp":0,"wounds":{"value":0,"max":3},"darkness":{"value":0,"max":6}},"opposition":{"defaultLevel":5,"modifier":0},"bookmark":{"wound1":"","wound2":"","wound3":"","extraWound":""}},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241652,"modifiedTime":1783973241652,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"uzsHDab5MqNJ17cK","name":"Pietrik and the Cauldron Fae","type":"hunter","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/avatars/pregens/lost-stories-pietrik-and-the-cauldron-fae.png","items":[{"_id":"Z4jOeoIwo14c5FOI","name":"Descriptor 1","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"I am a rebel who is used to living on the streets. I know my way \naround the slums and how to deal with the lowlifes. Rules are \nmade to be broken.","notes":"See bt-ls-hunters-sheets-1.2-eng-BASE-SCREEN.pdf, pages 8.","positive":"I am a rebel who is used to living on the streets. I know my way around the slums and how to deal with the lowlifes. Rules are made to be broken.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241652,"modifiedTime":1783973241652,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"I5BL6gQwKNgHakLi","name":"Descriptor 2","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"I fear nothing and throw myself into any situation. The \nadrenaline of risk drives me to succeed. I get bored easily in \nsituations where there is no danger.","notes":"See bt-ls-hunters-sheets-1.2-eng-BASE-SCREEN.pdf, pages 8.","positive":"I fear nothing and throw myself into any situation. The adrenaline of risk drives me to succeed. I get bored easily in situations where there is no danger.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241652,"modifiedTime":1783973241652,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"FCh9rrchtm457Cyi","name":"Descriptor 3","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"The Cauldron Fae is always with me, in the form of a small \nfloating light. Her magic is still powerful, and I often summon \nher to wreak havoc or play tricks on humans.","notes":"See bt-ls-hunters-sheets-1.2-eng-BASE-SCREEN.pdf, pages 8.","positive":"The Cauldron Fae is always with me, in the form of a small floating light. Her magic is still powerful, and I often summon her to wreak havoc or play tricks on humans.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241652,"modifiedTime":1783973241652,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"QS9nXrlGJAOEp5rR","name":"Lost Childhood","type":"gift","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/icon-gift.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"Despite your young age, you have no qualms about \ntaking action against enemies. Y ou gain 1 Additional Success in all \nactions that require the use of subterfuge. If you attack a target that is \nunaware of your presence, you inflict 1 Additional Wound.","notes":"See bt-ls-hunters-sheets-1.2-eng-BASE-SCREEN.pdf, pages 8.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241652,"modifiedTime":1783973241652,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"03cqwQwlZD4hln7Z","name":"Fearless","type":"gift","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/icon-gift.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"Y ou are immune to any fear or mind control effects that \nprevent you from acting as you wish. If you suffer 1 Wound from an \nOpponent or Threat, you may regain 1 Soma in your next action and \nmay consider a Failure as an Outcome with a Cost.","notes":"See bt-ls-hunters-sheets-1.2-eng-BASE-SCREEN.pdf, pages 8.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241652,"modifiedTime":1783973241652,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"jrhciskWJEFbXPph","name":"Dark Ego - The Magic of Disbelief","type":"darkEgo","img":"icons/svg/terror.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"The Cauldron Fae unleashes \nher magic to enable you to perform amazing actions. As an action, \nyou can formulate a magic sentence including the fragment I don’t \nbelieve and make its effect concrete. For example, “I don’t believe in \ngravity” would allow you to fly, while “I don’t believe the Hunters of \nthe Order exist” would allow you to hurt the Hunters in an attempt to \nmake them disappear. If your statement has no offensive effect, spend \n1 Soma to gain the power you summoned for the entire Scene. On \nthe other hand, if you want the spell to affect a target \nother than yourself, spend 1 Soma \nto inflict a Wound or apply the effect without making a Check. Each \ntime you use the Magic of Disbelief, roll a die. On a roll of 5 or 6, the \nStoryteller gains 1 Prank Token. The Storyteller can spend 1 Prank \nToken during a Scene to activate the effect of this Gift (you do not take a \nWound because the Activator was not normally triggered) and have the \nCauldron Fae cast a spell to complicate your life or attempt to damage \nsomething that represents progress and modernity. If the Storyteller has \nno accumulated Prank Tokens, you may choose to ignore all the Soma \ncosts to activate the effects of this Gift, but the Storyteller will gain 1 \nPrank Token.","notes":"See bt-ls-hunters-sheets-1.2-eng-BASE-SCREEN.pdf, pages 8.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0,"trigger":"Without thinking about the possible consequences, throw \nyourself into an action that is impossible for an ordinary person."},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241652,"modifiedTime":1783973241652,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"Nt5t7dzFTYHa3DLN","name":"A dueling blade","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"A dueling blade","notes":"See bt-ls-hunters-sheets-1.2-eng-BASE-SCREEN.pdf, pages 8.","quantity":1},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241653,"modifiedTime":1783973241653,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"YblIYcDJirwaSvqi","name":"A book of fairytales given to me by Gwendolyn, the only person I consider a friend","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"A book of fairytales given to me by Gwendolyn, the only person I consider a friend","notes":"See bt-ls-hunters-sheets-1.2-eng-BASE-SCREEN.pdf, pages 8.","quantity":1},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241653,"modifiedTime":1783973241653,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"cGpqH0ISzqnEk6Gy","name":"A necklace with a little bell","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"A necklace with a little bell","notes":"See bt-ls-hunters-sheets-1.2-eng-BASE-SCREEN.pdf, pages 8.","quantity":1},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241653,"modifiedTime":1783973241653,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"itqrBSGRWfeoIe5C","name":"A worn pirate flag I keep as a trophy","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"A worn pirate flag I keep as a trophy","notes":"See bt-ls-hunters-sheets-1.2-eng-BASE-SCREEN.pdf, pages 8.","quantity":1},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241653,"modifiedTime":1783973241653,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"az6pTPVvtWNYQjZ9","name":"A set of sharp needles","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"A set of sharp needles","notes":"See bt-ls-hunters-sheets-1.2-eng-BASE-SCREEN.pdf, pages 8.","quantity":1},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241653,"modifiedTime":1783973241653,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"qiiuVSSFfcIxBH9Y","name":"Source Sheet","type":"storyElement","img":"icons/svg/scroll.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"<p><strong>Lost Stories</strong></p><p>bt-ls-hunters-sheets-1.2-eng-BASE-SCREEN.pdf, pages 8.</p>","notes":"bt-ls-hunters-sheets-1.2-eng-BASE-SCREEN.pdf, pages 8"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241653,"modifiedTime":1783973241653,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}],"effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"pregenSlug":"lost-stories-pietrik-and-the-cauldron-fae","pregenCollection":"Lost Stories","source":"bt-ls-hunters-sheets-1.2-eng-BASE-SCREEN.pdf","pages":"8"}},"system":{"details":{"concept":"Lost Stories","origin":"Pietrik and the Cauldron Fae","role":"Hunter of the Order","notes":"<p><strong>Lost Stories</strong></p><p>bt-ls-hunters-sheets-1.2-eng-BASE-SCREEN.pdf, pages 8.</p>"},"resources":{"soma":{"value":6,"max":6},"xp":0,"wounds":{"value":0,"max":3},"darkness":{"value":0,"max":6}},"opposition":{"defaultLevel":5,"modifier":0},"bookmark":{"wound1":"","wound2":"","wound3":"","extraWound":""}},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241653,"modifiedTime":1783973241653,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"bYXzI7NIBjuLoGE6","name":"Loki the Deceiver","type":"hunter","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/avatars/pregens/lost-stories-loki-the-deceiver.png","items":[{"_id":"wMxaiwxmCmzhyFw5","name":"Descriptor 1","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"I can disguise myself to assume any identity. I can easily imitate \nmen, women, and even fantastical creatures. I have great respect \nfor a successful deception and hate to expose it, even if it would \nbenefit me.","notes":"See bt-ls-hunters-sheets-1.2-eng-BASE-SCREEN.pdf, pages 10.","positive":"I can disguise myself to assume any identity. I can easily imitate men, women, and even fantastical creatures. I have great respect for a successful deception and hate to expose it, even if it would benefit me.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241653,"modifiedTime":1783973241653,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"gigycI0DDGQ5XTZf","name":"Descriptor 2","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"I am a skilled acrobat, I tell stories, perform magic tricks, and put \nmy audience in a good mood. I enjoy chaos and adding confusion \nto situations is a way for me to bring balance to the world.","notes":"See bt-ls-hunters-sheets-1.2-eng-BASE-SCREEN.pdf, pages 10.","positive":"I am a skilled acrobat, I tell stories, perform magic tricks, and put my audience in a good mood. I enjoy chaos and adding confusion to situations is a way for me to bring balance to the world.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241653,"modifiedTime":1783973241653,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"x7KIVz4HgyHLxA1X","name":"Descriptor 3","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"I am a master at distorting and unraveling deception. Verbal \nand body language hold no secrets for me. I don’t like to get my \nhands dirty and would rather have someone else do it for me.","notes":"See bt-ls-hunters-sheets-1.2-eng-BASE-SCREEN.pdf, pages 10.","positive":"I am a master at distorting and unraveling deception. Verbal and body language hold no secrets for me. I don’t like to get my hands dirty and would rather have someone else do it for me.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241653,"modifiedTime":1783973241653,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"gJa4Ga6QDII8EBQM","name":"Thousand Faces","type":"gift","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/icon-gift.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"Once per Scene, you can assume the identity of \nanother Hunter. Choose a Hunter’s Sheet that no one is using and use it \nfor the rest of the Scene. Y ou have access to all the Gifts and abilities on \nthe Sheet, with the exception of the Soma points and Wounds, which you \nwill keep from Loki’s Sheet. Even though you have their likeness, you are \nnot the Hunter you are impersonating, so you do not know their personal \nhistory and cannot activate the Special Scenario Gifts associated with \nthem. Any effects of the Gifts you activate while impersonating another \nHunter will end when you return to your true identity or at the end of \nthe Scene. If someone discovers who you really are, your masquerade \nends and you take 1 Wound. If you wish, you can return to your original \nappearance before the end of the Scene. If you discover a deception and \ndo nothing to expose it, you gain 1 Soma.","notes":"See bt-ls-hunters-sheets-1.2-eng-BASE-SCREEN.pdf, pages 10.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241653,"modifiedTime":1783973241653,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"J01InEGQSikATdXy","name":"Trickster","type":"gift","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/icon-gift.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"Y ou get 2 Additional Successes if you use your skills as \nan entertainer to perform an action. This includes polite conversation, \nsleight of hand, or performing stunts. Once per Scene, if you help an \nenemy (for example as a Cost), you gain 1 Soma.","notes":"See bt-ls-hunters-sheets-1.2-eng-BASE-SCREEN.pdf, pages 10.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241653,"modifiedTime":1783973241653,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"OCVoWul6I2aizlZm","name":"Dark Ego - The Great Deception","type":"darkEgo","img":"icons/svg/terror.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"The whole world is a lie, and only \nthose who are truly aware of it can pull the strings of any story. During \nthe course of the Scene, you can activate each of the following effects \nonce:\n1. Materialize an item that is useful for the situation you are facing and \nthat an ally of yours is carrying without knowing it.\n2. Switch places with a Minor NPC. The exchange takes place in the \nblink of an eye, and those present will only see where you are now \nand where your target has ended up. Highly skilled NPCs and other \nHunters are immune to this effect.\n3. Make an NPC that you have met before appear in the Scene. This is \nan illusion that will do your bidding and will dissolve as soon as it \ntakes 1 Wound or it becomes clear that it is not the real person.\n4. Gain 1 Additional Success in a Check you make by exploiting a \nsubject’s character flaw.","notes":"See bt-ls-hunters-sheets-1.2-eng-BASE-SCREEN.pdf, pages 10.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0,"trigger":"Organize a deception by studying it in detail, or expose a \ndeception to the people being deceived."},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241653,"modifiedTime":1783973241653,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"m26X0FOr4LobnuXd","name":"Theatrical costume","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"Theatrical costume","notes":"See bt-ls-hunters-sheets-1.2-eng-BASE-SCREEN.pdf, pages 10.","quantity":1},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241653,"modifiedTime":1783973241653,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"5YZweCDa45HQfyqc","name":"A snake-shaped flask containing a strong acid","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"A snake-shaped flask containing a strong acid","notes":"See bt-ls-hunters-sheets-1.2-eng-BASE-SCREEN.pdf, pages 10.","quantity":1},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241653,"modifiedTime":1783973241653,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"QMyOiuCRK6kqNNVV","name":"A necklace of great value engraved with the word “Brísingamen”","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"A necklace of great value engraved with the word “Brísingamen”","notes":"See bt-ls-hunters-sheets-1.2-eng-BASE-SCREEN.pdf, pages 10.","quantity":1},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241653,"modifiedTime":1783973241653,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"nbqq8Tuugx4VF3ri","name":"Various musical instruments and juggling equipment","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"Various musical instruments and juggling equipment","notes":"See bt-ls-hunters-sheets-1.2-eng-BASE-SCREEN.pdf, pages 10.","quantity":1},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241653,"modifiedTime":1783973241653,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"CXRAa8L6dpejJ8An","name":"A series of sharp daggers hidden throughout my clothing","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"A series of sharp daggers hidden throughout my clothing","notes":"See bt-ls-hunters-sheets-1.2-eng-BASE-SCREEN.pdf, pages 10.","quantity":1},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241653,"modifiedTime":1783973241653,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"Zp7yRXSwo28tLLt7","name":"A diary in which are written the names of all the men and women whose hearts I have broken","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"A diary in which are written the names of all the men and women whose hearts I have broken","notes":"See bt-ls-hunters-sheets-1.2-eng-BASE-SCREEN.pdf, pages 10.","quantity":1},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241653,"modifiedTime":1783973241653,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"UacQFtkhkREkM5i9","name":"Source Sheet","type":"storyElement","img":"icons/svg/scroll.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"<p><strong>Lost Stories</strong></p><p>bt-ls-hunters-sheets-1.2-eng-BASE-SCREEN.pdf, pages 10.</p>","notes":"bt-ls-hunters-sheets-1.2-eng-BASE-SCREEN.pdf, pages 10"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241653,"modifiedTime":1783973241653,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}],"effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"pregenSlug":"lost-stories-loki-the-deceiver","pregenCollection":"Lost Stories","source":"bt-ls-hunters-sheets-1.2-eng-BASE-SCREEN.pdf","pages":"10"}},"system":{"details":{"concept":"Lost Stories","origin":"Loki the Deceiver","role":"Hunter of the Order","notes":"<p><strong>Lost Stories</strong></p><p>bt-ls-hunters-sheets-1.2-eng-BASE-SCREEN.pdf, pages 10.</p>"},"resources":{"soma":{"value":6,"max":6},"xp":0,"wounds":{"value":0,"max":3},"darkness":{"value":0,"max":6}},"opposition":{"defaultLevel":5,"modifier":0},"bookmark":{"wound1":"","wound2":"","wound3":"","extraWound":""}},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241653,"modifiedTime":1783973241653,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"okIxnhNUoqVuVw0H","name":"The Silent Mother","type":"hunter","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/avatars/pregens/lost-stories-the-silent-mother.png","items":[{"_id":"0mVczjIIx7Gi9lhX","name":"Descriptor 1","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"I know my way around high society and have amassed great \nwealth through countless marriages. I am known in the \nunderworld for my exploits. I hate being accused of being a \ncriminal.","notes":"See bt-ls-hunters-sheets-1.2-eng-BASE-SCREEN.pdf, pages 12.","positive":"I know my way around high society and have amassed great wealth through countless marriages. I am known in the underworld for my exploits. I hate being accused of being a criminal.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241653,"modifiedTime":1783973241653,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"dezYlUKgf3KcthDj","name":"Descriptor 2","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"I am able to understand the potential of young women and know \nhow to guide their steps to develop their true potential. I consider \neach of my protégés a true daughter and would give my life to \nsave them.","notes":"See bt-ls-hunters-sheets-1.2-eng-BASE-SCREEN.pdf, pages 12.","positive":"I am able to understand the potential of young women and know how to guide their steps to develop their true potential. I consider each of my protégés a true daughter and would give my life to save them.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241653,"modifiedTime":1783973241653,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"QPA91FBbyDY4KK5v","name":"Descriptor 3","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"Although I appear helpless, I am a capable spy who knows how to \ndefend herself in dangerous situations. I never miss an opportunity \nto accumulate wealth and resources.","notes":"See bt-ls-hunters-sheets-1.2-eng-BASE-SCREEN.pdf, pages 12.","positive":"Although I appear helpless, I am a capable spy who knows how to defend herself in dangerous situations. I never miss an opportunity to accumulate wealth and resources.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241653,"modifiedTime":1783973241653,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"J7ljTRjf9f1kqbck","name":"Legacy","type":"gift","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/icon-gift.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"Y ou can use all the resources you have accumulated from \nyour many marriages of convenience. Y ou can use each of these effects \nonce per Scenario:\n1. A Family Asset: Y ou can bring a large property into play, such as \na mansion or business. Y ou have free access to the property and its \nresources.\n2. A Family Friend: Y ou can introduce a Minor NPC who has a debt or \npartnership agreement with your family. The Storyteller will sketch the \nNPC, who will be well-disposed towards you.\n3. A Family Treasure: Y ou can bring into play a rare and valuable item \nthat you own as a family heirloom.","notes":"See bt-ls-hunters-sheets-1.2-eng-BASE-SCREEN.pdf, pages 12.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241653,"modifiedTime":1783973241653,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"bKZF1Jn9j3sJmB8L","name":"My Beloved Daughters","type":"gift","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/icon-gift.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"Two young girls you saved from an \nunfortunate fate follow you on your adventures. Y our adopted \ndaughters are two Minor NPCs with the following profiles:\nOL Medium 5 - (1 Wound)\nDecide on their names and stories, and work with the Storyteller to \ncreate a Descriptor for each of them that describes their abilities. Y our \nadopted daughters cannot have magical abilities or more than a good \neducation in their chosen discipline. Y our daughters will do their best to \nserve you at every opportunity.","notes":"See bt-ls-hunters-sheets-1.2-eng-BASE-SCREEN.pdf, pages 12.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241653,"modifiedTime":1783973241653,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"sQpKhIfFl436Ij6j","name":"Dark Ego - The Caring Mother","type":"darkEgo","img":"icons/svg/terror.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"Choose a female NPC or Hunter \nand name her your Pupil. Y our Pupil must be young and, in your \nopinion, deserving of your benevolence. Y ou will always know where \nyour Pupil is, and she will gain 1 Additional Success to her actions (or \nincrease her OL by 1 in the case of an NPC) if you are present in the \nScene to comfort her with your words. Y ou get 1 Additional Success if \nyou act against someone who endangers your Pupil. If an NPC or Hunter \nuses a Gift to harm your disciple, you can spend 1 Soma to prevent the \nGift from being activated.","notes":"See bt-ls-hunters-sheets-1.2-eng-BASE-SCREEN.pdf, pages 12.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0,"trigger":"Your words inspire a young girl to find her way or protect her \nfrom injustice."},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241653,"modifiedTime":1783973241653,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"gBdn9dNKV6lYAm32","name":"Noble robes","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"Noble robes","notes":"See bt-ls-hunters-sheets-1.2-eng-BASE-SCREEN.pdf, pages 12.","quantity":1},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241653,"modifiedTime":1783973241653,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"lPo9lQeHjDzleMV8","name":"Family jewelry and wealth","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"Family jewelry and wealth","notes":"See bt-ls-hunters-sheets-1.2-eng-BASE-SCREEN.pdf, pages 12.","quantity":1},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241653,"modifiedTime":1783973241653,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"odS5fxbMaSceXAnG","name":"Two trained pigeons you can use to send messages","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"Two trained pigeons you can use to send messages","notes":"See bt-ls-hunters-sheets-1.2-eng-BASE-SCREEN.pdf, pages 12.","quantity":1},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241653,"modifiedTime":1783973241653,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"FGwnaLPWXJLKp65c","name":"A set of long sewing pins","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"A set of long sewing pins","notes":"See bt-ls-hunters-sheets-1.2-eng-BASE-SCREEN.pdf, pages 12.","quantity":1},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241653,"modifiedTime":1783973241653,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"0W1UXaackiaRp45o","name":"A long cloak and a mask depicting a smiling mother","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"A long cloak and a mask depicting a smiling mother","notes":"See bt-ls-hunters-sheets-1.2-eng-BASE-SCREEN.pdf, pages 12.","quantity":1},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241653,"modifiedTime":1783973241653,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"SpRUkXNsKSoumQiz","name":"A sublimely crafted weapon","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"A sublimely crafted weapon","notes":"See bt-ls-hunters-sheets-1.2-eng-BASE-SCREEN.pdf, pages 12.","quantity":1},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241653,"modifiedTime":1783973241653,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"JrSELbDxzQgsnxnv","name":"Source Sheet","type":"storyElement","img":"icons/svg/scroll.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"<p><strong>Lost Stories</strong></p><p>bt-ls-hunters-sheets-1.2-eng-BASE-SCREEN.pdf, pages 12.</p>","notes":"bt-ls-hunters-sheets-1.2-eng-BASE-SCREEN.pdf, pages 12"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241653,"modifiedTime":1783973241653,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}],"effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"pregenSlug":"lost-stories-the-silent-mother","pregenCollection":"Lost Stories","source":"bt-ls-hunters-sheets-1.2-eng-BASE-SCREEN.pdf","pages":"12"}},"system":{"details":{"concept":"Lost Stories","origin":"The Silent Mother","role":"Hunter of the Order","notes":"<p><strong>Lost Stories</strong></p><p>bt-ls-hunters-sheets-1.2-eng-BASE-SCREEN.pdf, pages 12.</p>"},"resources":{"soma":{"value":6,"max":6},"xp":0,"wounds":{"value":0,"max":3},"darkness":{"value":0,"max":6}},"opposition":{"defaultLevel":5,"modifier":0},"bookmark":{"wound1":"","wound2":"","wound3":"","extraWound":""}},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241653,"modifiedTime":1783973241653,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"OSQeEX3bvHY3Rw3J","name":"Karasu Kuroi the Wandering Monk","type":"hunter","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/avatars/pregens/lost-stories-karasu-kuroi-the-wandering-monk.png","items":[{"_id":"M6MEkz88ywnFnDQt","name":"Descriptor 1","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"Y ou can mentally communicate for the rest of the Scene.","notes":"See bt-ls-hunters-sheets-1.2-eng-BASE-SCREEN.pdf, pages 14.","positive":"Y ou can mentally communicate for the rest of the Scene.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241654,"modifiedTime":1783973241654,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"Qvk101dWECvOFZZj","name":"Descriptor 2","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"I am an exorcist monk. My body is tempered by a lifetime of asceticism \nand fighting evil spirits. I do not tolerate blasphemy and those who use \nknowledge for personal gain.","notes":"See bt-ls-hunters-sheets-1.2-eng-BASE-SCREEN.pdf, pages 14.","positive":"I am an exorcist monk. My body is tempered by a lifetime of asceticism and fighting evil spirits. I do not tolerate blasphemy and those who use knowledge for personal gain.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241654,"modifiedTime":1783973241654,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"HadOmgKS9bWo2Agx","name":"Descriptor 3","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"Prayer keeps my mind steadfast and my words are an inspiration to \nthose who have faith. I do not tolerate the concepts of faith and \ndevotion being questioned.","notes":"See bt-ls-hunters-sheets-1.2-eng-BASE-SCREEN.pdf, pages 14.","positive":"Prayer keeps my mind steadfast and my words are an inspiration to those who have faith. I do not tolerate the concepts of faith and devotion being questioned.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241654,"modifiedTime":1783973241654,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"CXMvdKWUbV7P1csh","name":"Dark Ego Descriptor","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"My greatest secret is that I am like those I fight. My true essence is that \nof a Yokai ghost, which is why I have a talent for unearthing Broken \nTales. I try to do good deeds in the hope of reincarnating as a human.","notes":"See bt-ls-hunters-sheets-1.2-eng-BASE-SCREEN.pdf, pages 14.","positive":"My greatest secret is that I am like those I fight. My true essence is that of a Yokai ghost, which is why I have a talent for unearthing Broken Tales. I try to do good deeds in the hope of reincarnating as a human.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241654,"modifiedTime":1783973241654,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"GOCMKSRuSK6LWFIE","name":"Monk","type":"gift","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/icon-gift.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"Y ou can spend 1 Soma to activate a piece of your Spirit Hunter \nEquipment:\n1. Pastoral Shakujo: Banging your staff on the ground can temporarily \ninterrupt the effect of a spell or curse. The duration of the interruption (set by \nthe Storyteller) can vary from a few moments to the entire Scene, depending \non the power of the spell.\n2. Hauchiwa Fan: With a fan blast, you can make a leap of up to ten meters \nforward or upward. Y ou can use this effect on an ally.\n3. Tengu-gui Mask: Y ou can wear your mask to change your facial features, taking on a physical appearance appropriate to the context. Create a \nDescriptor that represents your appearance, but remember that you cannot \nreplicate the features of a specific subject. When you activate a Gift or suffer 1 \nWound, you will revert to your original appearance. \nThe use of this Gift is limited by the possession of the corresponding \nEquipment: if you lose an item, you cannot use the relevant option until you \nrecover it. During an Interlude, you recover any missing Equipment.","notes":"See bt-ls-hunters-sheets-1.2-eng-BASE-SCREEN.pdf, pages 14.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241654,"modifiedTime":1783973241654,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"smzJjqsrED08uB6Q","name":"Moral Rigor","type":"gift","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/icon-gift.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"Y ou demonstrate righteousness in word and deed. Y ou gain \n1 Additional Success on all Position Checks where you make a commitment \nby giving your word as a guarantee. By spending 1 Soma, you can make \nmental contact with a subject present in the Scene who must accept the link.","notes":"See bt-ls-hunters-sheets-1.2-eng-BASE-SCREEN.pdf, pages 14.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241654,"modifiedTime":1783973241654,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"X0SxHR64azshj6Lj","name":"Dark Ego - You Are What You Fight","type":"darkEgo","img":"icons/svg/terror.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"When you reveal your true nature, \nyour body changes into the form of a humanoid raven. Y ou will gain the \nfollowing abilities:\n1. Y ou can move by flying thanks to the large wings on your back. Y ou gain \n1 Additional Success on all Defense Checks while hovering in the air. \n2. Y ou can use your large beak to strike an enemy as an additional action, \nbut you cannot communicate by speaking.\n3. Y ou gain 1 Additional Success if you act to injure someone who has \ninflicted 1 Wound on you in the current Scene.","notes":"See bt-ls-hunters-sheets-1.2-eng-BASE-SCREEN.pdf, pages 14.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0,"trigger":"You reveal your true nature to prove that not all spirits are evil."},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241654,"modifiedTime":1783973241654,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"rLpJLFZ461M9vFPc","name":"My prized traveling Shakujō","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"My prized traveling Shakujō","notes":"See bt-ls-hunters-sheets-1.2-eng-BASE-SCREEN.pdf, pages 14.","quantity":1},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241654,"modifiedTime":1783973241654,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"YqfO0OuPUYVY3KdK","name":"My prized Hauchiwa fan","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"My prized Hauchiwa fan","notes":"See bt-ls-hunters-sheets-1.2-eng-BASE-SCREEN.pdf, pages 14.","quantity":1},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241654,"modifiedTime":1783973241654,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"GrygUEKvWKI33bda","name":"A Tengu-gui raven mask","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"A Tengu-gui raven mask","notes":"See bt-ls-hunters-sheets-1.2-eng-BASE-SCREEN.pdf, pages 14.","quantity":1},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241654,"modifiedTime":1783973241654,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"Qvs4wO002VuibwTL","name":"A theater mask with a long nose that I use to hide my Asian features","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"A theater mask with a long nose that I use to hide my Asian features","notes":"See bt-ls-hunters-sheets-1.2-eng-BASE-SCREEN.pdf, pages 14.","quantity":1},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241654,"modifiedTime":1783973241654,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"yRMkENh4mW0YJsCo","name":"A katana that belonged to a famous samurai","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effe