ou can mentally communicate for the rest of the Scene."},"resources":{"soma":{"value":6,"max":6},"xp":0,"wounds":{"value":0,"max":3},"darkness":{"value":0,"max":6}},"opposition":{"defaultLevel":5,"modifier":0},"bookmark":{"wound1":"","wound2":"","wound3":"","extraWound":""}},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241654,"modifiedTime":1783973241654,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"WOetj5VbnIKzAfDC","name":"The 7 Hessian Mercenaries","type":"hunter","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/avatars/pregens/lost-stories-the-7-hessian-mercenaries.png","items":[{"_id":"EVOFtOy8FZjmskN5","name":"Descriptor 1","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"Outcome with an Increment: The goal has been reached, and the team has \nbrought home something important. The Storyteller will tell you what.","notes":"See bt-ls-hunters-sheets-1.2-eng-BASE-SCREEN.pdf, pages 16.","positive":"Outcome with an Increment: The goal has been reached, and the team has brought home something important. The Storyteller will tell you what.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241654,"modifiedTime":1783973241654,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"vQkgAhk2nLf1f5gN","name":"Descriptor 2","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"We are experienced mercenaries and have seen every battlefield. We \nhate working for free and any chance to bring home some extra loot is \ngood.","notes":"See bt-ls-hunters-sheets-1.2-eng-BASE-SCREEN.pdf, pages 16.","positive":"We are experienced mercenaries and have seen every battlefield. We hate working for free and any chance to bring home some extra loot is good.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241654,"modifiedTime":1783973241654,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"K5v6CHq5WZCjuBZq","name":"Descriptor 3","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"We are adept at getting things, information, people, or anything you \nwant - ask and we will find it. We are intolerant of authority and \nanything with a hierarchy of command.","notes":"See bt-ls-hunters-sheets-1.2-eng-BASE-SCREEN.pdf, pages 16.","positive":"We are adept at getting things, information, people, or anything you want - ask and we will find it. We are intolerant of authority and anything with a hierarchy of command.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241654,"modifiedTime":1783973241654,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"YqkrOGJhDoFwANwY","name":"Dark Ego Descriptor","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"Discipline and order are the keys to victory. We act as a team because \nthat is what has allowed us to survive so far. Team first and foremost.","notes":"See bt-ls-hunters-sheets-1.2-eng-BASE-SCREEN.pdf, pages 16.","positive":"Discipline and order are the keys to victory. We act as a team because that is what has allowed us to survive so far. Team first and foremost.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241654,"modifiedTime":1783973241654,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"I5tXuBobmahFkc4l","name":"The Team","type":"gift","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/icon-gift.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"At the beginning of each Scene, you choose the 3 members \nof the Main Team. Y ou will receive the 3 Gifts and the Special Equipment of \nthe members you have chosen. The other 4 dwarves form the Support Team. \nThe Main Team acts as a single Hunter and receives 1 Penalty to Checks for \neach team member not present in a Scene. Wounds are also cumulative for all \nmembers, and any member can act until the Team takes its last Wound. During \na Scene, you can spend 1 Soma to swap a Main Team member for a Support \nTeam member.","notes":"See bt-ls-hunters-sheets-1.2-eng-BASE-SCREEN.pdf, pages 16.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241654,"modifiedTime":1783973241654,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"Oek3JjBOj4uBO2X5","name":"On Mission","type":"gift","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/icon-gift.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"Once per Scene, you can send the Support Team on a mission \nto accomplish a goal, such as capturing an NPC, discovering information, or \nanything else you deem useful. The Storyteller sets the OL of the mission just \nlike a normal Position Check. To find out what happens, you must make a \nPosition Check, where you get 1 Base Success for each Support Team Member \n(usually 4), but you cannot spend Soma to get Additional Successes. Depending \non the result:\nFailure: The objective was missed, and one of the team members is out of the \ngame for the rest of the Scenario. Describe what happened in the words of the \nreturning teammates. If the story makes at least one other Player laugh, you will \nrecover 1 Soma.\nOutcome with a Cost: The goal was completed, but there were problems. The \nStoryteller describes how it went and suggests a complication.\nStandard Outcome: Goal completed, no problems.","notes":"See bt-ls-hunters-sheets-1.2-eng-BASE-SCREEN.pdf, pages 16.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241654,"modifiedTime":1783973241654,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"o5RUBtNKdP7j6JiU","name":"Dark Ego - Heigh-ho, Heigh-ho","type":"darkEgo","img":"icons/svg/terror.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"If you are preparing for a confrontation, \nno one can stand up to you. If it is on a mission, the Support Team immediately \nre-enters the Scene (even if it means interrupting another task assigned through \nthe On Mission Gift), with all the narrative benefits that can bring. For the rest \nof the Scene, the Main and Support Teams will act as a single Hunter 2 times \nper Exchange, not consecutively. Any personal Gifts from the various members \nmay be used.","notes":"See bt-ls-hunters-sheets-1.2-eng-BASE-SCREEN.pdf, pages 16.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0,"trigger":"Begin a confrontation or challenge with the singing of your battle \nhymn."},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241654,"modifiedTime":1783973241654,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"u1DJKv5TN0UMflGa","name":"Swords and guns in abundance","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"Swords and guns in abundance","notes":"See bt-ls-hunters-sheets-1.2-eng-BASE-SCREEN.pdf, pages 16.","quantity":1},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241654,"modifiedTime":1783973241654,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"OJEckieJ3mBWswZ5","name":"Shovels and picks for digging holes and trenches","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"Shovels and picks for digging holes and trenches","notes":"See bt-ls-hunters-sheets-1.2-eng-BASE-SCREEN.pdf, pages 16.","quantity":1},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241654,"modifiedTime":1783973241654,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"kXRT6uTvQhME8Uu8","name":"Nuts and playing cards","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"Nuts and playing cards","notes":"See bt-ls-hunters-sheets-1.2-eng-BASE-SCREEN.pdf, pages 16.","quantity":1},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241654,"modifiedTime":1783973241654,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"KpoiiBr6fGx8PZic","name":"A bottle of fine brandy waiting for its chance to be opened","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"A bottle of fine brandy waiting for its chance to be opened","notes":"See bt-ls-hunters-sheets-1.2-eng-BASE-SCREEN.pdf, pages 16.","quantity":1},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241654,"modifiedTime":1783973241654,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"cEijg65awyWbgT5M","name":"The key to the secret hiding place where we have accumulated our life’s earnings, but whose location no one remembers (damned drunks!)","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"The key to the secret hiding place where we have accumulated our life’s earnings, but whose location no one remembers (damned drunks!)","notes":"See bt-ls-hunters-sheets-1.2-eng-BASE-SCREEN.pdf, pages 16.","quantity":1},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241654,"modifiedTime":1783973241654,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"zrFbED5ngSWRj9Y9","name":"A handkerchief for each of us, sewn by a pure and special girl we defended from the Order Hunters","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"A handkerchief for each of us, sewn by a pure and special girl we defended from the Order Hunters","notes":"See bt-ls-hunters-sheets-1.2-eng-BASE-SCREEN.pdf, pages 16.","quantity":1},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241654,"modifiedTime":1783973241654,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"GrOxbPCsehlNH1Fr","name":"Tobacco and wine","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"Tobacco and wine","notes":"See bt-ls-hunters-sheets-1.2-eng-BASE-SCREEN.pdf, pages 16.","quantity":1},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241654,"modifiedTime":1783973241654,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"xL7qTke3hF8xJbAY","name":"Source Sheet","type":"storyElement","img":"icons/svg/scroll.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"<p><strong>Lost Stories</strong></p><p>bt-ls-hunters-sheets-1.2-eng-BASE-SCREEN.pdf, pages 16.</p>","notes":"bt-ls-hunters-sheets-1.2-eng-BASE-SCREEN.pdf, pages 16"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241654,"modifiedTime":1783973241654,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}],"effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"pregenSlug":"lost-stories-the-7-hessian-mercenaries","pregenCollection":"Lost Stories","source":"bt-ls-hunters-sheets-1.2-eng-BASE-SCREEN.pdf","pages":"16"}},"system":{"details":{"concept":"Lost Stories","origin":"The 7 Hessian Mercenaries","role":"Hunter of the Order","notes":"Outcome with an Increment: The goal has been reached, and the team has \nbrought home something important. The Storyteller will tell you what."},"resources":{"soma":{"value":6,"max":6},"xp":0,"wounds":{"value":0,"max":3},"darkness":{"value":0,"max":6}},"opposition":{"defaultLevel":5,"modifier":0},"bookmark":{"wound1":"","wound2":"","wound3":"","extraWound":""}},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241654,"modifiedTime":1783973241654,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"vqeTB3IIfFys5lPx","name":"Circe the Alchemist","type":"hunter","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/avatars/pregens/lost-stories-circe-the-alchemist.png","items":[{"_id":"rx8zjaptROfZB033","name":"Descriptor 1","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"Eurylochus cannot use more than one Pharmaka special effect per Scene.","notes":"See bt-ls-hunters-sheets-1.2-eng-BASE-SCREEN.pdf, pages 20.","positive":"Eurylochus cannot use more than one Pharmaka special effect per Scene.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241654,"modifiedTime":1783973241654,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"pCUlqXRwbYCxIMrF","name":"Descriptor 2","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"I have studied alchemy with the greatest masters, and my potions can produce wondrous effects. I am so drawn to knowledge that I neglect \nmy own safety.","notes":"See bt-ls-hunters-sheets-1.2-eng-BASE-SCREEN.pdf, pages 20.","positive":"I have studied alchemy with the greatest masters, and my potions can produce wondrous effects. I am so drawn to knowledge that I neglect my own safety.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241655,"modifiedTime":1783973241655,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"xV4DpZ5gThpseyne","name":"Descriptor 3","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"Eurylochus is my faithful servant pig and helps me with every task. He \nhas an almost human intelligence and one look is enough to understand \nus. I love him like a brother.","notes":"See bt-ls-hunters-sheets-1.2-eng-BASE-SCREEN.pdf, pages 20.","positive":"Eurylochus is my faithful servant pig and helps me with every task. He has an almost human intelligence and one look is enough to understand us. I love him like a brother.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241655,"modifiedTime":1783973241655,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"lgrT0RheV90dtbC9","name":"Dark Ego Descriptor","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"I have a special power over people who are hopelessly attracted to my \npresence. I am shy and often break down when I receive too much \nexplicit attention.","notes":"See bt-ls-hunters-sheets-1.2-eng-BASE-SCREEN.pdf, pages 20.","positive":"I have a special power over people who are hopelessly attracted to my presence. I am shy and often break down when I receive too much explicit attention.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241655,"modifiedTime":1783973241655,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"mdybBbYpSm5enONx","name":"Pharmaka","type":"gift","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/icon-gift.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"At the beginning of each Scenario, you receive 3 Pharmaka \nTokens. Spend 1 Token when someone ingests one of your potions, then pick \none of the following effects:\n1. The subject transforms into an animal of your choice for the remainder of \nthe Scene. The person retains their human intelligence. \n2. The subject is in a confused state, which lowers their OL by 1 (or 1 Penalty in the case of a Hunter) for the rest of the Scene.\n3. The subject regains vitality and gains an Additional Wound that fades at \nthe end of the Scene.\nY ou are naturally resistant to your creations, and if you want to activate an \neffect on yourself, you must spend 1 Soma in addition to a Pharmaka Token. \nParticularly powerful subjects and Hunters may require you to perform \na Position Check before they suffer the effects of your potions. During an Interlude, or if you get your hands on valuable alchemical ingredients, you can \nrecover 1 Pharmaka Token.","notes":"See bt-ls-hunters-sheets-1.2-eng-BASE-SCREEN.pdf, pages 20.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241655,"modifiedTime":1783973241655,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"6Lg9hAAXBTSdJkja","name":"Travel Companion","type":"gift","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/icon-gift.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"Eurylochus is a Minor NPC with the following profile:\nOL 5 Medium - (2 Wounds) \nDescriptor: I am Circe’s faithful pig servant and would do anything for her. \nEurylochus has always been your companion in experimentation, and over the \nyears he has been imbued with the power of Pharmaka. By spending 1 Soma, \nyou can activate one of the following effects:\n1. Human Form: Eurylochus takes the form of a handsome young man with \nflowing blond hair. He cannot speak but gains all the other advantages of a \nhuman body.\n2. Size Change: Eurylochus can shrink to the size of a mouse or grow to the \nsize of an elephant. The effect lasts for the duration of the Scene.\n3. Regeneration: Eurylochus will recover all of his Wounds, which can also \nbring him back into action if he is down to zero.","notes":"See bt-ls-hunters-sheets-1.2-eng-BASE-SCREEN.pdf, pages 20.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241655,"modifiedTime":1783973241655,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"muizoCPq8B0cqXUq","name":"Dark Ego - Goddess Blood","type":"darkEgo","img":"icons/svg/terror.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"Y ou have the power of a goddess within you, \neven if you do not know how to use it. When you activate your aura, you \nchoose an NPC who will be kind to you and try to fulfill your every wish. This \nGift will have no effect on someone who has hostile intentions towards you, \nbut you will gain 2 Additional Successes on all Defense Checks you make, \nsince harming you seems an unnatural action even to those who hate you.\nY ou can activate all of the Travel Companion Gift’s effects on Eurylochus at \nthe same time.","notes":"See bt-ls-hunters-sheets-1.2-eng-BASE-SCREEN.pdf, pages 20.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0,"trigger":"Unleash your divine power with a charming or swaggering attitude \nat the most inopportune moment."},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241655,"modifiedTime":1783973241655,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"AUZUBKQbtNY6lP88","name":"Your precious portable laboratory","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"Your precious portable laboratory","notes":"See bt-ls-hunters-sheets-1.2-eng-BASE-SCREEN.pdf, pages 20.","quantity":1},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241655,"modifiedTime":1783973241655,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"9BtJLzxU9Dmag9jk","name":"A bag of alchemical components","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"A bag of alchemical components","notes":"See bt-ls-hunters-sheets-1.2-eng-BASE-SCREEN.pdf, pages 20.","quantity":1},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241655,"modifiedTime":1783973241655,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"DHompJ1nqahy2jSf","name":"A pair of smoke vials","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"A pair of smoke vials","notes":"See bt-ls-hunters-sheets-1.2-eng-BASE-SCREEN.pdf, pages 20.","quantity":1},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241655,"modifiedTime":1783973241655,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"k03e2gliPc861XYP","name":"A pair of acid vials","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"A pair of acid vials","notes":"See bt-ls-hunters-sheets-1.2-eng-BASE-SCREEN.pdf, pages 20.","quantity":1},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241655,"modifiedTime":1783973241655,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"tiT6hcEGGtWpYUID","name":"A pair of reagent vials","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"A pair of reagent vials","notes":"See bt-ls-hunters-sheets-1.2-eng-BASE-SCREEN.pdf, pages 20.","quantity":1},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241655,"modifiedTime":1783973241655,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"dbptE1JLwCKsxxlA","name":"The pharmacopeia you are writing","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"The pharmacopeia you are writing","notes":"See bt-ls-hunters-sheets-1.2-eng-BASE-SCREEN.pdf, pages 20.","quantity":1},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241655,"modifiedTime":1783973241655,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"G4OolvfzOx6gC5jz","name":"A small bag of fruit for Eurylochus","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"A small bag of fruit for Eurylochus","notes":"See bt-ls-hunters-sheets-1.2-eng-BASE-SCREEN.pdf, pages 20.","quantity":1},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241655,"modifiedTime":1783973241655,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"bvZE1NVa29R6hOCs","name":"A tome on the animal world","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"A tome on the animal world","notes":"See bt-ls-hunters-sheets-1.2-eng-BASE-SCREEN.pdf, pages 20.","quantity":1},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241655,"modifiedTime":1783973241655,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"6hHOxIP2wyhtA9Ez","name":"A perfectly balanced metal staff","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"A perfectly balanced metal staff","notes":"See bt-ls-hunters-sheets-1.2-eng-BASE-SCREEN.pdf, pages 20.","quantity":1},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241655,"modifiedTime":1783973241655,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"UZsNA57Q5zWc6m7w","name":"Scissors, scalpels, and pliers","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"Scissors, scalpels, and pliers","notes":"See bt-ls-hunters-sheets-1.2-eng-BASE-SCREEN.pdf, pages 20.","quantity":1},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241655,"modifiedTime":1783973241655,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"Hs2J5QEa9wSqUxpI","name":"A magnifying glass","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"A magnifying glass","notes":"See bt-ls-hunters-sheets-1.2-eng-BASE-SCREEN.pdf, pages 20.","quantity":1},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241655,"modifiedTime":1783973241655,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"jzFrHzDehOH3Y6c7","name":"Source Sheet","type":"storyElement","img":"icons/svg/scroll.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"<p><strong>Lost Stories</strong></p><p>bt-ls-hunters-sheets-1.2-eng-BASE-SCREEN.pdf, pages 20.</p>","notes":"bt-ls-hunters-sheets-1.2-eng-BASE-SCREEN.pdf, pages 20"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241655,"modifiedTime":1783973241655,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}],"effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"pregenSlug":"lost-stories-circe-the-alchemist","pregenCollection":"Lost Stories","source":"bt-ls-hunters-sheets-1.2-eng-BASE-SCREEN.pdf","pages":"20"}},"system":{"details":{"concept":"Lost Stories","origin":"Circe the Alchemist","role":"Hunter of the Order","notes":"Eurylochus cannot use more than one Pharmaka special effect per Scene."},"resources":{"soma":{"value":6,"max":6},"xp":0,"wounds":{"value":0,"max":3},"darkness":{"value":0,"max":6}},"opposition":{"defaultLevel":5,"modifier":0},"bookmark":{"wound1":"","wound2":"","wound3":"","extraWound":""}},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241655,"modifiedTime":1783973241655,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"s0IibRK53ZJ25ou0","name":"Captain William of Nottingham","type":"hunter","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/avatars/pregens/lost-stories-captain-william-of-nottingham.png","items":[{"_id":"j4Qq0zmVTphScIDK","name":"Descriptor 1","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"I am a good planner and carry all kinds of useful equipment for \nmy work. I hate sudden changes of plans.","notes":"See bt-ls-hunters-sheets-1.2-eng-BASE-SCREEN.pdf, pages 22.","positive":"I am a good planner and carry all kinds of useful equipment for my work. I hate sudden changes of plans.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241655,"modifiedTime":1783973241655,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"LiO5Fnxpq1aCzuL7","name":"Descriptor 2","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"I am a lawman and I am proud of my office. I have good \nleadership skills and know how to get those in charge to carry out \nan order. I like to be praised for my abilities.","notes":"See bt-ls-hunters-sheets-1.2-eng-BASE-SCREEN.pdf, pages 22.","positive":"I am a lawman and I am proud of my office. I have good leadership skills and know how to get those in charge to carry out an order. I like to be praised for my abilities.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241655,"modifiedTime":1783973241655,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"TStf9yBvxAYnlsY8","name":"Descriptor 3","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"Years of working as a bounty hunter have made me adept at \nhunting down and eliminating villains. When I am one step away \nfrom my goal, I do not consider retreating.","notes":"See bt-ls-hunters-sheets-1.2-eng-BASE-SCREEN.pdf, pages 22.","positive":"Years of working as a bounty hunter have made me adept at hunting down and eliminating villains. When I am one step away from my goal, I do not consider retreating.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241655,"modifiedTime":1783973241655,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"XIHfYY5YuJoSWgj2","name":"Collect Taxes","type":"gift","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/icon-gift.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"At the end of each Scene, you receive 1 Taxes Token \nif you have discovered riches or secrets related to a location or NPC that \nyou can use to your advantage (at the Storyteller’s discretion). Y ou start \neach Scenario with 1 Taxes Token. At any time, you can spend 1 Taxes \nToken to activate one of these effects:\n1. Ask the Storyteller to reveal an NPC’s Gift or Equipment.\n2. Allow an ally to activate a Gift by replacing a special requirement or \nSoma cost.\n3. Confer 1 Additional Success to the action of an allied Hunter.","notes":"See bt-ls-hunters-sheets-1.2-eng-BASE-SCREEN.pdf, pages 22.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241655,"modifiedTime":1783973241655,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"OsL2e5heNRVFN2Xj","name":"Lawman","type":"gift","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/icon-gift.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"Y ou can spend 1 Soma to assert your authority over \nordinary people. NPCs who recognize local authority will not try to \nharm you unless you act aggressively first. Even in cases of conflict, they \nwill avoid choosing you as a target unless you are the first to threaten \nthem. Y ou gain 1 Additional Success if you try to convince or intimidate \nsomeone who recognizes authority.","notes":"See bt-ls-hunters-sheets-1.2-eng-BASE-SCREEN.pdf, pages 22.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241655,"modifiedTime":1783973241655,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"lcWPwyvpJRdSPAGg","name":"Dark Ego - Capture the Outlaws","type":"darkEgo","img":"icons/svg/terror.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"Under your leadership, evildoers \nare short-lived. Receive 2 Taxes Tokens. At any time during the Scene, \nyou can spend 1 Taxes Token to activate the following additional effects. \nEach effect can only be activated once per Exchange:\n1. Allow one of your allies to act immediately to carry out one of your \norders, even if they have already acted in the Exchange.\n2. Gain 2 Additional Successes for any action you take to stop (not \neliminate) a criminal or prevent his escape.\n3. Reveal an aspect of an NPC’s private business to your advantage, \nsuch as a connection to another NPC or what they are trying to \nprotect at all costs.","notes":"See bt-ls-hunters-sheets-1.2-eng-BASE-SCREEN.pdf, pages 22.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0,"trigger":"Act to capture or render harmless subjects you deem evil."},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241655,"modifiedTime":1783973241655,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"gfLyHfJ0FZEZsuG8","name":"A short sword","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"A short sword","notes":"See bt-ls-hunters-sheets-1.2-eng-BASE-SCREEN.pdf, pages 22.","quantity":1},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241655,"modifiedTime":1783973241655,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"KfommoUcuu1kkAfk","name":"A black powder pistol","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"A black powder pistol","notes":"See bt-ls-hunters-sheets-1.2-eng-BASE-SCREEN.pdf, pages 22.","quantity":1},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241655,"modifiedTime":1783973241655,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"GJBOAuf1YIzfWbCk","name":"A long cloak of green cloth","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"A long cloak of green cloth","notes":"See bt-ls-hunters-sheets-1.2-eng-BASE-SCREEN.pdf, pages 22.","quantity":1},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241655,"modifiedTime":1783973241655,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"lOMEjVMCFJtWpUWW","name":"A bag full of coins","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"A bag full of coins","notes":"See bt-ls-hunters-sheets-1.2-eng-BASE-SCREEN.pdf, pages 22.","quantity":1},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241655,"modifiedTime":1783973241655,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"f8Q0uKE5KWmSnvGh","name":"Handcuffs of thick metal","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"Handcuffs of thick metal","notes":"See bt-ls-hunters-sheets-1.2-eng-BASE-SCREEN.pdf, pages 22.","quantity":1},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241655,"modifiedTime":1783973241655,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"tt7Eimj16onaKamE","name":"Coats of arms and medals earned in service","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"Coats of arms and medals earned in service","notes":"See bt-ls-hunters-sheets-1.2-eng-BASE-SCREEN.pdf, pages 22.","quantity":1},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241655,"modifiedTime":1783973241655,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"0qUmVitirzgBG1Dh","name":"A fine cross necklace given me by my old flame Marian","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"A fine cross necklace given me by my old flame Marian","notes":"See bt-ls-hunters-sheets-1.2-eng-BASE-SCREEN.pdf, pages 22.","quantity":1},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241655,"modifiedTime":1783973241655,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"PYORs8yfnEn7LvcN","name":"A certificate of merit penned by a prince","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"A certificate of merit penned by a prince","notes":"See bt-ls-hunters-sheets-1.2-eng-BASE-SCREEN.pdf, pages 22.","quantity":1},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241655,"modifiedTime":1783973241655,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"CmWfnTYyfJxyTH90","name":"Source Sheet","type":"storyElement","img":"icons/svg/scroll.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"<p><strong>Lost Stories</strong></p><p>bt-ls-hunters-sheets-1.2-eng-BASE-SCREEN.pdf, pages 22.</p>","notes":"bt-ls-hunters-sheets-1.2-eng-BASE-SCREEN.pdf, pages 22"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241655,"modifiedTime":1783973241655,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}],"effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"pregenSlug":"lost-stories-captain-william-of-nottingham","pregenCollection":"Lost Stories","source":"bt-ls-hunters-sheets-1.2-eng-BASE-SCREEN.pdf","pages":"22"}},"system":{"details":{"concept":"Lost Stories","origin":"Captain William of Nottingham","role":"Hunter of the Order","notes":"<p><strong>Lost Stories</strong></p><p>bt-ls-hunters-sheets-1.2-eng-BASE-SCREEN.pdf, pages 22.</p>"},"resources":{"soma":{"value":6,"max":6},"xp":0,"wounds":{"value":0,"max":3},"darkness":{"value":0,"max":6}},"opposition":{"defaultLevel":5,"modifier":0},"bookmark":{"wound1":"","wound2":"","wound3":"","extraWound":""}},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241655,"modifiedTime":1783973241655,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"T8tm6XUaYiG0c9LL","name":"Moriarty the Gentleman Thief","type":"hunter","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/avatars/pregens/lost-stories-exclusives-moriarty-the-gentleman-thief.png","items":[{"_id":"LZqxitn4bxt11yMy","name":"Descriptor 1","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"I am an experienced criminal and I know what it takes to pull off \na perfect heist. Planning and precision are the basis for success, \nand I refuse to rely on improvisation or luck.","notes":"See Broken Tales - Lost Stories - Exclusive Pre-Gen Hunters.pdf, pages 2.","positive":"I am an experienced criminal and I know what it takes to pull off a perfect heist. Planning and precision are the basis for success, and I refuse to rely on improvisation or luck.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241655,"modifiedTime":1783973241655,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"Tb9RuAoGM0T6Qmzy","name":"Descriptor 2","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"My misdeeds have made me a real celebrity - I have clashed with \nheroes, nobles, and religious people, and I know how to deal with \neach of them. Sometimes I like to give my enemies a small \nadvantage just to make the challenge more interesting.","notes":"See Broken Tales - Lost Stories - Exclusive Pre-Gen Hunters.pdf, pages 2.","positive":"My misdeeds have made me a real celebrity - I have clashed with heroes, nobles, and religious people, and I know how to deal with each of them. Sometimes I like to give my enemies a small advantage just to make the challenge more interesting.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241655,"modifiedTime":1783973241655,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"fPdDc27jTKDlSwOE","name":"Descriptor 3","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"I am as ingenious in the use of concealed weapons and low blows \nas I am in plotting crime. The memory of my lost love has changed \nme deeply, and I try to prevent crime from creating innocent \nvictims.","notes":"See Broken Tales - Lost Stories - Exclusive Pre-Gen Hunters.pdf, pages 2.","positive":"I am as ingenious in the use of concealed weapons and low blows as I am in plotting crime. The memory of my lost love has changed me deeply, and I try to prevent crime from creating innocent victims.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241655,"modifiedTime":1783973241655,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"9zcvNzmxiqsIgtqn","name":"Diabolical Plan","type":"gift","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/icon-gift.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"Once per Scenario, you can do each of the \nfollowing:\n1. Find a useful item (that you had previously planted) in your location. Receive 1 Spider Web Token.\n2. Deliver a message to someone without anyone else noticing. The \nmessage will be delivered during the Scene and, if you wish, you \nwill receive a reply at the beginning of the next Scene. Receive 1 \nSpider Web Token.\n3. Introduce an allied Minor NPC of yours to the Scene, who will be \nwilling to testify on your behalf. Receive 1 Spider Web Token.","notes":"See Broken Tales - Lost Stories - Exclusive Pre-Gen Hunters.pdf, pages 2.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241655,"modifiedTime":1783973241655,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"5AGW4sX2vUfCAslk","name":"Dark Eminence","type":"gift","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/icon-gift.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"Gain 1 Additional Success on all Checks involving \ndeception or obtaining something illegally. When you arrive at a new \nlocation, the Storyteller will reveal the possible presence of criminal \norganizations and their misdeeds. If you strike a beneficial pact with \na criminal or powerful organization, you will receive 1 Spider Web \nToken.","notes":"See Broken Tales - Lost Stories - Exclusive Pre-Gen Hunters.pdf, pages 2.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241655,"modifiedTime":1783973241655,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"dctqlxgg8ITLwkAZ","name":"Dark Ego - The Napoleon of Crime","type":"darkEgo","img":"icons/svg/terror.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"When you reveal your plan in \nall its glory, the unsuspecting pawns of your game will be left speechless. \nY ou will receive 2 Spider Web Tokens. Y ou can spend them as if they \nwere Soma points. Y ou can also activate the following effects at any time \nin the Scene at a cost of 1 Spider Web Token each:\n1. Discovering the Gift of an NPC. \n2. Allow an ally to activate their Dark Ego by ignoring the Activator. \n3. Provide 1 Additional Success to an Ally’s Position Check.","notes":"See Broken Tales - Lost Stories - Exclusive Pre-Gen Hunters.pdf, pages 2.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0,"trigger":"Announce your plan loudly. Show everyone that what you \nhave done before has created an advantage in the current situation."},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241655,"modifiedTime":1783973241655,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"MBZf6FarxZim2qtp","name":"Refined dandy’s clothes","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"Refined dandy’s clothes","notes":"See Broken Tales - Lost Stories - Exclusive Pre-Gen Hunters.pdf, pages 2.","quantity":1},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241655,"modifiedTime":1783973241655,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"59Rv2Pj4CIcNGbOj","name":"A fine pipe to remember me by","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"A fine pipe to remember me by","notes":"See Broken Tales - Lost Stories - Exclusive Pre-Gen Hunters.pdf, pages 2.","quantity":1},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241655,"modifiedTime":1783973241655,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"NpUchRM2Izer2rdd","name":"A futuristic air pistol","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"A futuristic air pistol","notes":"See Broken Tales - Lost Stories - Exclusive Pre-Gen Hunters.pdf, pages 2.","quantity":1},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241655,"modifiedTime":1783973241655,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"vVnbsuaj900WdIgT","name":"A monocle of fine workmanship","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"A monocle of fine workmanship","notes":"See Broken Tales - Lost Stories - Exclusive Pre-Gen Hunters.pdf, pages 2.","quantity":1},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241655,"modifiedTime":1783973241655,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"OErBlAmYbeEZ7hsY","name":"A broad cape concealing stilettos and poisons","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"A broad cape concealing stilettos and poisons","notes":"See Broken Tales - Lost Stories - Exclusive Pre-Gen Hunters.pdf, pages 2.","quantity":1},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241655,"modifiedTime":1783973241655,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"2ixJSfpwmM7yenid","name":"A bouquet of passe-partout","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"A bouquet of passe-partout","notes":"See Broken Tales - Lost Stories - Exclusive Pre-Gen Hunters.pdf, pages 2.","quantity":1},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241655,"modifiedTime":1783973241655,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"5vgKlQ06tFQRiXJM","name":"An animated staff","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"An animated staff","notes":"See Broken Tales - Lost Stories - Exclusive Pre-Gen Hunters.pdf, pages 2.","quantity":1},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241655,"modifiedTime":1783973241655,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"INwWyZnSgvP4HTmm","name":"Boots with hidden pockets. I am the greatest criminal mastermind of all time, and the echoes of my misdeeds have reverberated around the world. Thanks to my incredible cunning, I have always made fools of the authorities, pulled off the most incredible thefts, and manipulated institutions like puppets in my hands. All this until I crossed paths with the World’s Most Famous Investigator. I knew immediately that he would be a challenge worthy of my talents, and for years we battled each other through misdeeds and investigations. On the day of our showdown, however, I realized the truth that I had always tried to hide in my heart. What united us was not rivalry, but the love that can only be felt for someone who is your perfect better half. Feigning death, we retired to private life, but the idyll was shortlived. Called to duty on an international case, he broke our pact and returned to the limelight to do what he does best. Distraught and wounded, I took refuge in the Order. As a Hunter, I used my brilliant mind to fight the darkness and forget my lost love. Moriarty the Gentleman Thief","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"Boots with hidden pockets. I am the greatest criminal mastermind of all time, and the echoes of my misdeeds have reverberated around the world. Thanks to my incredible cunning, I have always made fools of the authorities, pulled off the most incredible thefts, and manipulated institutions like puppets in my hands. All this until I crossed paths with the World’s Most Famous Investigator. I knew immediately that he would be a challenge worthy of my talents, and for years we battled each other through misdeeds and investigations. On the day of our showdown, however, I realized the truth that I had always tried to hide in my heart. What united us was not rivalry, but the love that can only be felt for someone who is your perfect better half. Feigning death, we retired to private life, but the idyll was shortlived. Called to duty on an international case, he broke our pact and returned to the limelight to do what he does best. Distraught and wounded, I took refuge in the Order. As a Hunter, I used my brilliant mind to fight the darkness and forget my lost love. Moriarty the Gentleman Thief","notes":"See Broken Tales - Lost Stories - Exclusive Pre-Gen Hunters.pdf, pages 2.","quantity":1},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241655,"modifiedTime":1783973241655,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"Ca0ZMM9nuZ5y8cdT","name":"Source Sheet","type":"storyElement","img":"icons/svg/scroll.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"<p><strong>Lost Stories Exclusives</strong></p><p>Broken Tales - Lost Stories - Exclusive Pre-Gen Hunters.pdf, pages 2.</p>","notes":"Broken Tales - Lost Stories - Exclusive Pre-Gen Hunters.pdf, pages 2"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241655,"modifiedTime":1783973241655,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}],"effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"pregenSlug":"lost-stories-exclusives-moriarty-the-gentleman-thief","pregenCollection":"Lost Stories Exclusives","source":"Broken Tales - Lost Stories - Exclusive Pre-Gen Hunters.pdf","pages":"2"}},"system":{"details":{"concept":"Lost Stories Exclusives","origin":"Moriarty the Gentleman Thief","role":"Hunter of the Order","notes":"<p><strong>Lost Stories Exclusives</strong></p><p>Broken Tales - Lost Stories - Exclusive Pre-Gen Hunters.pdf, pages 2.</p>"},"resources":{"soma":{"value":6,"max":6},"xp":0,"wounds":{"value":0,"max":3},"darkness":{"value":0,"max":6}},"opposition":{"defaultLevel":5,"modifier":0},"bookmark":{"wound1":"","wound2":"","wound3":"","extraWound":""}},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241656,"modifiedTime":1783973241656,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"Q0uwORWywNW8rx2l","name":"The Pale Medic","type":"hunter","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/avatars/pregens/lost-stories-exclusives-the-pale-medic.png","items":[{"_id":"kiG0HELYXtcqKY8W","name":"Descriptor 1","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"I am a good doctor and I know the cure for every disease, I can tell the \nphysical state of health of a patient just by looking at them. I hate \nviolence and physical confrontation.","notes":"See Broken Tales - Lost Stories - Exclusive Pre-Gen Hunters.pdf, pages 4.","positive":"I am a good doctor and I know the cure for every disease, I can tell the physical state of health of a patient just by looking at them. I hate violence and physical confrontation.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241656,"modifiedTime":1783973241656,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"ZGZTQhukF6dHPii1","name":"Descriptor 2","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"I have a certain amount of charm and I know how to put people at ease \nwith my polite manner. I feel uncomfortable in places where I have not \nbeen invited or where it is obvious that my presence is unwelcome.","notes":"See Broken Tales - Lost Stories - Exclusive Pre-Gen Hunters.pdf, pages 4.","positive":"I have a certain amount of charm and I know how to put people at ease with my polite manner. I feel uncomfortable in places where I have not been invited or where it is obvious that my presence is unwelcome.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241656,"modifiedTime":1783973241656,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"lqYjm1dKE1EkZ4wR","name":"Descriptor 3","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"I have vampire blood in me and my strength is far superior to that of \nan ordinary human. I am extremely sensitive to sunlight and try to \navoid it as much as possible.","notes":"See Broken Tales - Lost Stories - Exclusive Pre-Gen Hunters.pdf, pages 4.","positive":"I have vampire blood in me and my strength is far superior to that of an ordinary human. I am extremely sensitive to sunlight and try to avoid it as much as possible.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241656,"modifiedTime":1783973241656,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"V42SBvWsWPd4BM5w","name":"Cursed Blood","type":"gift","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/icon-gift.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"Y our blood has incredible properties, so at the end of each \nScene, you recover 1 Wound; this can allow you to return even if you have \nno Wounds left. Self-inflict 1 Wound to draw your blood. Whoever drinks it \n(except you) can choose one of the following effects:\n1. Recover 1 Wound.\n2. Gain 1 Additional Success (increases OL by 1 in the case of an NPC) on \nall Checks for the rest of the Scene. For each Check in which this bonus \nis used, roll a die: if you roll a 5 or 6, the blood’s effect ends.","notes":"See Broken Tales - Lost Stories - Exclusive Pre-Gen Hunters.pdf, pages 4.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241656,"modifiedTime":1783973241656,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"G3PzPVf3M0rATGo3","name":"Welcome to My House","type":"gift","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/icon-gift.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"If you care for an NPC, or are able to talk to them \nin a social setting, you gain 1 Additional Success on any Position Checks you \nmake to influence them. If the Check results in a Positive Outcome, you gain \n1 Additional Success on all Checks you make against that NPC for the rest of \nthe Scenario. After your conversation, the Storyteller will reveal something \nyou didn’t know about the NPC, such as part of their Agenda or a Gift you \nhaven’t seen in action.","notes":"See Broken Tales - Lost Stories - Exclusive Pre-Gen Hunters.pdf, pages 4.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241656,"modifiedTime":1783973241656,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"f0fMh4qYHJx5NuVn","name":"Dark Ego - The Vampire","type":"darkEgo","img":"icons/svg/terror.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"Self-inflict 1 Wound and release the power of \nthe ancient curse that permeates your body. Y ou gain 1 Additional Success for \neach Position Check you make using your supernatural power. Y ou can use \neach of the following powers once per Scene:\n1. Turn into a cloud of mist. In this form, you will move slowly but can \navoid all obstacles. While in this form, you retain all your senses, can \nonly be injured by magic, and cannot physically interact with objects or \npeople.\n2. Summon three wolves that will act under your total control. The wolves \nare Minor NPCs with the following profiles: \nOL Medium 5 - (1 Wound) - Descriptor: I am a big wild wolf, ready to \nfight to the death for my master. \n3. Communicate telepathically with another person on whom you used one \nof your Gifts during the Scenario.","notes":"See Broken Tales - Lost Stories - Exclusive Pre-Gen Hunters.pdf, pages 4.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0,"trigger":"Drink and savor human blood in front of someone. Alternatively, \nbreak a crucifix or throw away garlic in disgust."},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241656,"modifiedTime":1783973241656,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"3rYcsEfRr4LRstpT","name":"A dark doctor’s uniform","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"A dark doctor’s uniform","notes":"See Broken Tales - Lost Stories - Exclusive Pre-Gen Hunters.pdf, pages 4.","quantity":1},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241656,"modifiedTime":1783973241656,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"4q2k0L1zFgiW3Ebp","name":"A pair of fine dark glasses","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"A pair of fine dark glasses","notes":"See Broken Tales - Lost Stories - Exclusive Pre-Gen Hunters.pdf, pages 4.","quantity":1},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241656,"modifiedTime":1783973241656,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"6fpG9X9S3cptOnhr","name":"A vial of Transylvanian soil","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"A vial of Transylvanian soil","notes":"See Broken Tales - Lost Stories - Exclusive Pre-Gen Hunters.pdf, pages 4.","quantity":1},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241656,"modifiedTime":1783973241656,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"fEYr0XrXcNrHCCAk","name":"An ash stake crusted with blood","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"An ash stake crusted with blood","notes":"See Broken Tales - Lost Stories - Exclusive Pre-Gen Hunters.pdf, pages 4.","quantity":1},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241656,"modifiedTime":1783973241656,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"do1Ab5ydTSPtHXwa","name":"A doctor’s bag","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"A doctor’s bag","notes":"See Broken Tales - Lost Stories - Exclusive Pre-Gen Hunters.pdf, pages 4.","quantity":1},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241656,"modifiedTime":1783973241656,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"JOkSIFtl2XhSGkRZ","name":"A dozen vials of my blood","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"A dozen vials of my blood","notes":"See Broken Tales - Lost Stories - Exclusive Pre-Gen Hunters.pdf, pages 4.","quantity":1},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241656,"modifiedTime":1783973241656,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"hcn8qInNjegImK3z","name":"A necklace made by nomads","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"A necklace made by nomads","notes":"See Broken Tales - Lost Stories - Exclusive Pre-Gen Hunters.pdf, pages 4.","quantity":1},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241656,"modifiedTime":1783973241656,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"RAxCBMa7WU7VFx5k","name":"A vial of precious human blood","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"A vial of precious human blood","notes":"See Broken Tales - Lost Stories - Exclusive Pre-Gen Hunters.pdf, pages 4.","quantity":1},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241656,"modifiedTime":1783973241656,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"K4PGCeFvlw0kFshn","name":"Source Sheet","type":"storyElement","img":"icons/svg/scroll.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"<p><strong>Lost Stories Exclusives</strong></p><p>Broken Tales - Lost Stories - Exclusive Pre-Gen Hunters.pdf, pages 4.</p>","notes":"Broken Tales - Lost Stories - Exclusive Pre-Gen Hunters.pdf, pages 4"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241656,"modifiedTime":1783973241656,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}],"effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"pregenSlug":"lost-stories-exclusives-the-pale-medic","pregenCollection":"Lost Stories Exclusives","source":"Broken Tales - Lost Stories - Exclusive Pre-Gen Hunters.pdf","pages":"4"}},"system":{"details":{"concept":"Lost Stories Exclusives","origin":"The Pale Medic","role":"Hunter of the Order","notes":"<p><strong>Lost Stories Exclusives</strong></p><p>Broken Tales - Lost Stories - Exclusive Pre-Gen Hunters.pdf, pages 4.</p>"},"resources":{"soma":{"value":6,"max":6},"xp":0,"wounds":{"value":0,"max":3},"darkness":{"value":0,"max":6}},"opposition":{"defaultLevel":5,"modifier":0},"bookmark":{"wound1":"","wound2":"","wound3":"","extraWound":""}},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241656,"modifiedTime":1783973241656,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"8NNokL69uVSp9Rcc","name":"The Respectable Mr. and Mrs. Mars","type":"hunter","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/avatars/pregens/lost-stories-exclusives-the-respectable-mr-and-mrs-mars.png","items":[{"_id":"uIo5zM9QCWbAkrMD","name":"Descriptor 1","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"If you do, you will recover 2 Soma and gain 1 Invasion! Token.","notes":"See Broken Tales - Lost Stories - Exclusive Pre-Gen Hunters.pdf, pages 6.","positive":"If you do, you will recover 2 Soma and gain 1 Invasion! Token.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241656,"modifiedTime":1783973241656,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"yEpMRU0bc2vMn39H","name":"Descriptor 2","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"We are a harmless middle-aged couple and no one would ever consider \nus a danger. We are adept at going unnoticed. Our passion for human \nfood drives us to real binges.","notes":"See Broken Tales - Lost Stories - Exclusive Pre-Gen Hunters.pdf, pages 6.","positive":"We are a harmless middle-aged couple and no one would ever consider us a danger. We are adept at going unnoticed. Our passion for human food drives us to real binges.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241656,"modifiedTime":1783973241656,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"ZNh0tphqMAc37MOx","name":"Descriptor 3","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"We are always connected to the Mars Operations Center, and this \nallows us to have information about history and science. We are \nmorbidly attracted to any form of art because it is totally absent on our \nworld.","notes":"See Broken Tales - Lost Stories - Exclusive Pre-Gen Hunters.pdf, pages 6.","positive":"We are always connected to the Mars Operations Center, and this allows us to have information about history and science. We are morbidly attracted to any form of art because it is totally absent on our world.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241656,"modifiedTime":1783973241656,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"68hZlhW21yuQvQzv","name":"Dark Ego Descriptor","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"Our knowledge is far more advanced than human knowledge, and we \nhave incredible technology at our disposal. We always try to help those \nwho are considered outcasts or excluded from society...","notes":"See Broken Tales - Lost Stories - Exclusive Pre-Gen Hunters.pdf, pages 6.","positive":"Our knowledge is far more advanced than human knowledge, and we have incredible technology at our disposal. We always try to help those who are considered outcasts or excluded from society...","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241656,"modifiedTime":1783973241656,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"GJiMcK8mLQxacOVB","name":"Incognito Agents","type":"gift","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/icon-gift.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"Y ou are considered a single Hunter, sharing Soma and \nWounds, and can act 2 times per Exchange. If you are separated, each of you \nwill receive 2 Penalties to any Checks you make alone. At the end of a Scene, \nyou can wipe others’ memory of your being there.","notes":"See Broken Tales - Lost Stories - Exclusive Pre-Gen Hunters.pdf, pages 6.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241656,"modifiedTime":1783973241656,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"KsAGXjrirK6jJFxU","name":"Informants","type":"gift","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/icon-gift.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"Once per Scene, you can ask for insight into an NPC, location, or \nevent that has occurred. The Storyteller will provide you with information useful \nto your objectives. Once per Scene, if you witness the unleashing of technology, \nan invention, or a magical power, you can report back to the Operations Center.","notes":"See Broken Tales - Lost Stories - Exclusive Pre-Gen Hunters.pdf, pages 6.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241656,"modifiedTime":1783973241656,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"56xXU4GmoiiwBJgW","name":"Dark Ego - Alien Technology","type":"darkEgo","img":"icons/svg/terror.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"Y ou can always take advantage of your \nspecial Equipment:\n1. Laser Pistol: An accurate and silent firearm capable of ignoring all \ncommon defenses. Wounds inflicted cannot be healed until the end of the \nScenario. When a target is eliminated, it becomes a pile of ashes and cannot be \nhealed, even with special Gifts.\n2. Fog Generator: Instantly creates a thick black smoke that blocks the \nvisibility of non-aliens. The smoke lasts for a few minutes but can be quickly \ndispersed by a strong wind.\n3. Portable Tripod: A small multifunctional vehicle that moves on three legs \nand can carry up to six passengers. The Tripod can reach up to nine feet in \nheight and can easily avoid obstacles thanks to its flexible legs. \nWhenever you use alien technology and one or more NPCs witness it, you \nget 1 Invasion! Token. At the end of each Scene in which you have used the \nDark Ego, the Storyteller rolls 1 die for each Invasion! Token. If they roll at \nleast one 6, the Invasion! Tokens are reset and your comrades initiate an attack \non Earth. The Storyteller introduces 4 Martian Agents into the Scenario, who, \nif not eliminated by the end of it, will force you to return to the Operations \nCenter, removing you from the current Campaign.\nMartian Agent - OL Medium 5 - (1 Wound)\nDescriptor: I am an alien skilled in guerrilla warfare. My monstrous appearance \nparalyzes foolish humans with terror. \nAgenda: Eliminate all humans, starting with the most dangerous individuals: \nthe Hunters of the Order.\nGift - Armed for Invasion: A Martian Agent can use a single effect of Alien \nTechnology 1 time per Scene.","notes":"See Broken Tales - Lost Stories - Exclusive Pre-Gen Hunters.pdf, pages 6.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0,"trigger":"Show off your alien nature by using strange technology or revealing \nyour true identity."},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241656,"modifiedTime":1783973241656,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"ymLcGC1YWfIsEij4","name":"Well-made clothes","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"Well-made clothes","notes":"See Broken Tales - Lost Stories - Exclusive Pre-Gen Hunters.pdf, pages 6.","quantity":1},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241656,"modifiedTime":1783973241656,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"HwygytDxjfPKVS5E","name":"Walking umbrella and pipe","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"Walking umbrella and pipe","notes":"See Broken Tales - Lost Stories - Exclusive Pre-Gen Hunters.pdf, pages 6.","quantity":1},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241656,"modifiedTime":1783973241656,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"2M7Ns0oYev8NQiu9","name":"A small vase with a strange bright red seedling","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"A small vase with a strange bright red seedling","notes":"See Broken Tales - Lost Stories - Exclusive Pre-Gen Hunters.pdf, pages 6.","quantity":1},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241656,"modifiedTime":1783973241656,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"WsbsPNgCtQyRidoi","name":"A box of excellent chocolates","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"A box of excellent chocolates","notes":"See Broken Tales - Lost Stories - Exclusive Pre-Gen Hunters.pdf, pages 6.","quantity":1},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241656,"modifiedTime":1783973241656,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"xUR9xUwNOSWwOs0m","name":"Various fake identity documents","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"Various fake identity documents","notes":"See Broken Tales - Lost Stories - Exclusive Pre-Gen Hunters.pdf, pages 6.","quantity":1},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241656,"modifiedTime":1783973241656,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"emvYl6k9hVXtBXBi","name":"A portrait of a couple commissioned from a famous painter","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"A portrait of a couple commissioned from a famous painter","notes":"See Broken Tales - Lost Stories - Exclusive Pre-Gen Hunters.pdf, pages 6.","quantity":1},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241656,"modifiedTime":1783973241656,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"opuwEp5NBRncn2Da","name":"Source Sheet","type":"storyElement","img":"icons/svg/scroll.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"<p><strong>Lost Stories Exclusives</strong></p><p>Broken Tales - Lost Stories - Exclusive Pre-Gen Hunters.pdf, pages 6.</p>","notes":"Broken Tales - Lost Stories - Exclusive Pre-Gen Hunters.pdf, pages 6"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241656,"modifiedTime":1783973241656,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}],"effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"pregenSlug":"lost-stories-exclusives-the-respectable-mr-and-mrs-mars","pregenCollection":"Lost Stories Exclusives","source":"Broken Tales - Lost Stories - Exclusive Pre-Gen Hunters.pdf","pages":"6"}},"system":{"details":{"concept":"Lost Stories Exclusives","origin":"The Respectable Mr. and Mrs. Mars","role":"Hunter of the Order","notes":"If you do, you will recover 2 Soma and gain 1 Invasion! Token."},"resources":{"soma":{"value":5,"max":5},"xp":0,"wounds":{"value":0,"max":3},"darkness":{"value":0,"max":6}},"opposition":{"defaultLevel":5,"modifier":0},"bookmark":{"wound1":"","wound2":"","wound3":"","extraWound":""}},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241656,"modifiedTime":1783973241656,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"r85gFqIWgFjp2LPF","name":"Doctor V. Frankenstein","type":"hunter","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/avatars/pregens/lost-stories-exclusives-doctor-v-frankenstein.png","items":[{"_id":"ofa4HTiD2VgirOQp","name":"Descriptor 1","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"Gift - Reanimated Corpse: The Creature is immune to electricity and \ncold. Once per Scene, when an ally is about to take 1 Wound, they can \nactivate this Gift to have the Creature intervene in their defense and take \nthe Wound instead. If Victor is the one requesting the use of this Gift, roll \na die: if it comes up even, the Creature will act to save him by applying the \neffect; if it comes up odd, its deep resentment towards its creator will get \nthe better of it and the Creature will not intervene, skipping its possible \nactivation in the Exchange.","notes":"See Broken Tales - Lost Stories - Exclusive Pre-Gen Hunters.pdf, pages 8.","positive":"Gift - Reanimated Corpse: The Creature is immune to electricity and cold. Once per Scene, when an ally is about to take 1 Wound, they can activate this Gift to have the Creature intervene in their defense and take the Wound instead. If Victor is the one requesting the use of this Gift, roll a die: if it comes up even, the Creature will act to save him by applying the effect; if it comes up odd, its deep resentment towards its creator will get the better of it and the Creature will not intervene, skipping its possible activation in the Exchange.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241657,"modifiedTime":1783973241657,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"Y1lBWIDkG06PAJeI","name":"Descriptor 2","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"I am a luminary in physics and medicine and know secrets that the \nbrightest academics can only dream of. I often get lost in my own \nreasoning, which I articulate aloud without realizing it.","notes":"See Broken Tales - Lost Stories - Exclusive Pre-Gen Hunters.pdf, pages 8.","positive":"I am a luminary in physics and medicine and know secrets that the brightest academics can only dream of. I often get lost in my own reasoning, which I articulate aloud without realizing it.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241657,"modifiedTime":1783973241657,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"lmhvKlXSwdyBGwxX","name":"Descriptor 3","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"I always bring the Creature with me and know how to make the \nmost of its potential. There are times when the guilt of creating such \na monster brings me back to reality, and in those rare moments, I \ntry to do a good deed to atone for my sins.","notes":"See Broken Tales - Lost Stories - Exclusive Pre-Gen Hunters.pdf, pages 8.","positive":"I always bring the Creature with me and know how to make the most of its potential. There are times when the guilt of creating such a monster brings me back to reality, and in those rare moments, I try to do a good deed to atone for my sins.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241657,"modifiedTime":1783973241657,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"TmOHneKvHcGPqkzO","name":"Dark Ego Descriptor","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"My mad experiments have expanded my knowledge of death and \nthe occult. I can tell the difference between science and magic. I \ngreedily desire anything I deem useful for my research and have no \nqualms about obtaining it.","notes":"See Broken Tales - Lost Stories - Exclusive Pre-Gen Hunters.pdf, pages 8.","positive":"My mad experiments have expanded my knowledge of death and the occult. I can tell the difference between science and magic. I greedily desire anything I deem useful for my research and have no qualms about obtaining it.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241657,"modifiedTime":1783973241657,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"bQ3hN8fQd6NHuQwu","name":"Behold my Genius","type":"gift","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/icon-gift.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"By spending 1 Soma, you can use one of your \nfuturistic discoveries to generate an electric shock that inflicts 1 Wound. \nThe thunderbolt can strike up to twenty feet away and can change its \ntrajectory to avoid obstacles. Alternatively, you can spend 1 Soma to \ncharge an object with electricity, causing it to discharge when touched and \ninflicting 1 Wound. The object remains charged until the end of the Scene.","notes":"See Broken Tales - Lost Stories - Exclusive Pre-Gen Hunters.pdf, pages 8.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241657,"modifiedTime":1783973241657,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"Z6TL37xv5ndLWEN4","name":"The Creature","type":"gift","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/icon-gift.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"Y our first creation is an NPC managed by the Storyteller, \nwith the following profile: \nOL Medium 5 - (4 Wounds)\nDescriptor: I am a powerful creature who feels no pain and has the strength \nof four men. My appearance is disgusting because of the many stitches that \nhold the pieces of my body together.\nAgenda: To be considered a person like any other and to find a family to take \nme in / I wish Victor to die, but as my creator, I cannot kill him with my own \nhands, and instead I try to facilitate his passing by acting indirectly.","notes":"See Broken Tales - Lost Stories - Exclusive Pre-Gen Hunters.pdf, pages 8.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241657,"modifiedTime":1783973241657,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"xEjdCEdWMF2Ud6Qk","name":"Dark Ego - Reanimator","type":"darkEgo","img":"icons/svg/terror.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"Y ou appeal to the power of science to bring \nlife where there is none. Y ou receive 3 Reanimator Tokens. At your touch, \nand by spending 1 Reanimator Token, an inanimate object or corpse will \ncome to life for the duration of the Scene. Decide whether to also spend \n1 Soma to gain control of what you have animated, or to allow this new \ncreature to have free will. The Storyteller will create an NPC profile for \nhumans and animals (including the reanimation of a single part, such as \na hand or leg), or a Threat profile in the case of an inanimate object, such \nas a door or rope. If you are in control, the creation will do whatever you \ntell it to do. If the creation is acting with free will, it will be moved by the \nStoryteller and may even turn against you.","notes":"See Broken Tales - Lost Stories - Exclusive Pre-Gen Hunters.pdf, pages 8.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0,"trigger":"Dismember or dig up a corpse, ignoring the horror it may cause \nthose watching."},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241657,"modifiedTime":1783973241657,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"MG6cWIutl3IAojYk","name":"Books on science and medicine","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"Books on science and medicine","notes":"See Broken Tales - Lost Stories - Exclusive Pre-Gen Hunters.pdf, pages 8.","quantity":1},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241657,"modifiedTime":1783973241657,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"7h5pyJw8HvFkB8Gi","name":"A surgeon’s bag","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"A surgeon’s bag","notes":"See Broken Tales - Lost Stories - Exclusive Pre-Gen Hunters.pdf, pages 8.","quantity":1},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241657,"modifiedTime":1783973241657,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"bt8vRmh8SbNOCW4I","name":"Vials and jars with pieces of cadavers preserved in alcohol","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"Vials and jars with pieces of cadavers preserved in alcohol","notes":"See Broken Tales - Lost Stories - Exclusive Pre-Gen Hunters.pdf, pages 8.","quantity":1},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241657,"modifiedTime":1783973241657,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"K9yFUfKCJEQsMozv","name":"Electrodes","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"Electrodes","notes":"See Broken Tales - Lost Stories - Exclusive Pre-Gen Hunters.pdf, pages 8.","quantity":1},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241657,"modifiedTime":1783973241657,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"aBfM9KTdtJggUHc2","name":"A valuable machine that generates electricity","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"A valuable machine that generates electricity","notes":"See Broken Tales - Lost Stories - Exclusive Pre-Gen Hunters.pdf, pages 8.","quantity":1},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241657,"modifiedTime":1783973241657,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"gqse4nuJ50mi3g1l","name":"A surgical gown","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"A surgical gown","notes":"See Broken Tales - Lost Stories - Exclusive Pre-Gen Hunters.pdf, pages 8.","quantity":1},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241657,"modifiedTime":1783973241657,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"73Ky5hZNK8IHTSes","name":"Scalpel and saw","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"Scalpel and saw","notes":"See Broken Tales - Lost Stories - Exclusive Pre-Gen Hunters.pdf, pages 8.","quantity":1},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241657,"modifiedTime":1783973241657,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"QoC2JXTk5l7nUeg8","name":"False documents to gain access to morgues and cemeteries","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"False documents to gain access to morgues and cemeteries","notes":"See Broken Tales - Lost Stories - Exclusive Pre-Gen Hunters.pdf, pages 8.","quantity":1},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241657,"modifiedTime":1783973241657,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"z8cG6x63dLwH4JfF","name":"A handkerchief embroidered with the name of my beloved Elizabeth","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"A handkerchief embroidered with the name of my beloved Elizabeth","notes":"See Broken Tales - Lost Stories - Exclusive Pre-Gen Hunters.pdf, pages 8.","quantity":1},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241657,"modifiedTime":1783973241657,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"jiQWwOPRtwYtHieu","name":"Source Sheet","type":"storyElement","img":"icons/svg/scroll.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"<p><strong>Lost Stories Exclusives</strong></p><p>Broken Tales - Lost Stories - Exclusive Pre-Gen Hunters.pdf, pages 8.</p>","notes":"Broken Tales - Lost Stories - Exclusive Pre-Gen Hunters.pdf, pages 8"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241657,"modifiedTime":1783973241657,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}],"effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"pregenSlug":"lost-stories-exclusives-doctor-v-frankenstein","pregenCollection":"Lost Stories Exclusives","source":"Broken Tales - Lost Stories - Exclusive Pre-Gen Hunters.pdf","pages":"8"}},"system":{"details":{"concept":"Lost Stories Exclusives","origin":"Doctor V. Frankenstein","role":"Hunter of the Order","notes":"Gift - Reanimated Corpse: The Creature is immune to electricity and \ncold. Once per Scene, when an ally is about to take 1 Wound, they can \nactivate this Gift to have the Creature intervene in their defense and take \nthe Wound instead. If Victor is the one requesting the use of this Gift, roll \na die: if it comes up even, the Creature will act to save him by applying the \neffect; if it comes up odd, its deep resentment towards its creator will get \nthe better of it and the Creature will not intervene, skipping its possible \nactivation in the Exchange."},"resources":{"soma":{"value":6,"max":6},"xp":0,"wounds":{"value":0,"max":3},"darkness":{"value":0,"max":6}},"opposition":{"defaultLevel":5,"modifier":0},"bookmark":{"wound1":"","wound2":"","wound3":"","extraWound":""}},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241657,"modifiedTime":1783973241657,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"P9s6BDnrb6lYUNOW","name":"Lost Stories Exclusives Hunter 5","type":"hunter","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/avatars/pregens/lost-stories-exclusives-lost-stories-exclusives-hunter-5.png","items":[{"_id":"ss96PgHABCPhvrZc","name":"Descriptor 1","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"If your Champion is knocked out or killed, a new Champion will arrive at \nthe beginning of the next Scenario. Y ou gain 1 Additional Success on all \nChecks where your action removes you from your Champion’s obsessive \nattention.","notes":"See Broken Tales - Lost Stories - Exclusive Pre-Gen Hunters.pdf, pages 10.","positive":"If your Champion is knocked out or killed, a new Champion will arrive at the beginning of the next Scenario. Y ou gain 1 Additional Success on all Checks where your action removes you from your Champion’s obsessive attention.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241657,"modifiedTime":1783973241657,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"JIMkEhd9eT0iulFQ","name":"Descriptor 2","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"I have a talent for assessing people’s merits and flaws, so I am good at \ncoordinating the efforts of those who trust me. I have a soft spot for those \nwho fail but try hard, and though I don’t like to admit it, sometimes the \ninstinct to help losers still takes over.","notes":"See Broken Tales - Lost Stories - Exclusive Pre-Gen Hunters.pdf, pages 10.","positive":"I have a talent for assessing people’s merits and flaws, so I am good at coordinating the efforts of those who trust me. I have a soft spot for those who fail but try hard, and though I don’t like to admit it, sometimes the instinct to help losers still takes over.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241657,"modifiedTime":1783973241657,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"uxlI1M6d7H4TKpvv","name":"Descriptor 3","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"I am very vain and love to waste time admiring my own image.","notes":"See Broken Tales - Lost Stories - Exclusive Pre-Gen Hunters.pdf, pages 10.","positive":"I am very vain and love to waste time admiring my own image.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241657,"modifiedTime":1783973241657,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"56F0zsDutAqw25OW","name":"Dark Ego Descriptor","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"I am an ancient fairy and my magic allows me to manipulate and \ndominate water. I don’t like to be recognized by humans, so I try to \nkeep my powers hidden from prying eyes.","notes":"See Broken Tales - Lost Stories - Exclusive Pre-Gen Hunters.pdf, pages 10.","positive":"I am an ancient fairy and my magic allows me to manipulate and dominate water. I don’t like to be recognized by humans, so I try to keep my powers hidden from prying eyes.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241657,"modifiedTime":1783973241657,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"zKm4twRaiDGMCqyr","name":"Blessing of the Defeated","type":"gift","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/icon-gift.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"If your ally suffers a Wound or fails a Check, \nthey will gain 1 Additional Success (or increase their OL by 1 in the case \nof an NPC) on their next action. Alternatively, once per Scenario, you can \nchoose to have them recover 2 Soma or 1 Wound, or alternatively gain 2 XP . \nIf an NPC achieves their Agenda’s goal thanks to your help, you recover 1 \nSoma and gain 1 XP . \nI have a strong influence on people and my charm cannot be ignored.","notes":"See Broken Tales - Lost Stories - Exclusive Pre-Gen Hunters.pdf, pages 10.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241657,"modifiedTime":1783973241657,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"OMZdS2PpLIMSYPpE","name":"The Lady’s Champion","type":"gift","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/icon-gift.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"There’s always some fool who follows you around \nand proclaims themselves your Champion, until you lose all patience. The \nStoryteller creates an NPC with the following profile at the beginning of the \nScenario:\nOL Medium 5 - (3 Wounds)\nDescriptor: A positive feature that identifies the identity and abilities of the \naspiring Champion. A Downside that identifies total devotion, obsession, love, \nor admiration for Vivienne of the Lake.\nAgenda: Help and protect Vivienne at all costs. Even if my lady tells me not to \nget in her way, I must do so to ensure her safety.","notes":"See Broken Tales - Lost Stories - Exclusive Pre-Gen Hunters.pdf, pages 10.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241657,"modifiedTime":1783973241657,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"Y4QvofH5Zh00oCU1","name":"Dark Ego - Water Fairy","type":"darkEgo","img":"icons/svg/terror.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"Y ou can spend 1 Soma to create 2 small pools \nof lake water, three feet wide and five inches deep. The pools will be created \non any surface, and you can create them anywhere within your field of vision. \nWhen you dip your feet into the water, you unleash your thousand-year-old \nfairy powers. Y ou can choose one of these effects as an additional action in \nany Exchange:\n1. Recover 1 Wound you suffered during this Scene.\n2. Move immediately to a place that you can see. No one can stop you, but \nyou must end up with your feet in contact with the water.\n3. Create a dense fog from a water source that limits visibility but has no \neffect on you.\n4. Hit a target with a jet of water from a pool you create. This is a normal \nattack that requires a Position Check and causes 1 Wound.","notes":"See Broken Tales - Lost Stories - Exclusive Pre-Gen Hunters.pdf, pages 10.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0,"trigger":"Dive into the water of a lake and drop your disguise, or give advice \nto someone you really care about."},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241657,"modifiedTime":1783973241657,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"igwah8FJkAhMki4q","name":"Fine clothes","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"Fine clothes","notes":"See Broken Tales - Lost Stories - Exclusive Pre-Gen Hunters.pdf, pages 10.","quantity":1},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241657,"modifiedTime":1783973241657,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"YLexdD1aQnZhNVNW","name":"Wigs, tricks, and masks","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"Wigs, tricks, and masks","notes":"See Broken Tales - Lost Stories - Exclusive Pre-Gen Hunters.pdf, pages 10.","quantity":1},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241657,"modifiedTime":1783973241657,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"qFC4dJR3YL7R0yV3","name":"A few trinkets the Order insists on calling “Treasures”","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"A few trinkets the Order insists on calling “Treasures”","notes":"See Broken Tales - Lost Stories - Exclusive Pre-Gen Hunters.pdf, pages 10.","quantity":1},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241657,"modifiedTime":1783973241657,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"jtIabv6sbsUz94Ni","name":"A small portrait of the only human I ever loved","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"A small portrait of the only human I ever loved","notes":"See Broken Tales - Lost Stories - Exclusive Pre-Gen Hunters.pdf, pages 10.","quantity":1},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241657,"modifiedTime":1783973241657,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"iYodYv5j8dj2EtEJ","name":"Source Sheet","type":"storyElement","img":"icons/svg/scroll.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"<p><strong>Lost Stories Exclusives</strong></p><p>Broken Tales - Lost Stories - Exclusive Pre-Gen Hunters.pdf, pages 10.</p>","notes":"Broken Tales - Lost Stories - Exclusive Pre-Gen Hunters.pdf, pages 10"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241657,"modifiedTime":1783973241657,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}],"effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"pregenSlug":"lost-stories-exclusives-lost-stories-exclusives-hunter-5","pregenCollection":"Lost Stories Exclusives","source":"Broken Tales - Lost Stories - Exclusive Pre-Gen Hunters.pdf","pages":"10"}},"system":{"details":{"concept":"Lost Stories Exclusives","origin":"Lost Stories Exclusives Hunter 5","role":"Hunter of the Order","notes":"If your Champion is knocked out or killed, a new Champion will arrive at \nthe beginning of the next Scenario. Y ou gain 1 Additional Success on all \nChecks where your action removes you from your Champion’s obsessive \nattention."},"resources":{"soma":{"value":6,"max":6},"xp":0,"wounds":{"value":0,"max":3},"darkness":{"value":0,"max":6}},"opposition":{"defaultLevel":5,"modifier":0},"bookmark":{"wound1":"","wound2":"","wound3":"","extraWound":""}},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241657,"modifiedTime":1783973241657,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"8U9oLHuDgT49C4GV","name":"Lost Stories Exclusives Hunter 6","type":"hunter","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/avatars/pregens/lost-stories-exclusives-lost-stories-exclusives-hunter-6.png","items":[{"_id":"e9fKBOsBdDAgYi7w","name":"Descriptor 1","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"Porziella, my faithful flea, is always with me and has guarded my \nback like a trusted servant. Over time, I have trained Porziella to \nperform various tasks, including very complex ones. Porziella loves \nhuman blood, and although this disgusts people, I try to satisfy her \nwhenever I can.","notes":"See Broken Tales - Lost Stories - Exclusive Pre-Gen Hunters.pdf, pages 12.","positive":"Porziella, my faithful flea, is always with me and has guarded my back like a trusted servant. Over time, I have trained Porziella to perform various tasks, including very complex ones. Porziella loves human blood, and although this disgusts people, I try to satisfy her whenever I can.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241658,"modifiedTime":1783973241658,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"8QmKPaTQvIzuayMY","name":"Descriptor 2","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"I learned some magic tricks from seven bandits, all of them brothers, \nand I know about arcane arts. I am attracted to magic and want to \ngather all knowledge about it.","notes":"See Broken Tales - Lost Stories - Exclusive Pre-Gen Hunters.pdf, pages 12.","positive":"I learned some magic tricks from seven bandits, all of them brothers, and I know about arcane arts. I am attracted to magic and want to gather all knowledge about it.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241658,"modifiedTime":1783973241658,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"v3RLn2DD0Zw72zvU","name":"Descriptor 3","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"I am courageous and stubborn. When I speak about justice and \nequality, the passion that animates me touches people’s hearts. For me, \nthe cause comes before everything and I am ready to take any action, \neven the most extreme.","notes":"See Broken Tales - Lost Stories - Exclusive Pre-Gen Hunters.pdf, pages 12.","positive":"I am courageous and stubborn. When I speak about justice and equality, the passion that animates me touches people’s hearts. For me, the cause comes before everything and I am ready to take any action, even the most extreme.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241658,"modifiedTime":1783973241658,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"nv6NIBZPVIjV7K6I","name":"Porziella the Faithful Flea","type":"gift","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/icon-gift.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"Y our trusty flea follows you like a shadow. \nPorziella is an NPC under your full control with the following profile:\nOL Medium 5 - (3 Wounds)\nDescriptor: I am a flea the size of a dog, my skin is so hard and thick that not \neven a sword can pierce it.\nGift - Loyal Flea: Porziella always recognizes blood by its taste, which allows \nher to follow a trail or recognize who it belongs to without error. Once per \nScenario, Porziella can shield Viola by taking 1 Wound in her place. If she \ndoes this, she will be out of combat until the end of the Scene. If Porziella is \nnot present, Viola can spend 1 Soma to bring her into the Scene immediately, \novercoming all obstacles and impediments.","notes":"See Broken Tales - Lost Stories - Exclusive Pre-Gen Hunters.pdf, pages 12.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241658,"modifiedTime":1783973241658,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"98Du55WprRoi8tf2","name":"The Magic of the Seven","type":"gift","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/icon-gift.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"Once per Scenario, you can use any of the \nfollowing powers, but you must have the appropriate Equipment.\n1. Mase’s Earring: It allows you to hear a speech even through a wall.\n2. Nardo’s Soap: Gives you 3 Additional Successes to free yourself from \nropes and chains, or to slip away. \n3. C ola’s Razor: Allows you to inflict 1 Additional Wound with one attack. \n4. Micco’s Staff: Plants sprout to block a passageway; the Storyteller creates a Threat that can absorb up to 3 Wounds before yielding. \n5. Petrullo’s Water: Creates a jet of water that strikes up to 30 feet but does \nno damage. \n6. Ascadeo’s Rock: It can be thrown and will fall exactly where you want it \nto fall, without causing any damage. \n7. Ceccone’s Crossbow: Grants you 2 Additional Successes when you \nshoot a dart.","notes":"See Broken Tales - Lost Stories - Exclusive Pre-Gen Hunters.pdf, pages 12.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241658,"modifiedTime":1783973241658,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"UWvbo86UcVemkzus","name":"Dark Ego - Taking Destiny into My Own Hands","type":"darkEgo","img":"icons/svg/terror.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"Nothing and no one \ncan hold you against your will. Y ou are free from all obstacles and can move \nat any time, even in the midst of battle, without anyone being able to block \nor harm you. By spending 1 Soma, you can automatically break down any \nenvironmental obstacle in your way, such as walls, doors, or a tangled web of \nbrambles. Y our presence undermines the authority of the powerful: all NPCs \ntied to any kind of authority lower their OL by 1; all Hunters tied to faith or \nwith strong leadership skills receive 1 Penalty per Check.","notes":"See Broken Tales - Lost Stories - Exclusive Pre-Gen Hunters.pdf, pages 12.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0,"trigger":"Stand up for someone being oppressed, or openly denounce those \nwho hold power over you.\nEquipment: \nA staff sprouting tendrils / A large bar of soap / A sharp razor / A small \npitcher of water / A perfectly polished rock / A light crossbow / A golden \nearring.\nSoma\n 6\nXP\nWounds \n1.\n2.\n3.\nExtra \nWound.\nI am the Princess of Altomonte, and I succeeded my father by taking full control of his lands. I have always rebelled against the old laws \nof the past, which placed all power in the hands of men. The strength of my ideas was unyielding, leading me to carry out serious acts of \nreprisal against the noble families most tied to the old patriarchal traditions. The Order intervened to stop me, but when they realized that \ntaking me prisoner would make me a martyr, I was offered a deal: join the ranks of the Order to fight the darkness. In exchange, I have \nbeen promised favors and political power with which to change the male-dominated society of my era forever."},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241658,"modifiedTime":1783973241658,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"nzkHSVZyA3huKfAU","name":"Source Sheet","type":"storyElement","img":"icons/svg/scroll.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"<p><strong>Lost Stories Exclusives</strong></p><p>Broken Tales - Lost Stories - Exclusive Pre-Gen Hunters.pdf, pages 12.</p>","notes":"Broken Tales - Lost Stories - Exclusive Pre-Gen Hunters.pdf, pages 12"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241658,"modifiedTime":1783973241658,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}],"effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"pregenSlug":"lost-stories-exclusives-lost-stories-exclusives-hunter-6","pregenCollection":"Lost Stories Exclusives","source":"Broken Tales - Lost Stories - Exclusive Pre-Gen Hunters.pdf","pages":"12"}},"system":{"details":{"concept":"Lost Stories Exclusives","origin":"Lost Stories Exclusives Hunter 6","role":"Hunter of the Order","notes":"<p><strong>Lost Stories Exclusives</strong></p><p>Broken Tales - Lost Stories - Exclusive Pre-Gen Hunters.pdf, pages 12.</p>"},"resources":{"soma":{"value":6,"max":6},"xp":0,"wounds":{"value":0,"max":3},"darkness":{"value":0,"max":6}},"opposition":{"defaultLevel":5,"modifier":0},"bookmark":{"wound1":"","wound2":"","wound3":"","extraWound":""}},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241658,"modifiedTime":1783973241658,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"CF5YTOjHqrnfS4P9","name":"Lost Stories Exclusives Hunter 7","type":"hunter","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/avatars/pregens/lost-stories-exclusives-lost-stories-exclusives-hunter-7.png","items":[{"_id":"7nEOJuhFrYoCpOqo","name":"Descriptor 1","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"Y ou start the Scenario with 6 Pebble Tokens. During a Scene, you can \nspend 1 Pebble to activate one of these effects:\n1. Return to a place you have already visited, this happens very fast \nand allows you to arrive before anyone else, avoiding any possible \nobstacle.\n2. Get information from the Storyteller about a Place’s weaknesses or \ndetails of a procedure, such as an arcane ritual or a guard shift.\n3. Act immediately after another Hunter, but only to perform an action \nthat is not intended to harm anyone. \n4. Pull a useful item from your bag to deal with a Threat that has arisen.","notes":"See Broken Tales - Lost Stories - Exclusive Pre-Gen Hunters.pdf, pages 14.","positive":"Y ou start the Scenario with 6 Pebble Tokens. During a Scene, you can spend 1 Pebble to activate one of these effects: 1. Return to a place you have already visited, this happens very fast and allows you to arrive before anyone else, avoiding any possible obstacle. 2. Get information from the Storyteller about a Place’s weaknesses or details of a procedure, such as an arcane ritual or a guard shift. 3. Act immediately after another Hunter, but only to perform an action that is not intended to harm anyone. 4. Pull a useful item from your bag to deal with a Threat that has arisen.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241658,"modifiedTime":1783973241658,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"QJyeNN8IXckpvKzd","name":"Descriptor 2","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"I have an unusual mind and remember every detail, even years \nlater. My body is puny and I hate to do strenuous work.","notes":"See Broken Tales - Lost Stories - Exclusive Pre-Gen Hunters.pdf, pages 14.","positive":"I have an unusual mind and remember every detail, even years later. My body is puny and I hate to do strenuous work.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241658,"modifiedTime":1783973241658,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"fGBTjDyRw5nCK0Lh","name":"Descriptor 3","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"I have charisma to spare and I am a smooth talker who commands \nrespect and admiration. I must always have the last word.","notes":"See Broken Tales - Lost Stories - Exclusive Pre-Gen Hunters.pdf, pages 14.","positive":"I have charisma to spare and I am a smooth talker who commands respect and admiration. I must always have the last word.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241658,"modifiedTime":1783973241658,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"nT5e8msZexkZtr7E","name":"Dark Ego Descriptor","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"It only takes me a few seconds to assess the situation and use it to \nmy advantage. I have a soft spot for loving families who remind me \nof what I will never have.","notes":"See Broken Tales - Lost Stories - Exclusive Pre-Gen Hunters.pdf, pages 14.","positive":"It only takes me a few seconds to assess the situation and use it to my advantage. I have a soft spot for loving families who remind me of what I will never have.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241658,"modifiedTime":1783973241658,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"EbQzIvm6R98HYwQZ","name":"Tiny","type":"gift","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/icon-gift.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"Y ou know how to go unnoticed, so no one will ever pick you as \na direct target of one of their actions if there is at least one other Hunter \nin the Scene. Y ou can spend 1 Soma to leave a location without anyone \nnoticing, as long as there is at least one other Hunter to attract attention. \nY ou get 1 Additional Success on each Check where you can use your \ndiminutive stature, but you also get 1 Penalty on each Check where you \nhave to use brute force or physical strength.","notes":"See Broken Tales - Lost Stories - Exclusive Pre-Gen Hunters.pdf, pages 14.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241658,"modifiedTime":1783973241658,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"MTAOGOyWrwQM3c3d","name":"In the Right Place at the Right Time","type":"gift","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/icon-gift.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"Y ou don’t get confused easily.","notes":"See Broken Tales - Lost Stories - Exclusive Pre-Gen Hunters.pdf, pages 14.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241658,"modifiedTime":1783973241658,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"lDHJJODVXd2K1Ig0","name":"Dark Ego - Infallible Cunning","type":"darkEgo","img":"icons/svg/terror.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"When you activate this Gift, the \nStoryteller will reveal to you the Downside of all NPCs in the Scene. \nY ou’ll also learn the easiest way to escape from your location and the most \nvaluable item present. When a Hunter (including you) performs a Check \nand gets a Standard Outcome, you can spend 1 Soma to add 1 Increment \nof your choice, including a special effect of a Gift possessed by the Hunter \nperforming the action.","notes":"See Broken Tales - Lost Stories - Exclusive Pre-Gen Hunters.pdf, pages 14.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0,"trigger":"Take a few minutes to observe the situation and tell the NPC in \nfront of you what you really think of them. \nEquipment: \nA bag of white pebbles / Seven small gold crowns / Valuable coins and \njewels / A mask with the features of an ogre / A pair of valuable traveling \nboots with two hidden stilettos / Contracts and records of secret negotiations \n/ The key to one of your many secret hideouts / A sling. \nSoma\n 6\nXP\nWounds \n1.\n2.\n3.\nExtra \nWound.\nI am the most important criminal of my time, and there are more than a thousand scoundrels in my employ. I have \nsingle-handedly built up my power through cunning, even committing acts that many people consider despicable. \nThose who lecture me on my misdeeds do not understand that the only thing I wanted in my life was a family that loved \nme. The Order disrupted my criminal empire, but when they realized that eliminating me would start a war among \noutlaws across Europe, I was pardoned and welcomed as a Hunter. My gifts and knowledge ensure a constant flow \nof information, which I use to track down whatever the Order is hunting. Locked away in the fortress of my solitude, I \ncontinue to run my empire. Perhaps I can find a true family in the ranks of the Hunters."},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241658,"modifiedTime":1783973241658,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"koQswZYMAKV4gfcO","name":"Source Sheet","type":"storyElement","img":"icons/svg/scroll.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"<p><strong>Lost Stories Exclusives</strong></p><p>Broken Tales - Lost Stories - Exclusive Pre-Gen Hunters.pdf, pages 14.</p>","notes":"Broken Tales - Lost Stories - Exclusive Pre-Gen Hunters.pdf, pages 14"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241658,"modifiedTime":1783973241658,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}],"effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"pregenSlug":"lost-stories-exclusives-lost-stories-exclusives-hunter-7","pregenCollection":"Lost Stories Exclusives","source":"Broken Tales - Lost Stories - Exclusive Pre-Gen Hunters.pdf","pages":"14"}},"system":{"details":{"concept":"Lost Stories Exclusives","origin":"Lost Stories Exclusives Hunter 7","role":"Hunter of the Order","notes":"Y ou start the Scenario with 6 Pebble Tokens. During a Scene, you can \nspend 1 Pebble to activate one of these effects:\n1. Return to a place you have already visited, this happens very fast \nand allows you to arrive before anyone else, avoiding any possible \nobstacle.\n2. Get information from the Storyteller about a Place’s weaknesses or \ndetails of a procedure, such as an arcane ritual or a guard shift.\n3. Act immediately after another Hunter, but only to perform an action \nthat is not intended to harm anyone. \n4. Pull a useful item from your bag to deal with a Threat that has arisen."},"resources":{"soma":{"value":6,"max":6},"xp":0,"wounds":{"value":0,"max":3},"darkness":{"value":0,"max":6}},"opposition":{"defaultLevel":5,"modifier":0},"bookmark":{"wound1":"","wound2":"","wound3":"","extraWound":""}},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241658,"modifiedTime":1783973241658,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"GCwmgaZ2Bf97OmOx","name":"Lost Stories Exclusives Hunter 8","type":"hunter","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/avatars/pregens/lost-stories-exclusives-lost-stories-exclusives-hunter-8.png","items":[{"_id":"umPH1whSPprXc0Qk","name":"Descriptor 1","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"I am a skilled Hunter and know what it takes to survive in wild \nplaces. I find it hard to trust anyone, but when I do, I never question \nthe good faith of the person I have chosen.","notes":"See Broken Tales - Lost Stories - Exclusive Pre-Gen Hunters.pdf, pages 16.","positive":"I am a skilled Hunter and know what it takes to survive in wild places. I find it hard to trust anyone, but when I do, I never question the good faith of the person I have chosen.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241658,"modifiedTime":1783973241658,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"asTzwawxk26wqRYD","name":"Descriptor 2","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"My senses are keen and my body is hardened by the outdoors. I hate \nbig cities, hustle and bustle, and generally can’t stand people who talk \ntoo much.","notes":"See Broken Tales - Lost Stories - Exclusive Pre-Gen Hunters.pdf, pages 16.","positive":"My senses are keen and my body is hardened by the outdoors. I hate big cities, hustle and bustle, and generally can’t stand people who talk too much.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241658,"modifiedTime":1783973241658,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"2GRF4ZvCOgULSxSB","name":"Descriptor 3","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"I am trained to kill all kinds of beasts and know how to use the \nhunting grounds to my advantage. Monsters must always be \ndestroyed, for them I see no mercy or redemption.","notes":"See Broken Tales - Lost Stories - Exclusive Pre-Gen Hunters.pdf, pages 16.","positive":"I am trained to kill all kinds of beasts and know how to use the hunting grounds to my advantage. Monsters must always be destroyed, for them I see no mercy or redemption.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241658,"modifiedTime":1783973241658,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"tjV8UKWxQfkURkA0","name":"Hunting Companion","type":"gift","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/icon-gift.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"Y ou don’t open your heart easily, but occasionally \nyou find companions you can trust. At the beginning of the Scenario, you \nchoose another Hunter as your hunting companion, who will receive 1 \nAdditional Success on all Defense Checks they make while you are in close \nproximity to cover their back. Y ou will always know where your hunting \ncompanion is and can spend 1 Soma to get to where they are, ignoring all \nobstacles. Y ou never speak and cannot express yourself verbally, but your \ncompanion will always clearly understand anything you try to tell them.","notes":"See Broken Tales - Lost Stories - Exclusive Pre-Gen Hunters.pdf, pages 16.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241658,"modifiedTime":1783973241658,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"S5IV1MCMSr2ZRjuV","name":"Stalking","type":"gift","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/icon-gift.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"No prey can escape you, once per Scene you can find distinct \ntraces in a place or on an object. The Storyteller will reveal a useful piece of \ninformation of your choice: who left the clue, where it is, or a weakness in the \nobject. Y ou can spend 1 Soma to blend into your surroundings: as long as you \ndo not take any conspicuous actions (at the Storyteller’s discretion), Minor \nNPCs will not be able to see you, and you will get 3 Additional Successes on \nany Checks you make to go unnoticed or catch someone off guard.","notes":"See Broken Tales - Lost Stories - Exclusive Pre-Gen Hunters.pdf, pages 16.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241658,"modifiedTime":1783973241658,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"pBRa4QpyyF0InkPM","name":"Dark Ego - It’s Time to Kill the Beast","type":"darkEgo","img":"icons/svg/terror.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"Once per Scene, if you make an \nattack against an enemy with monstrous characteristics, you automatically \nhit without a Check and your attack inflicts 2 Wounds. All of the Wounds \nyou inflict leave clearly visible marks and cannot be healed by the victim \nuntil the end of the Scenario. When you activate this Gift, the Storyteller will \nreveal to you one Gift of each monstrous opponent in the Scene. \nNote: A “monstrous trait” is defined as any Hunter or NPC with Gifts or \nDescriptors that represent superhuman physical traits and abilities that also \ngive them a monstrous appearance. However, the Storyteller has the final say \non whether or not a Character is monstrous.","notes":"See Broken Tales - Lost Stories - Exclusive Pre-Gen Hunters.pdf, pages 16.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0,"trigger":"Openly challenge a monstrous creature by revealing your true nature.\nEquipment: \nThe right weapon for each beast / A cloak that changes color according to \nits surroundings / A small leaf-shaped ocarina / Animal traps / A deer heart \npreserved under spirits / A necklace of wolf fangs. \nSoma\n 6\nXP\nWounds \n1.\n2.\n3.\nExtra \nWound.\nI am a lone beast slayer who has dedicated his entire life to eradicating monsters and aberrations. The \nOne Who Plots in the Shadows corrupted my soul by drawing on the pain of the monsters’ poor victims I \ncould not save. The Order has freed me from this evil influence and welcomed me into its ranks as a strong \narm against all manner of monsters. I do not like to talk or waste time with complicated plans: when it is \ntime to begin the hunt, having my weapons ready is all that matters."},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241658,"modifiedTime":1783973241658,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"eGieUgjSCQphOxi8","name":"Source Sheet","type":"storyElement","img":"icons/svg/scroll.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"<p><strong>Lost Stories Exclusives</strong></p><p>Broken Tales - Lost Stories - Exclusive Pre-Gen Hunters.pdf, pages 16.</p>","notes":"Broken Tales - Lost Stories - Exclusive Pre-Gen Hunters.pdf, pages 16"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241658,"modifiedTime":1783973241658,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}],"effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"pregenSlug":"lost-stories-exclusives-lost-stories-exclusives-hunter-8","pregenCollection":"Lost Stories Exclusives","source":"Broken Tales - Lost Stories - Exclusive Pre-Gen Hunters.pdf","pages":"16"}},"system":{"details":{"concept":"Lost Stories Exclusives","origin":"Lost Stories Exclusives Hunter 8","role":"Hunter of the Order","notes":"<p><strong>Lost Stories Exclusives</strong></p><p>Broken Tales - Lost Stories - Exclusive Pre-Gen Hunters.pdf, pages 16.</p>"},"resources":{"soma":{"value":6,"max":6},"xp":0,"wounds":{"value":0,"max":3},"darkness":{"value":0,"max":6}},"opposition":{"defaultLevel":5,"modifier":0},"bookmark":{"wound1":"","wound2":"","wound3":"","extraWound":""}},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241658,"modifiedTime":1783973241658,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"9sYiYE9mAkUH5CBu","name":"Lost Stories Exclusives Hunter 9","type":"hunter","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/avatars/pregens/lost-stories-exclusives-lost-stories-exclusives-hunter-9.png","items":[{"_id":"eljCXUoiZFoiBsKc","name":"Descriptor 1","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"I have extremely keen eyesight and no detail escapes me. I can see \neverything, even in the dark or in the thickest fog. Sometimes I don’t \nunderstand whether the things I see are real or just a figment of my \nimagination.","notes":"See Broken Tales - Lost Stories - Exclusive Pre-Gen Hunters.pdf, pages 18.","positive":"I have extremely keen eyesight and no detail escapes me. I can see everything, even in the dark or in the thickest fog. Sometimes I don’t understand whether the things I see are real or just a figment of my imagination.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241658,"modifiedTime":1783973241658,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"R3FmES4ApvkGoYry","name":"Descriptor 2","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"I am used to walking around completely naked, so my physique is \ntough. I hate having unnecessary things on me, except for my beloved \ncrown.","notes":"See Broken Tales - Lost Stories - Exclusive Pre-Gen Hunters.pdf, pages 18.","positive":"I am used to walking around completely naked, so my physique is tough. I hate having unnecessary things on me, except for my beloved crown.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241658,"modifiedTime":1783973241658,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"Y167iSr58Rtrr4UR","name":"Descriptor 3","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"I am good with words, I know etiquette, and I know how to dazzle the \ncrowd. I cannot refrain from commenting with the utmost sincerity \non the way my interlocutors dress.","notes":"See Broken Tales - Lost Stories - Exclusive Pre-Gen Hunters.pdf, pages 18.","positive":"I am good with words, I know etiquette, and I know how to dazzle the crowd. I cannot refrain from commenting with the utmost sincerity on the way my interlocutors dress.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241659,"modifiedTime":1783973241659,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"gr8mXAexVZ22u7XM","name":"What I Want to See","type":"gift","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/icon-gift.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"If you see it, you can make it real. Y ou can spend 1 \nSoma and say what object you have in front of you. For the rest of the Scene, \nyou can use it as if it were real with all the characteristics it should have. Y ou \nget 1 Additional Success for each Check if you gain a genuine advantage due \nto the fact that others cannot see the object. Y ou can only have one object \ncreated by this Gift at a time. Y ou are completely immune to any effect based \non reducing or nullifying the ability to see.","notes":"See Broken Tales - Lost Stories - Exclusive Pre-Gen Hunters.pdf, pages 18.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241659,"modifiedTime":1783973241659,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"zLG1P7BTyrf8PhPU","name":"What I Don’t Want to See","type":"gift","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/icon-gift.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"Y ou start each Scene in the shadows, and \nas long as you are in this state, no one will notice your presence or the fact \nthat you are completely naked. As long as you do not perform actions that \nmake you the center of attention, you can continue to do whatever you want \nwithout anyone getting in the way, and you will never be singled out for \naction by a possible enemy. Subjects who base their perception on senses \nother than sight can easily detect you. When you perform a conspicuous \naction or decide to draw attention to yourself, you shift into the light. As \nlong as you are in this state, everyone will see you for what you really are. Y ou \nget 1 Additional Success on the first Check you make when you enter this \nstate. Y ou can spend 1 Soma at any time to return to the shadows.","notes":"See Broken Tales - Lost Stories - Exclusive Pre-Gen Hunters.pdf, pages 18.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241659,"modifiedTime":1783973241659,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"vziYOkAVgR3fsD2C","name":"Dark Ego - All Eyes on Me","type":"darkEgo","img":"icons/svg/terror.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"When you choose to be the center of \nattention, you are the king of the party. Decide what you want to wear and \nwhat valuables you want to display, and you will look the part. Y ou will also \nreceive the following benefits:\n1. All NPCs present will be favorably disposed toward you, and you can \ncreate an Agenda for one of them to represent their strong interest in \nyou. Particularly powerful subjects may require a Position Check, at the \nStoryteller’s discretion. \n2. If a lie is told in your presence, the person who told it suffers 1 Wound \ncaused by bleeding from the eyes.\n3. If you help someone permanently improve the aesthetics of a person or \nplace, you gain 1 Soma. \nThe effect of this Gift lasts until the end of the Scene or until you activate \nanother of your Gifts.","notes":"See Broken Tales - Lost Stories - Exclusive Pre-Gen Hunters.pdf, pages 18.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0,"trigger":"Take a few minutes to prepare for a meeting with someone you \ndeem important. \nEquipment: \nThe precious crown that I always wear on my head. \nSoma\n 5\nXP\nWounds \n1.\n2.\n3.\nExtra \nWound.\nI was a vain ruler and had eyes only for beauty. My heart was pure and my desire to help others was \nsincere, but everyone took advantage of me and clouded my vision with false words. Seeing beyond the wall \nof lies cost me dearly, but now I am not afraid. I see everything as it is, even myself. The Order hired me as a \nHunter, asking only that I use my power in the service of justice, without ulterior motives, without falsehood. \nBut is that really the case? I no longer care, for now, the only truth that matters to me is the one I choose to \ncreate with my mind."},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241659,"modifiedTime":1783973241659,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"wSJApWxwcFLrO3J8","name":"Source Sheet","type":"storyElement","img":"icons/svg/scroll.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"<p><strong>Lost Stories Exclusives</strong></p><p>Broken Tales - Lost Stories - Exclusive Pre-Gen Hunters.pdf, pages 18.</p>","notes":"Broken Tales - Lost Stories - Exclusive Pre-Gen Hunters.pdf, pages 18"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241659,"modifiedTime":1783973241659,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}],"effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"pregenSlug":"lost-stories-exclusives-lost-stories-exclusives-hunter-9","pregenCollection":"Lost Stories Exclusives","source":"Broken Tales - Lost Stories - Exclusive Pre-Gen Hunters.pdf","pages":"18"}},"system":{"details":{"concept":"Lost Stories Exclusives","origin":"Lost Stories Exclusives Hunter 9","role":"Hunter of the Order","notes":"<p><strong>Lost Stories Exclusives</strong></p><p>Broken Tales - Lost Stories - Exclusive Pre-Gen Hunters.pdf, pages 18.</p>"},"resources":{"soma":{"value":5,"max":5},"xp":0,"wounds":{"value":0,"max":3},"darkness":{"value":0,"max":6}},"opposition":{"defaultLevel":5,"modifier":0},"bookmark":{"wound1":"","wound2":"","wound3":"","extraWound":""}},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241659,"modifiedTime":1783973241659,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
